(2, '2', '1131', '陳依兌', '43160200000000 ', '43160', '1856', '1', 1, 10, '人工智慧創新應用', 'Innovative Applications of Artificial Intelligence', '陳依兌,謝楠楨,葉馨婷,翁仕彥,郭朝揚', 5, 0, 5, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F906', '2', '1,2', '修課限制：本所、外所、跨校', '本課程旨在增進同學對人工智慧前瞻且創新議題的瞭解，啟發同學們\r\n對如何運用AI人工智慧，以提升產業競爭優勢之策略思維。課程進行將以理論與實務之AI策\r\n略為主，透過播放相關短片與專題講座、專題演討等方式讓同學們理解AI科技對健康照護產\r\n業、生活型態等所造成的影響與改變。接著，以主題討論方式藉由探討AI科技應用於健康照\r\n護產業中的實際案例，幫助學生更了解目前產業與國際的趨勢。', 'This course aims to enhance students\' understanding of forward\r\nlooking and innovative issues of artificial intelligence, and inspire students\' strategic \r\nthinking on how to use AI artificial intelligence to enhance industrial competitiveness. \r\nThe course will focus on theoretical and practical AI strategies. By playing relevant \r\nshort videos, special lectures, special lectures, etc., students will understand the \r\nimpact and changes of AI technology on the health care industry and lifestyle. Then, by \r\ndiscussing the actual cases of AI technology applied in the health care industry in the \r\nform of a themed discussion, it will help students better understand the current industry \r\nand international trends.', '9074', '6691Z021', '669A10', '人日碩10', '90,740,774,055,902,500,000'),
(3, '3', '1131', '郭朝揚', '431600229011A0', '43160', '229', '1', 1, 0, '人工智慧', 'Artificial Intelligence', '郭朝揚', 7, 1, 6, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F906', '4', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本所、外所、跨校', '本課程將介紹人工智慧的基本理論，從人工智慧應用在各領域的案例，讓同學理解人工智慧的原\r\n理，並進一步推動學生跨領域結合的思維，將人工智慧應用在不同的專業領域上。', 'This course incorporates the introduction of healthcare and basic \r\ntheory of artificial intelligence. We will explore the application of AI in healthcare, \r\nwhich can cultivate students’ capacity of knowledge, innovation, and interdisciplinary \r\nthinking. Students can apply the AI in many fields.', '1109', '6691Q031', '669211', 'AI研一  ', '1109'),
(4, '4', '1131', '陳依兌', '431600067011A0', '43160', '67', '1', 1, 0, '研究方法論', 'Research Methodology', '陳依兌,翁仕彥,郭朝揚,葉馨婷', 5, 0, 5, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F906', '4', '9,10', '修課限制：本所、外所、跨校', '本課程內容第一階段為科學研究:包含科學精神、研究主題的選\r\n擇、文獻的蒐集彙整、研究構念的概念化與操作化、測量的基本概念與方法、假說的檢定、\r\n抽樣的基本概念、 資料分析、研究結果的呈現與詮釋等。第二階段為撰寫學術研究論文:學\r\n術論文各章節的寫作要 點,包含題目與摘要、前言、文獻探討、APA 論文寫作格式、概念性\r\n架構與假說檢定、測量、 結果、結論與討論。', 'This course is designed to accomplish four objectives. The course \r\nwill begin with issues in scientific thinking, model building, and ethical implications. \r\nSecondly, it will familiarize students with major procedures in research design, such as \r\nthe \r\nformation of research questions, literature review, conceptualization and \r\noperationalization of research questions, questionnaire design, and sampling procedures). \r\nThirdly, the course will review methods in data collection and analysis with special \r\nemphasis on the evaluation of data quality such as reliability and validity. Finally, \r\nthis course will familiarize students with major guidelines for writing research papers.', '9074', '6691Q021', '669211', 'AI研一  ', '9,074,025,211,090,550'),
(5, '5', '1131', '葉馨婷', '431600044011A0', '43160', '44', '1', 1, 0, '進階應用統計學', 'Advanced Applied Statistics', '葉馨婷', 5, 0, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F906', '4', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所、外所、跨校', '本課程旨在幫助學生瞭解統計學相關應用，包括資料整理、機率\r\n論、抽樣分配、估計與信心區間等主 題；學期後半段，將著重在提出研究假設之能力培養，\r\n同時訓練學生運用各種方法進行假設檢 定，包括卡方檢定、t-test、變異數分析、簡單迴歸\r\n分析，並透過課程講授、交互討論、課後作業及學習考試方式，探討統計學相關之觀念、原\r\n則、模式與方法。', 'This course is designed to help students understand the application \r\nof statistics. Including data collection, probability theory, sampling allocation, \r\nestimation and confidence intervals; in the second half of the semester, the focus will \r\nbe on cultivating the ability to propose research hypotheses. This course also teaches \r\nstudents to use various methods to test hypotheses, including chi-square test, t- test, \r\nvariation analysis, simple regression analysis Students will explore concepts, principles, \r\nmodels and methods related to statistics through course lectures, discussions, homework \r\nand study exams.', '559', '6691Q011', '669211', 'AI研一  ', '559'),
(6, '6', '1131', '周定衡', '30860200000000 ', '30860', '1710', '1', 1, 11, '運動訓練科學專題研究', 'Individual Studies in Science of Sports Training', '周定衡', 3, 2, 1, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'I401', '1', '6,7', '修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. \n2.開放跨校選課  open for cross-registration with students from other schools. \n3.可選學生為國際運動科學外國學生專班一年級生、外系國際碩士班學生、全校國內碩士班學生 Eligible students include first-year students of the International Sport Science Master\'s Program, international master\'s program students from other departments, and all domestic master\'s program students in the university.修課限制：全英語授課', 'Sports training is an increasingly important area of sports science, and this course provides accessible and up-to-date coverage of this key topic. Modern coaches need to be applied scientists who keep abreast of research and are able to apply a multidisciplinary understanding to their practice. The course therefore examines training/coaching in terms of biomechanics, physiology and psychology, as well as perennial issues such as athlete motivation, nutrition, design of training programmes, talent identification, monitoring and ethics.', 'Sports training is an increasingly important area of sports science, and this course provides accessible and up-to-date coverage of this key topic. Modern coaches need to be applied scientists who keep abreast of research and are able to apply a multidisciplinary understanding to their practice. The course therefore examines training/coaching in terms of biomechanics, physiology and psychology, as well as perennial issues such as athlete motivation, nutrition, design of training programmes, talent identification, monitoring and ethics.', '1190', '6801Z151', '680Q11', '運國碩11', '1190'),
(7, '7', '1131', '吳孝觀', '30860100000000 ', '30860', '1350', '1', 1, 12, '輔助與復健運動醫學專題研究', 'Alternative and Rehabilitation Sport Medicine Research', '吳孝觀,林莉如', 3, 2, 1, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'I401', '4', '6,7', '\"修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. \n2.開放跨校選課  open for cross-registration with students from other schools. \n3.可選學生為國際運動科學外國學生專班一年級生、外系國際碩士班學生、全校國內碩士班學生 Eligible students include first-year students of the International Sport Science Master\'s Program, international master\'s program students from other departments, and all domestic master\'s program students in the university.\"\n修課限制：全英語授課', 'This course is designed to discuss the differences between alternative complementary medicine and current western medicine.  For example, the traditional Chinese medicine and herb medicine have already been gradually accepted, and we will guide students to read and search current scientific literatures that support the therapeutic benefits of alternative complementary medicine. Also, students will learn the benefit of exercise training, sport injury, mechanical stress and injury during sport or physical activity, and prevention of sport injury through reading the related scientific journals.  The scientific supports and current development for alternative and rehabilitation sport medicine will be covered in this course.', 'This course is designed to discuss the differences between alternative complementary medicine and current western medicine.  For example, the traditional Chinese medicine and herb medicine have already been gradually accepted, and we will guide students to read and search current scientific literatures that support the therapeutic benefits of alternative complementary medicine. Also, students will learn the benefit of exercise training, sport injury, mechanical stress and injury during sport or physical activity, and prevention of sport injury through reading the related scientific journals.  The scientific supports and current development for alternative and rehabilitation sport medicine will be covered in this course.', '1146', '6801Z141', '680Q12', '運國碩12', '11,469,098'),
(8, '8', '1131', '', '308600161011A0', '30860', '161', '1', 1, 0, '專題研究', 'Independent Study', '賴世烱,周定衡', 2, 2, 0, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '1', '\"修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. \n2.不開放跨校選課  open for cross-registration with students from other schools. \"\n', 'The aim of this course is to help students establish research capability in preparing the related issue of master dissertation. The course teaches students how to present a well-conducted dissertation with systematically research approaches and related references, and how to propose a research proposal. Students will be able to apply research knowledge through assignments. Students enrolling this class are expected to make progress reports and have discussion with the advisor in order to reach the goal of independent study.', 'The aim of this course is to help students establish research capability in preparing the related issue of master dissertation. The course teaches students how to present a well-conducted dissertation with systematically research approaches and related references, and how to propose a research proposal. Students will be able to apply research knowledge through assignments. Students enrolling this class are expected to make progress reports and have discussion with the advisor in order to reach the goal of independent study.', '0', '6801Q051', '680211', '國際運一', '4,641,190'),
(9, '9', '1131', '林懿苑', '30860100000000 ', '30860', '624', '1', 2, 21, '統計資料管理與分析策略', 'Data Management and Statistical Analysis', '林懿苑,林莉如', 3, 2, 1, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F603', '2', '5,6,7', '\"修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. \n2.開放跨校選課  open for cross-registration with students from other schools. \n3.可選學生為國際運動科學外國學生專班一年級生、外系國際碩士班學生、全校國內碩士班學生 Eligible students include first-year students of the International Sport Science Master\'s Program, international master\'s program students from other departments, and all domestic master\'s program students in the university.\"\n修課限制：全英語授課', 'The objective of this course is to provide students with practical applications of bio-statistical methods by running the SPSS statistical software. Two sample data (depression data and factor analysis data) in the health related agendas will be demonstrated.', 'The objective of this course is to provide students with practical applications of bio-statistical methods by running the SPSS statistical software. Two sample data (depression data and factor analysis data) in the health related agendas will be demonstrated.', '808', '6802Z041', '680R21', '運國碩21', '8,089,098'),
(10, '10', '1131', '', '308600300012A0', '30860', '300', '1', 2, 0, '碩士論文', 'Master Thesis', '廖翊宏', 1, 1, 0, 6.00, '全18週', 6.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '2', '\"修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. \n2.不開放跨校選課  open for cross-registration with students from other schools. \"\n修課限制：全英語授課', 'A research-based dissertation course, which offers students the opportunity to work on a comprehensive, individual project of genetic counseling. Topic to be agreed in consultation with a supervisor. The project will be of suitable complexity for results to be published for an expert audience.', 'A research-based dissertation course, which offers students the opportunity to work on a comprehensive, individual project of genetic counseling. Topic to be agreed in consultation with a supervisor. The project will be of suitable complexity for results to be published for an expert audience.', '0', '6802Q011', '680221', '國際運二', '469'),
(11, '11', '1131', '郭瓈灧', '33140200000000 ', '33140', '1786', '1', 1, 10, '心理健康與生活：癒上新鮮人', 'Mental Health and living: Healing factors that students should know', '郭瓈灧,陳伯瑋', 57, 11, 46, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F412', '4', '6,7', '修課限制：\n1.本系四技一般生一、二年級。\n2.限60人。', '本課程為高中與大學間的銜間課程，對於以培養生死關懷與健康心理諮商之科系宗旨，技高端並無與本系對應的科系，且本系為國內少有之特色科系。為培養進入本系之新鮮人能對本系有認同感，能從108課網的素養教育，到具有科系特色之專業學習，產生學習遷移之效果，故從專業發展、團體歷程學習與癒花園場域服務，三個方向設計本課程，以培養大一新鮮人之專業認同與助人工作之能力。', 'This course is an articulative course between high school and university. For the purpose of the department to cultivate life and death care and health psychological coun-seling, there is no department corresponding to this department at the high school, and this department is a rare department in Taiwan. In order to cultivate new people who enter the department to have a sense of identity with the department, and from the literacy edu-cation of the 2019 Master Framework for the 12-year Basic Education Curriculum Guide-lines to the professional learning with the characteristics of the department, the instructor want to produce the effect of learning transfer among freshman. This course is designed from the professional development, group process learning and Healing Garden service. The purpose of this course is designed to cultivate the professional identity of freshmen and the ability to help others in their work.', '8355', '4671Z341', '467A10', '生日四10', '83,559,895'),
(12, '12', '1131', '葉明理', '33140100000000 ', '33140', '1430', '1', 1, 10, '動物輔助治療理論與實務', 'Primary Application of Animal Assisted Therapy', '葉明理', 42, 8, 34, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F412', '4', '8,9', '修課限制：\n1.本系四技一般生、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、學士後、本所(本國生)、外所(本國生)、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校1名。\n2.限60人(含跨校1人、跨系5人)。', '本課程旨在建構學生參與專業動物輔助治療活動的基本知能。課程內容由動物輔助治療基本概念出發，帶領學生經歷個案評估、方案設計、與成果評值等方案規劃與執行的過程。並藉由課堂講授、討論、影片研討、實作體驗學習之活動，建構學生具備有動物輔助治療助理員能力。', 'This course is to establish students the basic abilities for attending animal assisted therapy activities. The contents include animal assisted therapy concepts, case assessment, program design, and evaluation. The teaching activities include lectures, group discussions, documentary films discussion, and on-site practice, etc. Students are expected to be initiated their knowledge and skills as animal assisted therapy assistants.', '872', '4671Z331', '467A10', '生日四10', '872'),
(13, '13', '1131', '鄧明宇', '331400383011A0', '33140', '383', '1', 1, 0, '人類發展學', 'Human Development', '鄧明宇', 59, 12, 47, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G403', '2', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生', '本課程旨在促使學生理解家庭如何型塑自己的發展，進而可以擴展理解他人發展的視框,作為諮商輔導的基礎。內容包含生命週期、自我價值、生命力、家庭溝通模式、家庭規條、與人連結。', 'This course aims at facilitating students to realize how his experiences in family influence his development. Based on this awareness is to build the foundation to understand and connect the others. These themes include life cycle, self-esteem, Life force, patterns of communication, family rules, connection.\r\nThrough self-awareness of personality traits and ability to communicate, understand their strengths and limitations in relationships. At the same time between learning interpersonal skills through effective communication, in order to improve the self-limitation of interpersonal communication, to achieve the establishment of relationships of healthy goodness.', '1082', '4671Q491', '467411', '生四一A ', '1082'),
(14, '14', '1131', '鄧明宇', '331400384011A0', '33140', '384', '1', 1, 0, '心理學', 'Psychology', '鄧明宇,謝亞恆,潘敏,賴世烱', 41, 11, 30, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G408', '2', '6,7,8', '修課限制：\n1.生41A單號、運41A雙號混班上課。\n2.跨域課程、院定必修。', '本課程旨在協助學生透過心理學增加對人的內在心理的認識，而增進與人接觸的興趣。內容包含生物心理學、感覺、知覺、意識、學習、記憶、思考、動機、情緒、壓力與健康，以及人格與社會心理學。期待學生可以應用心理學概念於日常生活中。', 'This course aims at helping students to increase understanding inner psychological process and to become interested in connecting people. These themes include psychobiology, sensation, perception, consciousness, learning, memory, thinking, motivation, emotion, stress and health, personality, social psychology. Expecting students could utilize psychological concept into daily life.', '1082', '4671Q501', '467411', '生四一A ', '1,082,122,912,480,460'),
(15, '15', '1131', '吳庶深', '331401074011A0', '33140', '1074', '1', 1, 0, '生命教育概論', 'Introduction to Life Education', '吳庶深', 60, 13, 47, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G403', '4', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生', '生命教育主要是引導學生從觀察與分享對生、老、死之感受的過程中，體會生命的意義及存在的價值，進而培養尊重和珍惜生命的情懷。本課程透過討論，引導學生探討自我悅納、關心家庭、熱愛他人、尊重大自然及探索生命的意義，建立積極正向的人生觀，發現生命的幸福。', 'This course proposes students can think and reflect the issues on life , explore the meaning of life in thinking about man’s conditions in the life world, issues on destiny、love、knowledge、character、art、religion、dying and death etc. \r\n The expectation of this course try to help students have positive recognition and attitude on life by way of many lectures and discussions.', '1906', '4671Q511', '467411', '生四一A ', '1906'),
(16, '16', '1131', '劉純和', '331400213011A0', '33140', '213', '1', 1, 0, '資訊素養與網路運用', 'Information Literacy and Network Application', '劉純和', 36, 11, 25, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F602', '5', '8,9', '1.第二階段加退選，開放修習「資訊素養與網路運用」課程之學生互相跨班選課。2.重修生請自第二階段開放選課。全部網路選課，無紙本加選。3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '本課程為電腦之基礎課程，主要培育學生資訊素養，以具備適當資訊應用能力。課程內容除強化電腦基本概念、作業系統與文書處理軟體應用能力外，並包含網路觀念、網路應用、網路安全、資訊倫理，與智慧財產權。', 'This course is a basic course to educate students to have enough knowledge about information literacy and network application. The course will include the basic concept of computers, operating systems, office application software, network applications, information security, and intellectual property concepts.', '9907', '4671F501', '467411', '生四一A ', '9907'),
(17, '17', '1131', '陳伯瑋', '331401075011A0', '33140', '1075', '1', 1, 0, '殯葬生死觀', 'Thanatology and Funeral', '陳伯瑋,曾煥棠,范俊銘', 64, 20, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G403', '2', '1,2', '修課限制：\n1.跨域課程。中文授課。\n2.本系四技一般生、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部。(外系5名)', '本課程旨在讓學生了解殯葬活動衍生生死的課題與觀點，包括認識相關的儀式與殯葬禮儀，其對個人及社會組織的影響。從生死學的實務與運用現況，從醫學、社會、宗教與倫理的觀點探討死亡歷程，本課程期使同學建立正向的生死觀，死亡一直都是禁忌，但是它卻是生命過程中的一部份。希望經由本課程深入淺出的安排，讓社會中的每個人能夠擁有生命尊嚴與死亡尊嚴。', 'This course proposes students can understand current research and application on life and death, explorate death trajectories from medical, social, religious and ethic perspections, recognize how death to affect personal behavior, ritual about death and its reflection on social organization. The expectation of this try to help students have positive recognition and attitude on death.', '9895', '4671Q521', '467411', '生四一A ', '989,506,030,985'),
(18, '18', '1131', '彭庭軒', '331400027011A0', '33140', '27', '1', 1, 0, '藝術文化史', 'History of Artistic Culture', '彭庭軒', 60, 11, 49, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'G407', '3', '8,9', '1.第二階段開放修習「藝術文化史/世界文明史」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。\n2.全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '透過藝術文化的類型與不同的表現形式及中西方藝術的演進與賞析，瞭解藝術的理念、內涵與歷史演變，深入探討藝術與生命、美感與生活、藝術與文化等重要議題之意義。培養學生對藝術文化有基本的認識與高度的敏感度，提升審美素養，持續自主學習的興趣。', 'Through the exploration of various types and form of art and culture, as well as the evolution and appreciation of Eastern and Western art, this course provides an understanding of the concepts, meaning and historical transformations of arts. It further delves deeply into significant topics such as art and life, aesthetics and everyday life, and art and culture. Students will acquire a foundational comprehension and heightened sensitivity of art and culture, enhance their aesthetic literacy, and foster a sustained commitment to self-directed education.', '1179', '4671F491', '467411', '生四一A ', '1179'),
(19, '19', '1131', '許均宇', '331401746011A0', '33140', '1746', '1', 1, 0, '體育-基本運動素養', 'P E-Fundamental Movement Capacities', '許均宇', 54, 10, 44, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '3', '6,7', '1.四技一年級新生，由教務處安排於入學系別之一年級原班授課。 \n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。 \n3.上課地點請洽體育室。 \n4.跨校。 ', '新生的體育教學課程設計著重在體適能的強化、健康運動概念介紹及休閒運\r\n動入門引導。主要內容包括健康體適能之心肺適能的強化，以及帶動身體協\r\n調性與強調團隊合作的籃球運動為主，期望學生不僅習得運動健康概念，也\r\n因球類運動而習得助人及團隊合作的態度。', 'The purpose of this course for freshman is emphasis on the both physical \r\nfitness and basic sport skill. Lecturers instruct the concept of sports and healthy to \r\nthe student through cardiovascular fitness and sport skill (basketball) as well as to \r\npromote the coordination of the body and the emphasis on teamwork of basketball. \r\nFreshmen not only acquire the concept of sports health, but also learn to help \r\npeople and teamwork attitude.', '9133', '4671F511', '467411', '生四一A ', '9133'),
(20, '20', '1131', '曾煥棠', '331401075011A1', '33140', '1075', '1', 1, 0, '殯葬生死觀', 'Thanatology and Funeral', '曾煥棠,陳伯瑋', 20, 3, 17, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G403', '4', '1,2', '修課限制：\n1.跨域課程。EMI全英語授課。\n2.本系四技一般生、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部。(外系5名)', '本課程旨在讓學生了解殯葬活動衍生生死的課題與觀點，包括認識相關的儀式與殯葬禮儀，其對個人及社會組織的影響。從生死學的實務與運用現況，從醫學、社會、宗教與倫理的觀點探討死亡歷程，本課程期使同學建立正向的生死觀，死亡一直都是禁忌，但是它卻是生命過程中的一部份。希望經由本課程深入淺出的安排，讓社會中的每個人能夠擁有生命尊嚴與死亡尊嚴。', 'This course proposes students can understand current research and application on life and death, explorate death trajectories from medical, social, religious and ethic perspections, recognize how death to affect personal behavior, ritual about death and its reflection on social organization. The expectation of this try to help students have positive recognition and attitude on death.', '603', '4671Q521', '467AA1', '生四一A1', '6,039,895'),
(21, '21', '1131', '鄧文章', '33140100000000 ', '33140', '1088', '1', 2, 20, '安寧療護與臨終陪伴', 'Terminal Care and Bedside Counseling', '鄧文章', 61, 17, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F414', '4', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上，限65人。', '本課程旨在幫助學生認識安寧療護的觀點與發展，及病人和家屬在臨終階段的需求，再延伸至臨終陪伴的內涵。透過課程講授、電影欣賞、資料閱讀、角色扮演、小組討論與報告等，讓學生能了解安寧療護的發展及運作，學習認識臨終病人家屬的全人層面，以及如何關懷末期病人與病家，探索反思自身經驗，並且能學習以心關懷陪伴。', 'This course aims to enable students to understand the concepts of hospice and palliative care. Through the course lectures, film shows, readings, group discussions and presentations, students can understand the phenomena of hospice and dying as well. Besides, they can explore their own experience and can learn to accompany with others.', '1901', '4672Z561', '467B20', '生日四20', '1901'),
(22, '22', '1131', '陳伯瑋', '33140000000000 ', '33140', '72', '1', 2, 20, '殯葬政策與法規', 'Funeral policy and laws', '陳伯瑋,翟子睿', 50, 13, 37, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'IB01', '1', '9,10', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上、外系二技一般生二年級以上、外系四技一般生二年級以上、外系二技進修部二年級以上，限55人(含外系5人)。', '「殯葬政策與法規」內容涵蓋殯葬政策與殯葬法規之探討分析，由於政策是法律條文設計之指導，殯葬政策部分主要在探討過去不同時期，政府為實現殯葬行政管理目的所採行的公共政策，至於現行政策規劃與法律條文設計是本學科最主要之內容，以引發學生學習動機及提升學習效果', '\"Funeral policy and laws\" covers the funeral policy and funeral laws and regulations of the analysis, because the policy is the design of the provisions of the legal provisions of the funeral policy part of the past to explore the different periods of the government to achieve the funeral administrative purposes adopted by the public policy, As for the current policy planning and legal provisions of the design is the main content of the discipline to lead students to learn motivation and improve learning outcomes.', '9895', '4672Z551', '467B20', '生日四20', '98,951,183'),
(23, '23', '1131', '陳伯瑋', '33140100000000 ', '33140', '1223', '1', 2, 20, '殯葬設施', 'Funeral Facilities', '陳伯瑋,曾煥棠', 62, 18, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'B114', '1', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上、外系二技一般生二年級以上、外系四技一般生二年級以上、外系二技進修部二年級以上、學士後，限65人(含外系5人)。', '本課程介紹台灣殯葬管理條例規範的殯葬設施與殯儀館，協助學生認識國內外殯葬的各種設施、殯葬設施的管理維護、殯葬設施規劃與改變。透過議題中心教學法教導學生從殯儀館、火化場、公墓...等設施，來了解在進行完善的殯葬服務時所會使用之殯葬週邊設施，使了解其在殯葬服務的重要性及藉以來圓滿人生最後階段的需求。除經由介紹各項設施設備的名稱與沿革外，並邀請公部門及私部門講師授課教導現今殯葬設施之管理現況與未來規劃及發展、了解殯葬設施成為鄰避衝突的因素，並透過專家與地方菁英代表的訪談或是座談會，讓學生學習殯葬設施設置造成鄰避衝突的因素、化解衝突過程以及可能的解決方法。並配合本校iLMS行動學習進行網路的資料上傳、討論與分享。', 'This course introduces Taiwan\'s funeral regulations norms funeral facilities, funeral home and abroad to help students understand the various facilities, facilities maintenance management funeral, funeral planning and changing. Teachers use iLMS learning platform for uploading network data, discuss and share opinion.', '9895', '4672Z571', '467B20', '生日四20', '98,950,603'),
(24, '24', '1131', '郭瓈灧', '33140200000000 ', '33140', '1759', '1', 2, 20, '職業重建服務導論', 'Vocational Rehabilitation Services', '郭瓈灧,辜世芳', 17, 3, 14, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G105', '4', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上，本課程學生必須至實務機構見習6週，故修課人數限30人。', '本課程旨在建立學生對職業重建服務的基本理念，促進了解職業重建服務人員應注意遵守之專業倫理與職業重建服務之各項服務資源現況，並	學習身心障礙者就業與職涯輔導，以及擔任身心障礙者就業服務員的服務內涵與服務歷程，進一步學習以工作分析與職務再設計、職場支持與輔導。因而建立職業重建的概念與身心障礙者職業重建服務內涵，培養擔任職業重建服務專業人員之核心知能，並學習應用諮商輔導相關知能於職業重建服務過程，最後能綜合所學發展自身對職業重建服務領域的專業認同與職涯選擇。', 'This course of introduction to Vocational Rehabilitation Services aims to establish students’ basic concept of vocational rehabilitation services, promote the understanding of professional ethics and vocational rehabilitation services resources. The professionals of vocational rehabilitation services should pay attention to, and learn about employment and career counseling for the disabled. The service connotation and service process of employment attendants for the physically and mentally disabled will be further studied by job analysis and job redesign, workplace support and guidance. Therefore, we establish the concept of vocational rehabilitation and the connotation of vocational rehabilitation services for the physically and mentally handicapped, cultivate the core knowledge to serve as vocational rehabilitation services professionals, and learn to apply the relevant knowledge of counseling and counseling in the career reconstruction service process. Starting from understanding the International Classification of Functional, Disability, and Health (ICF), impact of impairment, career development of people with disabilities, and vocational rehabilitation services. The students will learn intake interview, design a vocational rehabilitation plan, and implement services, and job analysis skills. Through the process, students will be more capable vocational rehabilitation professionals. Finally integrate what they have learned to develop their own career to be the professionals of vocational rehabilitation services. Promote their Professional identity and career choice in the service field.', '8355', '4672Z581', '467B20', '生日四20', '83,550,725'),
(25, '25', '1131', '吳庶深', '331401072012A0', '33140', '1072', '1', 2, 0, '社會心理學', 'Introduction to Social Psychology', '吳庶深', 75, 24, 51, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F414', '4', '8,9', '修課限制：\n1.跨域課程。\n2.本系四技一般生二年級以上、外系二技一般生二年級、外系四技一般生二年級以上、外系二技進修部二年級以上。(外系7名，共75名)', '透過理論與重要概念的介紹，引領學生進入社會心理學領域之中，藉由社會心理學的知識框架，協助學生得以重新檢視人際、生活、社會等各層面的事件，其所隱含的心理學意義，進而催化教學目標之達成。', 'Social psychology is the scientific study of how individuals think, feel, and behave in a social context. Let’s look at key issues of Social Psychology: social perception, social influence, social relations, applying social psychology (i.e. law, business and health).', '1906', '4672Q511', '467421', '生四二A ', '1906'),
(26, '26', '1131', '郭瓈灧', '331401080012A0', '33140', '1080', '1', 2, 0, '諮商與輔導概論', 'Introduction to Counseling', '郭瓈灧', 71, 21, 50, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F302', '3', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上', '本課程旨於提供初學諮商輔導學生們相關理論與技術，認識諮商輔導工作內涵，並且了解諮商輔導工作基本的運用的理論與實務。', 'This course is aimed to provide the knowledge of counseling theory and technical to the students who getting started with the learning of counseling. Besides, they can learn some counseling skill through the lesson.', '8355', '4672Q531', '467421', '生四二A ', '8355'),
(27, '27', '1131', '陳伯瑋', '331401191012A0', '33140', '1191', '1', 2, 0, '殯葬服務與管理', 'Funeral services and management', '陳伯瑋,曾煥棠,翟子睿', 66, 18, 48, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F301', '1', '1,2', '修課限制：\n1.跨域課程。\n2.本系四技一般生二年級以上。\n3.外系二技一般生二年級、外系四技一般生二年級以上、外系二技進修部二年級以上。(外系共5名)', '本課程旨在使學生能釐清對殯葬產業的認識與觀念，具備基本管理學知識，了解殯葬管理之範疇、沿革、專業知識與行政概念認知，進而應用課程內容剖析殯葬產業之經營管理生態與潛在問題等議題。因此，在教師督導協助下，學生要能針對殯葬管理議題擬定問題解讀、分析、研判與立論等書面架構，並透過相關殯葬從業之影片觀賞和企業機構之實際參訪觀摩及文獻資料的蒐集分析，協助滿足學習者的學習需求或解決學習上的問題。', 'After studying of the course, students will be able to have the knowledge about funeral management. Under the assistance of supervisors, students will learn to interpret funeral and interment’s subjects of debate.', '9895', '4672Q551', '467421', '生四二A ', '989,506,031,183'),
(28, '28', '1131', '鄧文章', '331401119012A0', '33140', '1119', '1', 2, 0, '變態心理學', 'Abnormal Psychology', '鄧文章', 69, 19, 50, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F301', '2', '6,7', '修課限制：\n1.本系四技一般生二年級以上。\n2.外系二技一般生二年級以上、外系四技一般生二年級以上、外系二技進修部二年級以上。(外系共3名)\n3.跨校(共3名)。', '變態心理學研究教學目的，乃針對目前臨床心理精神醫學實務中之重要議題做系統性的探討。藉由課室教學、小組討論、影片賞析、臨床實例、個別報告、方式，瞭解心理異常個案的理論基礎、治療實務及相關研究議題。', 'The course provides an opportunity for students to utilize theories and  skills that they have learned in abnormal psychology class in order to strengthen their knowledge of clinical diagnosis. Under supervision, students will get hands on experiences in designing abnormal psychology research. During the sessions, trainees will learn how to effectively define the client’s Mental Status and thus develop skills needed for further counseling or referring.', '1901', '4672Q541', '467421', '生四二A ', '1901'),
(29, '29', '1131', '林維芬', '331401728012A0', '33140', '1728', '1', 2, 0, '體育-現代舞', 'PE- Modern dance', '林維芬', 50, 7, 43, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '1', '6,7', '1. 第一階段志願選，僅由生四二A、運四二A互相跨班選課。\n2. 第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。\n3. 上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。\n4.跨校。', '在舞蹈的領域中，現代舞強調「探索」與「醒思」這\r\n兩項精神，人體的自我探索、人在時間與空間中的醒思，因此本課程著重於身體\r\n運作的認知與探索，課程目標強調經由肢體活動做身體能力的察覺與開發。課程\r\n內容以漸進的練習原則，探索累積學習者的身體經驗。', 'Among all dancing areas, modern dance emphasizes on both “exploration” \r\nand “disillusion” spirits, self-exploring on human body, consciousness about \r\nhuman within time and space. Therefore, this course emphasizes on \r\nrecognition and discovery of body operation, and the curricular goal stresses \r\non the awareness and development of body competence through body \r\nactivities. The course content is to explore the body experiences of \r\ncumulative learners by proper sequential practices.', '653', '4672F141', '467421', '生四二A ', '653'),
(30, '30', '1131', '陳伯瑋', '331401078012A1', '33140', '1078', '1', 2, 0, '人文與社會科學統計', 'Statistics for Humanities and Social Science', '陳伯瑋', 31, 6, 25, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S103', '2', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級，不開放重修生修課。', '介紹統計學的各項基本概念、資料檢核與統計特徵量、機率理論與機率分配、抽樣與抽樣分配、估計與檢定、卡方檢定、平均數差異相關、相關係數種類、線性迴歸分析、單因子變異數分析等.', 'This course includes such topics as the basic concepts of statistics, data validation and distribution of probability, probability theory and statistical characteristics, sampling and the sampling distribution, interval estimation, χ square estimation, average differences relation, types of correlation coefficients, linear regression analysis, path analysis, single-factor analysis of variance.', '9895', '4672Q521', '467BA1', '生四二A1', '9895'),
(31, '31', '1131', '陳伯瑋', '331401078012A2', '33140', '1078', '1', 2, 0, '人文與社會科學統計', 'Statistics for Humanities and Social Science', '陳伯瑋', 34, 12, 22, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B210', '3', '1,2', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上，此班僅限重修生修課。', '介紹統計學的各項基本概念、資料檢核與統計特徵量、機率理論與機率分配、抽樣與抽樣分配、估計與檢定、卡方檢定、平均數差異相關、相關係數種類、線性迴歸分析、單因子變異數分析等.', 'This course includes such topics as the basic concepts of statistics, data validation and distribution of probability, probability theory and statistical characteristics, sampling and the sampling distribution, interval estimation, χ square estimation, average differences relation, types of correlation coefficients, linear regression analysis, path analysis, single-factor analysis of variance.', '9895', '4672Q521', '467BA2', '生四二A2', '9895'),
(32, '32', '1131', '林育陞', '33140000000000 ', '33140', '363', '1', 3, 30, '藝術治療概論', 'The Introduction of Art Therapy', '林育陞', 35, 3, 32, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G403', '4', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級，限36人。', '本課程主要在介紹藝術治療的理論與實務，並且針對藝術治療如何應用於各年齡層之個案群中，進行深入的探討和研究。本課程預計分為十四個單元講授，分別介紹藝術治療的簡史、藝術治療在歐美及台灣的發展、不同的藝術治療取向、「表達性治療連續系統」(ETC)和「媒材可變特性」(MDV) 理論，了解這些理論與表達性藝術治療技法間的關係，並且透過參與藝療活動，學習和體驗藝術治療的精神，同時探討藝術治療在悲傷輔導、創傷治療、情緒障礙和行為問題之個案上的臨床運用。此課程以﹙1﹚研究著作之研讀﹙2﹚相關簡報之呈現與討論（3）表達性藝療活動之參與（４）個別和團體研究報告等方式進行，提供學生思考空間，並作為檢驗學習效果之參考。', 'Through the literature review, case studies and experiential art activities, this course will assist students in understanding the theories and practices in art therapy, as well as the connection between the arts and human life while gaining knowledge on how art can be used in the field of psychotherapy, life/death education, and grief counseling as a helpful tool to maintain one’s physical and mental health.', '1202', '4673Z691', '467C30', '生日四30', '1202'),
(33, '33', '1131', '李佩怡', '33140100000000 ', '33140', '1126', '1', 3, 31, '意義治療概論', 'Logotherapy', '李佩怡', 55, 11, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F409', '5', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上，限60人。', '幫助學生瞭解生命意義與身心靈健康的密切關係，從意義治療學的角度切入，探討安頓生命的道理，引導學生思考並實踐攸關個人成長及身心靈健康的重要課題。', 'The therapeutic component of Logotherapy follows the Judeo-Christian traditions, being open to anyone, and in this way ecumenical. In essence, Logotherapy aims at helping to find meaning and purpose in any life situation, actualizing the universal values set forth in the Ten Commandments and the Beatitudes. It is through finding meaning and purpose in suffering that healing and reconciliation can be attained and psychopathological symptoms can be relieved.', '335', '4673Z671', '467C31', '生日四31', '335'),
(34, '34', '1131', '陳伯瑋', '33140100000000 ', '33140', '1187', '1', 3, 32, '殯葬文書', 'The Professional Competence and Skills of Funeral Director and practice', '陳伯瑋,翟子睿,范俊銘', 29, 7, 22, 2.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'IB01', '1', '6,7,8', '修課限制：\n1.本系四技一般生三年級以上、外系四技一般生三年級以上、外系二技進修部三年級，限45人(含外系5人)。\n2.維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）。', '本課程從我國殯葬文書發展沿革於喪葬活動與司儀角色定位與功能相關論述，協助學生認識殯葬文書的規範與書寫，司儀禮生技巧等。本課程分為殯葬文書、殯葬司儀兩部分，課程內容概述如下：\r\n一、殯葬文書：\r\n  (一)介紹殯葬禮儀與文書的關係、古代殯葬文書的體類、當代殯葬文書的體類、訃文、碑文、銘文、祭文、輓聯等殯葬文書相關知能。。\r\n  (二)訃聞語法書寫技巧\r\n  (三)教導如何使用實用文書表格(治喪時程總表、作七時程表、出殯奠禮時程表、治喪人員分工表、出殯路線計車隊聯繫表)。\r\n二、殯葬司儀：\r\n  (一)介紹喪禮流程。 \r\n  (二)殯葬司儀之專業技能，規劃奠禮流程並主持家奠及公奠禮應具備之專業知能。\r\n  (三)覆旗暨民俗儀節。', 'Copy modern funeral instrument classes, make a practical instrument of modern funeral, funeral service the customs process, forward thinking on training, establish a correct sequence of funeral ideas, and professional skills training through the funeral ceremonies, give students a basic funeral knowledge and practice skills.', '9895', '4673Z681', '467C32', '生日四32', '989,511,830,985'),
(35, '35', '1131', '辜世芳', '33140200000000 ', '33140', '1760', '1', 3, 33, '職業重建個案管理服務導論', 'Career service and case management of the disabilities', '辜世芳,簡明山', 21, 1, 20, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G307', '1', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上，限45人。', '本科目之教學設計為橫向整合該系之心理相關科目，包括：發展心理學、諮商輔導實務與技術、悲傷輔導概論、心理測驗與衡鑑、生命回顧與老人關懷等科目。\r\n本科目之教學設計為縱向整合該系之醫療諮商與職業重建輔導領域相關科目，包括：身心障礙者特質與發展、復健諮商、諮商輔導實務與技術、職業重建服務導論、生死與諮商工作實習等課程。', 'The course aims to enhance students’ knowledge of a vocational rehabilitation counselor and employment specialist. Students will be able to analyze the employment barriers, develop a suitable services plan and implement the plan.', '725', '4673Z701', '467C33', '生日四33', '7,251,187'),
(36, '36', '1131', '鄧明宇', '331401089013A0', '33140', '1089', '1', 3, 0, '自殺與預防概論', 'Suicide and Prevention Studies', '鄧明宇', 59, 11, 48, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F414', '3', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上、本所5名、外系2名。', '本課程旨在使學生充分認識人類自殺行為的各個層面的相關學問，包括醫學、心理學、社會學、倫理學、文化人類學等；了解自殺前、中以及自殺後的問題，並傳授與自殺防治所需要之專業知識與技能，能夠應用課程設計進行實務操作。因此，在教師督導協助下，學生要能針對服務對象的問題及需求而擬定發展專題或專案（教學教案或輔導計劃），並從實際進行活動的演練中，設計教學或輔導成效評量以協助滿足學習者的學習需求或解決學習上的問題。', 'This course provides students with knowledge about suicide and prevention. The major elements include the theory of suicide, definition of suicide and related factor, influence,  suicidal preventing strategy. Students are required to identify and establish high risk and sigh of suicide, suicidal family care , constructs suicidal preventing strategy and discussed in this class.', '1082', '4673Q401', '467431', '生四三Ａ', '1082'),
(37, '37', '1131', '吳庶深', '331400031013A0', '33140', '31', '1', 3, 0, '哲學與人生', 'Philosophy and Life', '吳庶深', 47, 11, 36, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F408', '3', '3,4', '1.第二階段開放修習「哲學與人生/邏輯概論」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。\n2.全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '「哲學與人生」是對「人的生命」所作的「哲學反省」。人，作為自然的、社會的、歷史的存在，在他所生活的世界中，面臨著繁複多樣、瞬息萬變的問題：處境、命運、愛情、知識、道德、藝術、宗教、臨終與死亡……其中有些問題事實上已經深深困擾著我們，另外一些則伺機突襲，在我們還來不及準備的時候，就被迫面對。生命的意義究竟是什麼？本課程嘗試以深入淺出的討論，藉由過去、當代人物的所感、所思，促進學習者進一步反省自我生命之種種。', 'Philosophy and Life is as a philosophical reflective thinking for the life.\r\nHuman beings, as natural, social and historical beings, face a great many complex varied and fast changing problems in the life-world, for example, love, destiny, knowledge, morality, art, religion, dying, and moreover the death so on.... Actually some of them have deeply perplexed us, while others watch for their chances to attack there would leave no time for covering our ears and we are merely compelled to confront with them. After all, what does Life mean?\r\nWhereas this course tries to take up by the way a kind of discussion in explaining the profound in simple terms, and in making use of whatever in history, or the present age somebody\'s feeling and thinking, in order to promote the students to question themselves more about, and reflect further on all sorts of life-self.', '1906', '4673F231', '467431', '生四三Ａ', '1906'),
(38, '38', '1131', '鄧文章', '331401079013A0', '33140', '1079', '1', 3, 0, '家庭會談與家族治療概論', 'Family Interview and Family Therapy', '鄧文章', 58, 11, 47, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F414', '2', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大三以上', '本科目旨在使學生了解家庭的本質，協助學生了解家庭互動發展過程。包括兩性角色、選擇伴侶、婚姻關係與適應、夫妻溝通、親子溝通、工作與家庭、家庭危機處理、分居、離婚與段婚、單身、婚姻諮商等。並認識家庭會談的理論與實務，現代與後現代家族治療學派的策略和技巧，以便能以系統觀點去理解危機如何襯托在家庭背景中產生；又跟家庭系統產生什麼交互作用與影響，能有效運用會談策略。', 'This course is designed to assist students acquiring expertise about family interview and family therapy. In this course, students could understand the most important family therapy theories, and learn the practical skills. Students are expected to write an evaluation for their own family, and cooperate to write a therapy plan for special family. Several practices would be organized.', '1901', '4673Q411', '467431', '生四三Ａ', '1901'),
(39, '39', '1131', '李佩怡', '331401085013A0', '33140', '1085', '1', 3, 0, '悲傷輔導實務與技術', 'Practice and techniques of Grief Counseling', '李佩怡', 58, 11, 47, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F414', '2', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上', '本課程目標在於提供學生了解悲傷輔導理論與技術的應用，特別以體驗式學習和問題導向式學習(Problem based learning, PBL)兩者並進的方式，在知識面要求學生由產生問題意識到能蒐集資料、進行閱讀，回答問題，以學習悲傷輔導的知能；在應用技能面，則是協助學生由自身失落經驗起步，按著課程進度逐步對自身的悲傷經驗有更深的了解和整理，乃至於可以推己及人，將學習到的經驗應用於協助喪親者。', 'The course will lead students to apply basic theories of loss, grief and mourning to help grieving people . Through class discussions, experiential activities, and case formulation, students will learn: how people impact by losses, different perspectives of grief work, and techniques of helping grieving people. Teacher would lead most exercises to help students learn from their experiences and let students practice skills by small groups. Hopefully, students will prepare themselves to be helpers in the future.', '335', '4673Q381', '467431', '生四三Ａ', '335'),
(40, '40', '1131', '李玉嬋', '331401087013A0', '33140', '1087', '1', 3, 0, '醫療場域心理諮商', 'Health counseling in medical setting', '李玉嬋', 56, 10, 46, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F414', '4', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上', '本課程旨在讓學生了解醫療場域提供心理諮商的範疇，瞭解病患的遭受重大傷病的衝擊與影響，及其心理上如何啟動抗壓因應之機制；然後醫療場域提供心理諮商服務之實際運作狀況及其理論和方法之探討，進而培養學生面對醫療領域中各種健康問題衝擊而有心理壓力需求時，具備問題分析和諮商處遇能力，瞭解如何提供協助病患及其家屬提昇因應生病難題的適應力，也包括協助社區民眾心理健康促進以改善生活品質，也是擴大的醫療場域心理諮商服務範疇。', 'The course aims to enhance students’ knowledge of medical counseling. Students will be able to analyze the psychological problem of patients and make proper plans of counseling intervention. Furthermore, students will learn to assist patients to coping with the difficulties of chronic disease and assist people to promote their health and quality of life.', '606', '4673Q391', '467431', '生四三Ａ', '606'),
(41, '41', '1131', '林進隆', '331401717013A0', '33140', '1717', '1', 3, 0, '體育-桌球3', 'PE-Table Tennis3', '林進隆', 49, 14, 35, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '5', '3,4', '1.第一階段志願選，僅由語四三A、生四三A互相跨班選課。\n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。\n3.上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。\n4.跨校。', '此課程是先學習與養成良好的基本技術與接發球技術後\r\n再加強雙打戰術理論與應用。學習「雙打戰術理論模式」就是以理論為基礎，以提升雙\r\n打戰術觀念。而雙打注重的是技術與兩位球員搭配之默契並運用各種戰術以全面、快速、\r\n變化之打法獲得有效之成果或在比賽中贏取勝利。', 'In this course, a player should learn and cultivate good basic skills and the \r\nskills in receiving and serving the ball first, and then reinforce the theory and \r\napplications of doubles tactics. To learn “the model of doubles tactics theory” \r\nis to enhance the concept of doubles tactics based on theories. In doubles, the \r\nskills and the unspoken consensus of cooperation between the two players \r\nare emphasized; also, various kinds of tactics are applied, so as to use \r\ncomprehensive, rapid and variable playing skills to obtain effective results or \r\ntriumph.', '9146', '4673F241', '467431', '生四三Ａ', '9146'),
(42, '42', '1131', '鄧文章', '331401082014A0', '33140', '1082', '1', 4, 0, '生死與諮商工作實習', 'Practicum in Counseling', '鄧文章,李佩怡,吳庶深,葉明理,郭瓈灧,鄧明宇,陳伯瑋,曾煥棠,辜世芳', 46, 12, 34, 9.00, '全18週', 27.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '1', '1,2,3,4,6,7,8,9', '修課限制：\n1.實習課程、本系四技一般生四年級、暑假提前開課113/7/1-114/1/17，不開放選課。\n2.維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）。', '本課程是針對生死與健康心理諮商學系大學部學生所設計，目的乃在於結合本系所專業學科與發展特色，透過學生前往諮商輔導相關機構實務實習與工作參與之過程，提供學生與相關專業機構接觸之機會，緊密結合「教育、學習、產業」三方互動交流，以期達到提升實務諮商輔導相業知能目標。', 'This course is designed for undergraduate students majoring in Thanatology and Health Counseling. This course combined professional subjects and career training of our department is aimed for student career development. Through the internship and working involvement in relevant counseling facilities, Students have more chance to contact different professional institutes. Our goal is to enhance the practical and professional counseling knowledge and skill for our students via connecting “Education, Learning, Industry” 3 dimensions firmly.', '1901', '4674Q151', '467441', '生四四Ａ', '190,103,351,906,087,000,000,000,000,000,000,000'),
