(204, '195', '1131', '陳素秋', '211200592011C0', '21120', '592', '1', 1, 0, '生物統計學與實驗(一)', 'Biostatistics and Lab I', '陳素秋', 47, 8, 39, 2.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B210', '1', '8,9,10', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、學士後、跨校', '本課程傳授學生基本的生物統計學(一)原理及其電腦 Excel 之示範/操作，佐加計算機之示範計算，以使學生具備從事健康事業管理相關工作與初步電腦統計函數及簡單統計繪圖之操作實務。課程內容包括生物統計學概念、敘述統計學、機率概論、機率分布(Binomial, Normal, …)、抽樣分布、推論統計學(估計)，與其相關電腦 Excel 實作。', 'The objective of this course is to provide students with basic theories of Biostatistics I and simple calculation of Excel functions as well as simple figures drawing, a tool for the work in the health related fields. Subjects taught in this course include (1) basic concepts of Biostatistics I, (2) descriptive Statistics, (3) basic probability concepts, (4) probability distributions (Binomial, Normal, …), (5) sampling distributions, (6) inferential Statistics: estimation, (7) related practice by Excel.', '520', '2231Q611', '223213', '健二一C ', '520'),
(205, '196', '1131', '邱尚志', '211200033011C0', '21120', '33', '1', 1, 0, '服務學習', 'Service Learning', '邱尚志', 48, 7, 41, 0.00, '全18週', 1.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F403', '3', '5', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、學士後、跨校', '本課程設計旨在協助學生培養服務的精神，藉由至服務機構提供服務，落實課堂所學之服務知識與理念，並進而從服務中學習、瞭解服務於社區之重要性與體驗服務之意義，培養正向的服務態度，以期自我省思、瞭解自我進而促進自我成長與肯定生命價值。', 'This course is provided to introduce the basic concepts of volunteer, and help the students with fundamental understanding in non-profit organization (NPO). The class will be guided by different instructions of lecture, group discussion, homework and test', '9119', '2231Q571', '223213', '健二一C ', '9119'),
(206, '197', '1131', '陳紹韻', '211200029011C0', '21120', '29', '1', 1, 0, '哲學與宗教', 'Philosophy and Religion', '陳紹韻', 46, 7, 39, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F408', '5', '3,4', '1.第二階段開放修習「當代藝術導論/哲學與宗教/世界文明史/邏輯概論」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。\n2.全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '本課程以直向生命與橫向生命為主軸，引導學子正確的認識哲學、了解宗教，並將重心放在各哲學理論與宗教義理對生命的看法上，使哲學與宗教和人生「生、老、病、死」與「我、人、事、物」等不同面向相連結，探究人的特性與價值、人生的欲望與煩惱、對錯與善惡、真善美聖等問題，再融入各種人生觀、價值觀、知識論、倫理學、道德觀、宗教觀、修行觀等，使知、情、意、行能夠融為一體，藉以培養學生自我檢視與自我成長的態度，深入且多元的思考人生種種經驗與體會，進而建立良好的哲學思惟與宗教觀念，訂立適切且自他兩利的人生目標，展開幸福健康的生命旅程。', 'This course is designed according to the vertical and the horizontal aspects of life. Guide students to understand the fundamental content of philosophy and religion, and focus on the various philosophical theories and religious teachings. \"Birth, aging, sickness and death\" and \"oneself, humans, and subjects around one’s life\" will be linked together in this course. The characteristics and values of human beings, human\'s desires and troubles, right and wrong, good and evil, and etc. will be explored. The attitudes on life, values, knowledge, ethics, morality, religion and life and death will be examined. For cultivating positive and active concept, students have to integrate his/her knowledge, feelings, and intentions. May they be happy and healthy and establish a good philosophical contemplation and religious reflection, and in an appropriate direction of life which profits both themselves and other lives through the learning of this course', '9976', '2231F581', '223213', '健二一C ', '9976'),
(207, '198', '1131', '陳楚杰', '211200083011C0', '21120', '83', '1', 1, 0, '健康照護管理學', 'Healthcare Organizational Management', '陳楚杰', 49, 8, 41, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F403', '3', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、學士後、跨校', '本課程旨在協助學生獲得有關我國保健及醫療照護體系(Health Care System)內有關機構之組織及管理的基本知識與技能，及其在醫療相關部門管理之應用。課程內容以管理程序為架構，範圍從管理的簡介開始，再依循管理的過程分別介紹健康照護管理有關的主題－醫療體系與環境、規劃、組織、人力資源管理、領導與激勵、品管，風險管理等之理論與實務層面。以期學生由此能對健康照護管理有一基本的但完整的認識，以開發自己的管理潛能。', 'The purpose of this course is to assist the student with nursing experiences to gain the knowledge and skills of the organization and management, in turn, and to be able to apply those to healthcare management. Topics include：The concept of “Customer-Focu', '723', '2231Q601', '223213', '健二一C ', '723'),
(208, '199', '1131', '黃三翁', '211200036011C0', '21120', '36', '1', 1, 0, '健康經濟學', 'Health Economics', '黃三翁', 49, 7, 42, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F403', '3', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、學士後、跨校', '本課程乃醫療經濟學之基礎課程，主要內容為個體經濟學基本理論及分析工具的介紹，並藉由個體經濟學之理論及工具，對健康及醫療給付行為之需求、供給、成本控制及其他重要課題進行分析與解釋。', 'The course is a basic course for Health Economics, the essential contents of the course includes two parts; The first part introduces the basic theories for Microeconomics and analytic instruments .The second part analyses and explains the demand, supply,', '1225', '2231Q591', '223213', '健二一C ', '1225'),
(209, '200', '1131', '譚漢儒', '211200035011C0', '21120', '35', '1', 1, 0, '組織行為學', 'Organizational Behavior', '譚漢儒', 53, 8, 45, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F412', '4', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、學士後、跨校', '本課程將從組織之定義及組織行為之定義開始討論組織行為在管理層面之重要性，課程會包括組織行為全球觀點、組織行為之行程與差異、組織之激勵、個體決策、工作團對與溝通領導等組織研究領域相關重點。課程會以講授、活動與戶外教學來啟發同學在組織行為學上的概念及興趣。', 'The main objective of this course is to introduce the concept of Organizational Behavior (OB), such as the definition of OB and why this subject is important to enterprise. Second, the course attempts to stimulate students’ interest in the area of OB, so', '1143', '2231Q581', '223213', '健二一C ', '1143'),
(210, '201', '1131', '李威侃', '211200002011C0', '21120', '2', '1', 1, 0, '進階國文', 'Advanced Chinese Literature', '李威侃', 45, 9, 36, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F409', '5', '1,2', '1.第二階段加退選僅由全校21生互相跨班選課。\n2.第三階段加退選開放系外及重修生選課。\n3.主題:孫子兵法\n', '本課程藉由古典文學（散文、詩詞歌賦、傳奇、戲劇）、中國哲學、現代文學（新詩、散文、小說）及兒童文學之專題選讀，指導學生研讀文學典籍及賞析的方法，使學生能掌握先賢之生命智慧與藝術心靈，了解中國學術源流及古今文學的精義，從而體認傳統文化的歷史傳承之責任。', 'The main purpose of this course is to increase students’ capabilities of appreciating literary works and expressing verbally.  Through studies of representative works of classic and modern Chinese literature, students are given the opportunity to appreciate the abundant and luxuriant styles of Chinese literature.  The instructor will guide students, by teaching methods as lecturing, discussion, and self-learning, to explore the profundity and the vitality of Chinese literature and furthermore, to understand the truth, virtue, and beauty of Chinese culture.', '1063', '2231F561', '223213', '健二一C ', '1063'),
(211, '202', '1131', '曾育裕', '211200026011C0', '21120', '26', '1', 1, 0, '應用法規導論', 'Introduction of Professional Law', '曾育裕', 49, 8, 41, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F410', '2', '3,4', '1.第二階段開放修習護理/高照/醫教/助產/健管/長照/聽語「應用法規導論」課程之學生互相跨班選課。\n2.重修生請自第二階段開放選課。全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '本課程醫護法學之介紹，使學生對法律結構、法學理念及我國現行法有一整體性的認知，以奠定法學啟發基礎。從醫護正義概念出發，就醫護法規、醫護法制、護理法律責任與訴訟、醫護人員切身法律問題等，深入淺出有系統的介紹，以培養現代醫護人員正確的法律觀。並從醫護業務與法律實務的角度，點出護理人員與其他醫事人員的責任分際、臨床醫護人員與公共衛生醫護人員面臨法律問題的不同、醫病糾紛的預防與處理等，以強化醫護人員處理法律問題的能力。', 'This subject is taught by way of the introduction of the basic law to let the students to understand the whole outline of the construction of law，the virtue of the jurisprudence and the  present law in Taiwan.  It begins as the teaching of the concept of the professional justice and is succeeded by introducing the medical and nursing law，the institution of the professional law，the responsibility and litigation as well as the professional liability of the member of professional society to ensure the students to know the exact concept of the law and to develop problem-solving abilities .', '305', '2231F571', '223213', '健二一C ', '305'),
(212, '203', '1131', '何嘉玲', '211201769011C0', '21120', '1769', '1', 1, 0, '環境永續與資訊科學', 'Environmental Sustainability and Information Science', '何嘉玲,林和駿', 48, 7, 41, 2.00, '第1~16週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'S103,F402', '2', '1,1,2,2', '1.第二階段加退選，開放修習「環境教育/電腦軟體整合應用/環境永續與資訊科學」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。 2.全部網路選課，無紙本加選。 3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。1-8週上課地點及第9-16週上課地點。電腦教室:前八周S103', '本課程為環境永續發展與資訊科學之教學內容，主要在闡述環境永續發展的重要性，提昇學生永續發展的覺知，結合資訊科技的應用，以具備適當資訊應用的能力，培養維護環境永續的行動技能。\r\n課程內容涵蓋環境倫理、環境變遷與防災、節能減碳與能源管理、生態保育、電腦程式設計、結合環境教育主題之資訊應用等主題。教學策略運用做中學、在真實的情境中體驗、合作學習法、運用感官學習、探索環境與結合電腦軟體應用等議題。', 'This course focuses on the importance of sustainable environmental development and information science. By integrating the application of information technology, this course aims to explain the importance of sustainable environmental development and to raise students\' awareness of sustainable development in order to equip students with the ability to apply appropriate information technology and to develop the skills to maintain environmental sustainability.\r\n\r\nThe course covers topics such as environmental ethics, environmental change and disaster prevention, energy conservation and energy management, ecological conservation, computer programming, and information application integrated with environmental education themes. Teaching strategies include learning by doing, experiencing in real-life situations, cooperative learning methods, using sensory learning, exploring the environment, and integrating computer software applications.', '791', '2231F551', '223213', '健二一C ', '7,910,617'),
(213, '204', '1131', '趙曜', '211201722011C0', '21120', '1722', '1', 1, 0, '體育-木球', 'PE- Woodball', '趙曜', 48, 7, 41, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '1', '1,2', '1.第一階段志願選，僅由全校二技一年級生互相跨班選課。\n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。\n3.上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。\n4.跨校。', '利用循序漸進的教學方式，教導學生木球的基本動作，\r\n透過對木球基本動作的熟練，進而提昇學生對木球比賽的興趣、享受木球運動的樂趣。\r\n講授木球運動的規則及比賽策略。強調運動員必須在規則範圍內做合法的競賽，透過木\r\n球運動來幫助學生守法、守分與合作的精神，並協助運動習慣的養成，期望學生能以木\r\n球運動作為終身運動', 'The content of course is to instruct students’ Woodball skill by using \r\nstep-by-step teaching method. Over the basic movement of the skilled is to \r\nenhance the students\' interest in Woodball game and enjoyment the fun of \r\nWoodball. The rules and strategies of teaching Woodball to emphasize that \r\nathletes must be legitimate competition in the scope of the rules through the \r\nsport of Woodball to help students to obey the law, be law-abiding and \r\ncooperation spirit, Therefor, students are expected to develop the habit of \r\nexercise and to choice Woodball as a lifetime of activity.', '8331', '2231F541', '223213', '健二一C ', '8331'),
(214, '205', '1131', '譚漢儒', '21120100000000 ', '21120', '1251', '1', 2, 20, '問題分析與解決', 'Problem Analysis and Solving', '譚漢儒', 50, 8, 42, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F410', '3', '3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、學士後、跨校', '本課程旨在採用健康照護機構實務案例為素材，引導學生運用問題分析與決策及專案管理的概念、技術，在課堂上分析並引導討論相關案例，期使學生在畢業前即能孰悉醫療及健康事業機構的經營管理議題，以及相關領域問題處理的實務情境，有助於學生未來職場及早適應與管理能力之發揮。', 'The purpose of the course is to provide students with organized understanding and practicing ability on problem solving and decision making in healthcare organization. Firstly, by intruding basic concepts and techniques in problem solving and decision making, to construct students with related knowledge. Secondly, by using real cases in healthcare industries, students learn from pre-class reading, assignments, and following with class discussion for these cases, to construct student with ability of problem analysis in real situation. Finally, practicing with oral presentation and written report, and discussing in classroom, to deepen the ability for adapting and developing in future workplaces.', '1143', '2232Z551', '223B20', '健日二20', '1143'),
