(216, '207', '1131', '陳巧珊', '21120200000000 ', '21120', '1840', '1', 2, 20, '營運智慧概論', 'Introduction of Business Intelligence', '劉介宇,陳巧珊', 31, 8, 23, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F410', '3', '6,7,8', '修課限制：學程課程、本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、本課程限計畫職專班生修課、限30人', '本課程將教授並建立學生能理解各式資料(結構與非結構)生成的方式與商業邏輯，並且根據分析標的，彙集營運解決方案所需之數據資料及其來源，並將之表格或系統化，同時對企業營運之生產、行銷、研發、人資、資訊、財務與策略管理系統之流程有基本概括的了解，並能夠理解流程對應之資訊工具，以從營運業務流程中，快速掌握資料蒐集管道。並且以連鎖藥局為實習場所，綜整分析連鎖藥局營運資料之特性，結合R語言進行連鎖藥局資料分析及資料視覺化，進一步分析各連鎖藥局營運優勢及劣勢、協助評估動態競爭優勢與制定中短期營運發展策略。', 'This course will teach and establish students\' ability to understand the generation methods and business logic of various data (structured and unstructured), and according to the analysis target, gather the data and sources required for operational solutions, and form or systematize them , At the same time, have a basic and general understanding of the processes of production, marketing, R&amp;D, human resources, information, financial and strategic management systems of enterprise operations, and be able to understand the information tools corresponding to the processes, so as to quickly grasp data collection from operational business processes pipeline. And take the chain pharmacy as the practice place, comprehensively analyze the characteristics of the chain pharmacy\'s operation data, combine the R language to analyze and visualize the data of the chain pharmacy, further analyze the operating advantages and disadvantages of each chain pharmacy, and assist in evaluating the dynamic competitive advantage And formulate short-to-medium-term business development strategies.', '1193', '2232Z561', '223B20', '健日二20', '5,981,193'),
