(254, '245', '1131', '李麗惠', '21140000000000 ', '21140', '124', '1', 2, 20, '程式設計', 'Introduction of Computer Programming', '李麗惠', 40, 15, 25, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'B210', '3', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、學士後、跨校、程式設計課程、學程課程', '本課程的主要教學目的是教授「程式設計概念」與「設計方法」。課程的主要內容包括「程式設計概念」、「問題解決方法」、「程式流程圖設計」、「Console-Mode程式之設計」、「Event-Driven程式之設計」、「物件導向程式設計」、及「軟體專案練習」。整個課程中，學生分為數組，各組必須完成3個軟體專案。', 'The major subject of this course is to make an introduction of the concept of programming. The teaching activities will focus on discussing the concept of problem solving, designing the program flowchart and developing programs in C#. For the most part, w', '753', '4232Z581', '423B20', '健日四20', '753'),
(255, '246', '1131', '王台欣', '21140000000000 ', '21140', '50', '1', 2, 20, '藥理學', 'Pharmacology', '王台欣', 52, 10, 42, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G105', '2', '6,7', '修課限制：學程課程、本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、學士後、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '本學期授課內容主要是著重於藥物的基本認知、心理與神經系統用藥、心血管系統藥物、呼吸系統\r\n藥物、消化系統藥物、內分泌代謝系統藥物、腎臟泌尿系統藥物、血液與造血器官藥物、骨骼藥物、\r\n免疫系統抑制發炎藥物、感染症藥物、抗癌藥物、及外用藥物等。教導學生對藥物的藥理作用機轉\r\n及用途的知識，進而了解藥物與疾病之關聯', 'The teaching content mainly focuses on the basic knowledge of drugs, psychological and nervous system \r\ndrugs, cardiovascular system drugs, respiratory system drugs, digestive system drugs, endocrine and \r\nmetabolic system drugs, kidney and urinary system drugs, blood and hematopoietic organ drugs, and bone \r\ndisease drugs, immune system drugs, infectious disease drugs, anti-cancer drugs, and topical drugs, etc. \r\nTeach students knowledge about the pharmacological mechanism and uses of drugs, and then understand \r\nthe relationship between drugs and diseases.', '1255', '4232Z601', '423B20', '健日四20', '1255'),
(256, '247', '1131', '莊士勇', '21140100000000 ', '21140', '686', '1', 2, 20, '顧客關係管理', 'Customer Relationship Management', '莊士勇', 60, 7, 53, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F402', '1', '6,7,8', '修課限制：學程課程、本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、學士後、跨校', '本課程教學設計，主要目的是提供學生對於 CRM 顧客關係管理有一個全盤性的認識，輔助以本土的教材做為個案分析的基礎，使學生可以在理論與實務中獲得顧客關係管理的全面性認識，並能運用於未來職場實務中。', 'The course provides the basic knowledge, scope, and the evolving progress of customer relationship management (CRM).The curriculum design using case study that students can understand CRM theory and be applied to future career.', '379', '4232Z591', '423B20', '健日四20', '379'),
(257, '248', '1131', '譚延綸', '21140100000000 ', '21140', '1061', '1', 2, 21, '職場英文', 'English for the Work Place', '譚延綸', 39, 13, 26, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F609', '2', '3,4', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放人康學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。4.全英語授課。\n', '本課程為一學期兩小時兩學分的課程。由英語中級程度提昇至中高級之訓練課程。教學重點為職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧及其應用。於該課程中學生能熟悉並練習職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧。', 'This is a two-hour weekly and one-semester course which is worth two credits. This is an intermediate to high-intermediate level English course. The main contents of the course consist of: common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, communication skills in workplace, and the application of communication skills. In this course, students are expected: (a) to become familiar with common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, and communication skills; and (b) to apply common English vocabulary in workplace and business English dialogue expressions to their everyday English conversations.', '567', '4232F531', '423BBA', '健英二21', '567'),
(258, '249', '1131', '梁立芳', '21140100000000 ', '21140', '1061', '1', 2, 22, '職場英文', 'English for the Work Place', '梁立芳', 38, 17, 21, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'G108', '2', '1,2', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放人康學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。4.全英語授課。\n', '本課程為一學期兩小時兩學分的課程。由英語中級程度提昇至中高級之訓練課程。教學重點為職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧及其應用。於該課程中學生能熟悉並練習職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧。', 'This is a two-hour weekly and one-semester course which is worth two credits. This is an intermediate to high-intermediate level English course. The main contents of the course consist of: common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, communication skills in workplace, and the application of communication skills. In this course, students are expected: (a) to become familiar with common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, and communication skills; and (b) to apply common English vocabulary in workplace and business English dialogue expressions to their everyday English conversations.', '108', '4232F531', '423BBB', '健英二22', '108'),
(259, '250', '1131', '梁立芳', '21140100000000 ', '21140', '1061', '1', 2, 23, '職場英文', 'English for the Work Place', '梁立芳', 40, 11, 29, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'G108', '2', '3,4', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放人康學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。4.全英語授課。\n', '本課程為一學期兩小時兩學分的課程。由英語中級程度提昇至中高級之訓練課程。教學重點為職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧及其應用。於該課程中學生能熟悉並練習職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧。', 'This is a two-hour weekly and one-semester course which is worth two credits. This is an intermediate to high-intermediate level English course. The main contents of the course consist of: common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, communication skills in workplace, and the application of communication skills. In this course, students are expected: (a) to become familiar with common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, and communication skills; and (b) to apply common English vocabulary in workplace and business English dialogue expressions to their everyday English conversations.', '108', '4232F531', '423BBC', '健英二23', '108'),
(260, '251', '1131', '邱尚志', '211400594012A0', '21140', '594', '1', 2, 0, '公共衛生概論', 'Introduction to Public Health', '邱尚志', 40, 11, 29, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F920', '3', '3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、學士後、跨校', '本課程旨在系統性地介紹公共衛生學的基本概念，內容將從健康的定義開始，逐一導入健康照護體系、健康保險、健康照護機構管理、流行病學與疾病防治、全球環境變遷與公共衛生、環境衛生與環境保護、健康行為與健康促進、健康社區等課題。此外，規劃透過學生參訪自來水廠、廢水處理場、健康社區等活動，增進學習效果。七、教學目標：期使學生了解公共衛生學的基本理論與實務。', 'The purpose of the lesson is to provide students with organized understanding on essential elements and principles of public health .', '9119', '4232Q681', '423421', '健四二A ', '9119'),
(261, '252', '1131', '張育通', '211400592012A0', '21140', '592', '1', 2, 0, '生物統計學與實驗(一)', 'Biostatistics and Lab I', '張育通', 48, 12, 36, 2.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F804', '1', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、學士後、跨校', '本課程傳授學生基本的生物統計學(一)原理及其電腦 Excel 之示範/操作，佐加計算機之示範計算，以使學生具備從事健康事業管理相關工作與初步電腦統計函數及簡單統計繪圖之操作實務。課程內容包括生物統計學概念、敘述統計學、機率概論、機率分布(Binomial, Normal, …)、抽樣分布、推論統計學(估計)，與其相關電腦 Excel 實作。', 'The objective of this course is to provide students with basic theories of Biostatistics I and simple calculation of Excel functions as well as simple figures drawing, a tool for the work in the health related fields. Subjects taught in this course include (1) basic concepts of Biostatistics I, (2) descriptive Statistics, (3) basic probability concepts, (4) probability distributions (Binomial, Normal, …), (5) sampling distributions, (6) inferential Statistics: estimation, (7) related practice by Excel.', '1158', '4232Q671', '423421', '健四二A ', '1158'),
(262, '253', '1131', '林聖凱', '211400024012A0', '21140', '24', '1', 2, 0, '法律倫理與生活', 'Laws and Ethics of Daily Life', '林聖凱', 42, 10, 32, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F303', '5', '6,7', '1.第二階段開放修習「法律倫理與生活」課程之學生互相跨班選課。\n2.重修生請自第二階段開放選課。全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '本課程之介紹，在於使學生對法律常識、法律理念、倫理概念及我國現行法有一整體性的認知。從生活與倫理及正義概念出發，就常見的法律問題，深入淺出有系統的介紹，以培養現代人正確的法律觀及倫理觀。', 'This course helps students to develop the following concepts: law, ethic, legal perspective, and legal system of Taiwan. From the aspects of ethics and justice, this course introduces common legal issues, in order to develop the knowledge of law and ethic for students.', '304', '4232F511', '423421', '健四二A ', '304'),
