(348, '339', '1131', '蘇博玄', '20160200000000 ', '20160', '1857', '1', 1, 10, '健康科技與生醫產業研究', 'Health technology and biomedical industry research', '蘇博玄', 5, 2, 3, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F809', '3', '6,7', '修課限制：本所、外所、自第一階段開放全校研究所同步選課', '課程規劃希望能夠涵蓋健康科技和生醫產業的各個方面，同時\r\n提供學生學習和討論的機會，並鼓勵他們在團隊項目和案例研究中應用所學知識。', 'The curriculum is designed to cover all aspects of the health \r\ntechnology and biomedical industries, while providing opportunities for students to \r\nlearn and discuss, and encouraging them to apply what they have learned in team \r\nprojects and case studies.', '1232', '6901Z071', '690A10', '健日碩10', '1232'),
