(350, '341', '1131', '謝楠楨', '201600067011A0', '20160', '67', '1', 1, 0, '研究方法論', 'Research Methods', '謝楠楨', 5, 2, 3, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F1024', '2', '3,4', '修課限制：本所、外所', 'Course is designed for scientific master students. Course content provides students the practical use of tools in designing and conducting a scientific research. Course covers the basic research methodology techniques, data analysis techniques, ethical rules and other research tools, like article retrieve system, formatting tools, and reading, writing and presentation techniques.', 'Course is designed for scientific master students. Course content provides students the practical use of tools in designing and conducting a scientific research. Course covers the basic research methodology techniques, data analysis techniques, ethical rules and other research tools, like article retrieve system, formatting tools, and reading, writing and presentation techniques.', '774', '6901Q071', '690211', '健院研一', '774'),
(351, '342', '1131', '洪論評', '201601630011A0', '20160', '1630', '1', 1, 0, '健康科技研討', 'Seminar in Health Technology', '洪論評', 5, 2, 3, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F1024', '2', '6,7', '修課限制：本所、外所', '本課程介紹了健康照護與資訊科技應用的知識、基礎設施、功能和工具。在實務個案中探討規劃和管理知識在健康照護工作中的應用，重點傳遞著健康科技研究概念框架以及更深層次的影響。課程將以照護技術為發展前提，藉由案例分享，讓學生了解目前健康科技議題之下的產業變革，並瞭解相關技術應用優勢，包括資訊系統、醫療科技以及照護專業等。期望同學藉由個案的閱讀、討論、分析、傾聽與反思的過程，培養健康科技應用決策所需的邏輯思維與知識，提昇同學對於未來研究與就業展的專業能力。', 'This course introduces the knowledge, infrastructure, functions, and tools of health care and information technology applications. Practical cases explore the application of planning and management knowledge to health care work, conveying the conceptual framework of health technology research and its deeper implications. The course content will begin with care technology, and through case sharing, students will learn about the changes in the industry under current health technology issues and understand the advantages of related technology applications, including information systems, medical technology, and the care profession. Through case reading, discussion, analysis, and reflection, students will be able to link theory and practice to enhance their understanding of health technology development. This course is designed to enhance students\' understanding of the development of health technology. Through thorough exposure to health technology cases, course participants will become familiar with the logic, theories, and uses presented in the cases and understand the strengths, challenges, and limitations of the current industry development in the cases.', '750', '6901Q081', '690211', '健院研一', '750'),
