(420, '411', '1131', '陳彥宏', '22140100000000 ', '22140', '1470', '1', 4, 45, 'C#.NET程式開發與應用', 'C# .NET Program Development and Application', '陳彥宏', 0, 0, 0, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '3', '2,3,4', '20240913關課。第一堂上課為09/12於S105，待行政流程完成後一律於週四09:10-12:00、S105上課，異動完成前本課程只退不加。修課限制：本系四技一般生、外系四技一般生、本所（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、程式設計課程', '本課程為一學期 C#.NET 應用程式設計課程，以微軟.NET 平台 Visual Studio 2015 開發工\r\n具為程式開發基礎，課程內容將詳盡說明 C#語言的語法結構及流程控制能力同時加強\r\n多工處理程式之撰寫技巧及物件設計之能力。對於使用者圖形化介面則透過 WPF 技術\r\n之整合使程式邏輯與資料分開管理、而對資料庫之應用則加強存取串聯、整合等為課程\r\n教學重點，得以使學生具備就業市場中所需.NET 環境資訊系統開發能力。', 'One semester C # .NET application design courses, under the Microsoft .NET platform by using\r\nVisual Studio 2015 development tools to develop program. At the mean time the speaker will\r\ndetailed description of the course content grammatical structure and process control capabilities\r\nof C # language and strengthen the multi-processing program writing skills and ability to design of\r\nobjects. For the graphical user interface makes the WPF technology through the integration of\r\nprogrammable logic and data managed separately, and for the strengthening of the database\r\napplication, to equip students with the job market in the required .NET environmental\r\ninformation system development capabilities.', '279', '4404Z921', '440D45', '資日四45', '279'),
(421, '412', '1131', '徐建業', '22140200000000 ', '22140', '1566', '1', 4, 46, '巨量資料分析工具與應用', 'Tools and Applications on Big Data Analysis', '徐建業', 38, 25, 13, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'S103', '4', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大四、外系四技一般生大四、本所（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨域課程、程式設計課程', '隨著資訊科技進步，現今資料累積的速度遠遠超過所能處理的速度。無論科學研究或是各種企業應用領域，許多單位都以資料分析做為組織未來的重要發展方向。R和 Python是開放源碼軟體，為資料分析使用的工具相當適合。期望提供學生一個良好的大數據軟體學習路徑，幫助初學者運用軟體，學習資料探勘工作與視覺化應用。\r\n課程內容從軟體基本概念與資料整理入手，介紹與健康及醫療相關之巨量資料的基本知識與方法，資料的理解與統計等基本觀念的建立，介紹資料挖礦與大數據分析的理論方法與應用，並進行實機演練程式設計，進而提升學生大數據分析和數位決策能力。', 'With the advancement of information technology, data now accumulated much faster than that we can handle. In science or a variety of enterprise organizations, data analysis has become an important direction for decision making. R and Python are open source software, and is suitable to be used as analysis tools. In this course, we expect to provide students with a good learning path for software used on helping beginners to learn data visualization and data mining. Course contains the basic concepts of software and data compilation, the basic knowledge and methods of health and medical information, the basic concepts of statistics, the theory and method of data mining and analysis, and hands-on programming exercises. Students abilities of the big data analytics and digital decision-making will be enhanced.', '1609', '4404Z931', '440D46', '資日四46', '1609'),
(422, '413', '1131', '洪素英', '22140200000000 ', '22140', '1628', '1', 4, 47, '醫療機構管理實務', 'Management and Practice of Health care Institutions', '洪素英', 31, 21, 10, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G204', '1', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大四、外系四技一般生大四、本所（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程旨在協助學生將過去所學如何運用於健康照護機構實際管理。課程內容以健康照護機構所面臨問題及實務演練為主，範圍從健康照護管理的簡介開始，再依循管理的過程分別介紹健康照護機構管理有關的主題如健康照護體系面臨經營環境、健康照護管理發展策略規劃、組織運作、績效管理與激勵、人力資源管理、品質管理、財務管理、風險管理及危機應變等之實務層面，期學生能藉此課程，對健康照護管理有更深入地認識，以激發自己在醫院管理方面之興趣。', 'This course aims to enhance students\' practice ability of health care management.  Focusing on health care system and the problems faced by health care institutions, discusses how to resolve and manage including theory and practice of health care management. Introduces key topics and concepts related to the management of health care institutions such as health care system, case studies in strategy management and decision making, managing health care organizations,  administrative management responsibilities of health care environments, quality assurance management methods, human resources management, approaches to performance improvement financial management, risk or crisis management and response. Particular emphasis is placed on integrating analytic skills and conflict resolution methods into the practice of health care management. A portion of the class is devoted to simulation exercise in which general concepts and methods are demonstrated and practiced.  By the end of the course, it is expected that students will more understand and be inspired interest in hospital management.', '9104', '4404Z941', '440D47', '資日四47', '9104'),
(423, '414', '1131', '陳紹韻', '221400031014A0', '22140', '31', '1', 4, 0, '哲學與人生', 'Philosophy and Life', '陳紹韻', 22, 13, 9, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F408', '5', '1,2', '1.第二階段開放修習「哲學與人生/邏輯概論」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。\n2.全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '「哲學與人生」是對「人的生命」所作的「哲學反省」。人，作為自然的、社會的、歷史的存在，在他所生活的世界中，面臨著繁複多樣、瞬息萬變的問題：處境、命運、愛情、知識、道德、藝術、宗教、臨終與死亡……其中有些問題事實上已經深深困擾著我們，另外一些則伺機突襲，在我們還來不及準備的時候，就被迫面對。生命的意義究竟是什麼？本課程嘗試以深入淺出的討論，藉由過去、當代人物的所感、所思，促進學習者進一步反省自我生命之種種。', 'Philosophy and Life is as a philosophical reflective thinking for the life.\r\nHuman beings, as natural, social and historical beings, face a great many complex varied and fast changing problems in the life-world, for example, love, destiny, knowledge, morality, art, religion, dying, and moreover the death so on.... Actually some of them have deeply perplexed us, while others watch for their chances to attack there would leave no time for covering our ears and we are merely compelled to confront with them. After all, what does Life mean?\r\nWhereas this course tries to take up by the way a kind of discussion in explaining the profound in simple terms, and in making use of whatever in history, or the present age somebody\'s feeling and thinking, in order to promote the students to question themselves more about, and reflect further on all sorts of life-self.', '9976', '4404F131', '440441', '資四四A ', '9976'),
(424, '415', '1131', '陳亮均', '221400142014A0', '22140', '142', '1', 4, 0, '電子商務', 'E-Commerce', '陳亮均', 31, 20, 11, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F601', '3', '3,4,5', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大四、外系四技一般生大四、本所（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '隨著網際網路及資訊技術的不斷進步，流通業者在科技工具的運用上就愈發成熟與專業，如此除了能提昇企業經營效益外，最重要的是能分析消費者需求，進而提供消費者更好的產品及服務。課程主要為教導學生瞭解現行電子商務的範疇及導入的模式，從電子商務架構概論、開創市場機會、經營模式、市場行銷等單元介紹，進而切入企業電子化角度介紹企業資源於電子商務之應用，同時以實例探討，期望學生能清楚地瞭解電子商務的發展、技術與策略，並激發其對該領域的實作、研究及分析評估能力。', 'The digital economy, also known as the Internet economy, is an economy based on online transactions, mostly e-commerce. It includes digital wireline or wireless communication networks (e.g., the Internet, intranets, extranets, and VANs), computers, software, and other related information technologies.\r\nIn our course, we will lead to understand the phenomena, both technological, economic and social, behind these rapid changes, and how organizations successfully conduct Internet-based activities. This course provides an overview of e-commerce from both technological and managerial perspectives. It introduces e-commerce frameworks, and technological foundations; and examine basic concepts such as strategic formulation for e-commerce enterprises, management of their capital structures and public policy. This course is designed to familiarize students with current and emerging electronic commerce technologies using the Internet. Topics include Internet technology for business advantage, managing electronic commerce funds transfer, reinventing the future of business through electronic commerce, business opportunities in electronic commerce, electronic commerce Web site design, social, political and ethical issues associated with e-commerce, and business plans for technology ventures.', '1219', '4404Q221', '440441', '資四四A ', '1219'),
(425, '416', '1131', '陳彥宏', '221400090014A0', '22140', '90', '1', 4, 0, '實務專題(二)', 'Practical Project II', '林良憲,林東正,徐建業,連中岳,陳彥宏,洪論評,陳亮均,吳承翰', 78, 50, 28, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '6', '4', '修課限制：專題製作、本系四技一般生大四、本所（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、程式設計課程', '針對資訊管理主題上提出創新觀念，或對某主題存在的問題提出解決方案，在效能上提出改進具體建議之研究並加以驗證。', 'This course applies theories and practices of services marketing on the subject of health care marketing. In addition to the concepts of consumer behavior, service product positioning, and market segmentation, the 4Ps (i.e., Products, Place, Promotion, an', '279', '4404Q211', '440441', '資四四A ', '7,990,740,160,904,020,000,000,000,000,000'),
