(454, '445', '1131', '吳孝觀', '321400509011B0', '32140', '509', '1', 1, 0, '運動保健概論', 'Introduction to Athletic Training and Health', '吳孝觀,周定衡', 31, 16, 15, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G205', '1', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、護理及長照與幼保學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '本課程旨在教導學生運用現代醫學保健的知識和方法，配合解剖學和公共衛生學等相關學科，對運動參與者進行醫學監督和指導。一方面可以促進和改善不同族群身體活動的能力，同時也可以預防運動時所可能產生的運動傷害。', 'This course, accompanied with anatomy and public health, is to instruct students to understand the general knowledge of athletic training and health. It also provides students with the ability to medically supervise the exercise participants.  Students can not only learn how to improve physical activity for different groups of people, but also how  to prevent the potential movement injuries in exercise or sports.', '1146', '4501Q581', '450412', '運四一Ｂ', '11,461,190'),
(455, '446', '1131', '彭雪英', '321400514011B0', '32140', '514', '1', 1, 0, '運動營養學', 'Sports Nutrition', '彭雪英', 33, 20, 13, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G205', '3', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、護理及長照與幼保學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '本課程旨在教導學生認識營養學觀念（六大營養素、均衡飲食）與其在運動保健時所扮演的重要腳色及相互關係，除增加學生正確的運動營養知識外並能應用所學，提昇個人的運動指導的能力以幫助維持或改善國民的健康水平。', 'This course, accompanied with nutrition and exercise, is to instruct students to understand the general knowledge of nutrition and the roles of nutrients in improving sports performance.  Students can not only learn how to evaluate what foods and amounts are appropriate for them, but also how to improve their ability to integrally supervise the exercise participants in the future.', '474', '4501Q591', '450412', '運四一Ｂ', '474'),
(456, '447', '1131', '簡名豪', '321401746011B0', '32140', '1746', '1', 1, 0, '體育-基本運動素養', 'P E-Fundamental Movement Capacities', '簡名豪', 27, 15, 12, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '2', '1,2', '1.四技一年級新生，由教務處安排於入學系別之一年級原班授課。 \n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。 \n3.上課地點請洽體育室。 \n4.跨校。 ', '新生的體育教學課程設計著重在體適能的強化、健康運動概念介紹及休閒運\r\n動入門引導。主要內容包括健康體適能之心肺適能的強化，以及帶動身體協\r\n調性與強調團隊合作的籃球運動為主，期望學生不僅習得運動健康概念，也\r\n因球類運動而習得助人及團隊合作的態度。', 'The purpose of this course for freshman is emphasis on the both physical \r\nfitness and basic sport skill. Lecturers instruct the concept of sports and healthy to \r\nthe student through cardiovascular fitness and sport skill (basketball) as well as to \r\npromote the coordination of the body and the emphasis on teamwork of basketball. \r\nFreshmen not only acquire the concept of sports health, but also learn to help \r\npeople and teamwork attitude.', '9135', '4501F561', '450412', '運四一Ｂ', '9135'),
(457, '448', '1131', '洪雅琦', '321400516012A0', '32140', '516', '1', 2, 0, '人體肌動學', 'Introduction of Kinesiology', '洪雅琦', 54, 31, 23, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G405', '2', '6,7', '運四二AB合班。修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技進修部、護理及長照與幼保學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '介紹人體動作時肌肉骨骼系統所扮演的角色與功能，包括關節動作的形成、動作時肌肉間的交互作用，並藉此推演病變或傷害發生時可能的變化。', 'Upon completion of this course, the student will be able to discuss general principles of kinetics and kinematics applied to kinesiology and the factors contributing to joint motion, mobility and stability of individual joints. Students should learn how t', '424', '4502Q901', '450421', '運四二Ａ', '424'),
(458, '449', '1131', '洪雅琦', '321400515012A0', '32140', '515', '1', 2, 0, '肌力強化理論與實務', 'Muscle Strengthening Theory and Practice', '洪雅琦', 53, 30, 23, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G201', '1', '3,4', '運四二AB合班。修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技進修部、護理及長照與幼保學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '透過對肌肉的認識，根據所需訓練結果，選擇合宜的動作並規劃具週期考量的肌力訓練計畫為本課程的主要教育宗旨。教導學生有能力評估、選擇並設計合宜的阻力訓練動作，確保阻力訓練所帶來的效果。', 'Strength training and conditioning produces a better result when conducted in according with scientific concept of periodization. Periodization is scientific based method for structuring short-and long-term strength training and conditioning plans. This c', '424', '4502Q891', '450421', '運四二Ａ', '424'),
(459, '450', '1131', '彭雪英', '321400521012A0', '32140', '521', '1', 2, 0, '身體活動與老化', 'Physical Activity and Aging', '彭雪英', 53, 31, 22, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G201', '4', '6,7', '運四二AB合班。修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技進修部、護理及長照與幼保學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '本課程旨在教導學生老化進行過程及現象、身體活動與老化的關係等相關知識，提升對中老年人進行運動處方及身體活動設計時所需要的能力，並期待學生能在運動保健領域發輝所學，促進老人的健康。本課程將搭配證照研習，需考取相關證照。', 'This course, accompanied with topics relating to physical activity and aging, is to instruct students to understand the phenomenon and theory of aging, and the relationships between physical activity and aging. Students can learn not only the importance of increasing daily physical activity to prevent disease, but also how to improve their ability to integrally supervise the exercise participants, especially for the middle-aged and elderly person  in the future.', '474', '4502Q911', '450421', '運四二Ａ', '474'),
(460, '451', '1131', '吳孝觀', '321400513012A0', '32140', '513', '1', 2, 0, '運動生物力學', 'Sports Biomechanics', '吳孝觀', 54, 31, 23, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G201', '3', '1,2', '運四二AB合班。修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技進修部、護理及長照與幼保學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '運動力學主要探討作用於人體之力量以及這些力量所造成之影響。課程目的在於教導學生相關的科學基礎，以及運動力學在運動技術分析所扮演的角色。學生學習之後應對於靜力學與動力學有相當的認識，並且了解這些原理在運動方面之應用。', 'Sports Biomechanics is concerned with the forces that act on a human body and the effects that these forces produce. The purpose of this course is to present the scientific basis and to demonstrate how it can be used to advantage in the analysis of sports', '1146', '4502Q881', '450421', '運四二Ａ', '1146'),
(461, '452', '1131', '林育安', '321400021012A0', '32140', '21', '1', 2, 0, '環境教育', 'Environmental Education', '林育安', 57, 31, 26, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'G202', '4', '3,4', '1.第二階段加退選，開放修習「環境教育」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。2. 全部網路選課，無紙本加選。3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。修課限制：本系四技一般生、外系四技一般生', '本課程旨在闡述環境永續發展的意義與重要性，教學內涵希望提昇學生永續發展的覺知，增加永續發展的概念知識，培養正確的永續發展態度與價值觀，並發展永續發展的行動技能與行動經驗。課程強調在環境中進行教育，學習有關環境的知識、態度、技能，並且為實踐永續環境而準備。環境教育包含六個核心的學習要素：自然資源保育概念、環境管理概念的融入；生態原理、互動與互賴概念的融入；以及融入環境倫理與永續性的概念等。\r\n    課程內容涵蓋環境概論、環境倫理、環境教育法規、環境變遷與防災、節能減碳與能源管理、與永續發展與生態保育等主題內容。教學策略運用：做中學、在真實的情境中體驗、合作學習法、運用感官學習、探索環境議題等項目。教學方法採取課堂講解、分組討論、專題討論、現地參訪等方式進行，並以多媒體教材教學。期望藉由環境議題的認識與討論，深入環境的內涵；透過對於環境問題的觀察與思考，了解環境永續的本質及善盡環境保護的義務。環境教育是一種教育的過程，在過程中個人認識他們的環境，以及組成環境的生物、物理和文化間的交互作用，得到知識、技能和價值觀，並能個別或集體地了解並解決現在和將來的環境問題。', 'Environmental education is designed to explain the meaning and importance of environment and sustainable development. It refers to organized efforts to teach how natural environments function, and particularly, how human beings can manage behavior and ecosystems to live sustainably. It is a multi-disciplinary field integrating disciplines such as biology, chemistry, physics, ecology, earth science, atmospheric science, mathematics, and geography. The term often implies education within the school system, from primary to post-secondary. However, it sometimes includes all efforts to educate the public and other audiences, including print materials, websites, media campaigns, etc. \r\n  Environmental education consists of six core elements: the concept of conservation of natural resources, environmental management into ecological principles, into the concept of interaction and interdependence; and the concept of integration of environmental ethics and sustainable environment. Environmental education is the teaching of individuals, and communities, in transitioning to a society that is knowledgeable of the environment and its associated problems, aware of the solutions to these problems, and motivated to solve them.Environmental education is an educational process, in the process of personal awareness in their environment, and form an environment of interaction between biological, physical and cultural, are knowledge, skills, and values, and individually or collectively, can understand and solve current and future environmental problems.', '615', '4502F361', '450421', '運四二Ａ', '615'),
(462, '453', '1131', '梁昭玉', '321400027012A0', '32140', '27', '1', 2, 0, '藝術文化史', 'History of Artistic Culture', '梁昭玉', 56, 30, 26, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'G201', '3', '3,4', '1.第二階段開放修習「藝術文化史/世界文明史」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。\n2.全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '透過藝術文化的類型與不同的表現形式及中西方藝術的演進與賞析，瞭解藝術的理念、內涵與歷史演變，深入探討藝術與生命、美感與生活、藝術與文化等重要議題之意義。培養學生對藝術文化有基本的認識與高度的敏感度，提升審美素養，持續自主學習的興趣。', 'Through the exploration of various types and form of art and culture, as well as the evolution and appreciation of Eastern and Western art, this course provides an understanding of the concepts, meaning and historical transformations of arts. It further delves deeply into significant topics such as art and life, aesthetics and everyday life, and art and culture. Students will acquire a foundational comprehension and heightened sensitivity of art and culture, enhance their aesthetic literacy, and foster a sustained commitment to self-directed education.', '788', '4502F371', '450421', '運四二Ａ', '788'),
(463, '454', '1131', '黃正銘', '321401741012A0', '32140', '1741', '1', 2, 0, '體育-水上活動', 'PE-Underwater Activities', '黃正銘', 48, 17, 31, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '1', '6,7', '1. 第一階段志願選，僅由生四二A、運四二A互相跨班選課。\n2. 第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。\n3.上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。\n4.跨校。', '本課程旨在使學生學會正確之游泳技巧及姿勢，在學習各項游泳技能的過程\r\n中，培養水中自救之能力及觀念並強化其心肺功能。授課內容為救生自救觀\r\n念、捷泳、仰泳、蝶泳，期望能成為學生的終身運動項目。', 'The course is to have students learn correct swimming skills and poses and \r\nestablish the ability and concept of self rescue in the water and strengthen \r\ntheir cardio-pulmonary function through the process of learning various \r\nswimming skills. Curriculum includes self rescue concepts, front crawl, \r\nbackstroke, butterfly stroke in to hope of making swimming a lifelong exercise \r\nitem for the students.', '1244', '4502F391', '450421', '運四二Ａ', '1244'),
(464, '455', '1131', '吳孝觀', '321401830012A1', '32140', '1830', '1', 2, 0, '水域運動指導', 'Aquatic Activity and Sport Instruction', '吳孝觀', 30, 21, 9, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F605', '4', '8,9', '運動保健指導模組，授課地點：游泳池。修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技進修部、護理及長照與幼保學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '水域運動指導法是一門涵蓋游泳、水中排球、獨木舟、SUP立槳和浮潛等多種水上運動項目的課程，旨在幫助學生掌握基本技能、了解安全知識和訓練方法，提高他們在水域運動中的自信心和熟練度。', '“Aquatic Activity and Sport Instruction” is a course that covers a variety of water sports such as swimming, water volleyball, canoeing, SUP stand-up paddling and snorkeling. It is designed to help students master basic skills, understand safety and training methods, and improve their confidence and proficiency in water leisure activity and sport. The goals of this course are: students will be able to master the basic skills of swimming, water volleyball, canoeing, SUP paddling and snorkeling, including stance, breathing, arm and leg movements, passing, catching, jumping, dunking, canoe control, SUP paddling, and snorkeling positions. Students will be able to understand the safety knowledge and emergency disposal methods of water sports, how to choose safety equipment and keep themselves safe, and take emergency measures in emergency situations. Students will be able to master the training methods of water sports, including skill training, physical training, tactical training, etc., to improve their skills and competition ability. Through this course, students will not only learn the fun of water sports, but also improve their physical fitness and water sports skills, so that they can be more confident and safer in guiding water activities.', '1146', '4502Q941', '450BA1', '運四二A1', '1146'),
(465, '456', '1131', '周定衡', '321401831012A1', '32140', '1831', '1', 2, 0, '休閒運動指導', 'Instruction of Leisure Physical Activity and Sports', '周定衡', 27, 19, 8, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '2', '3,4', '授課地點：操場。運動保健指導模組。修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技進修部、護理及長照與幼保學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '休閒運動指導法是一門涵蓋陸上運動、球類運動、登山等多項休閒運動項目的課程，旨在幫助學生掌握基本技能、瞭解休閒運動安全知識和訓練方法，提高他們在休閒運動中的自信心和熟練度。', 'Instruction of Leisure Physical Activity and Sports is a course covering sports, land sports, outdoor ball games, cycling, mountaineering, etc. It aims to help students master basic skills, understand leisure sports safety knowledge and training methods, and improve their ability in leisure sports. confidence and proficiency.', '1190', '4502Q951', '450BA1', '運四二A1', '1190'),
(466, '457', '1131', '林懿苑', '321401674012A2', '32140', '1674', '1', 2, 0, '傳統整復推拿常用手法實務', 'The practice of Chinese traditional manual and massage techniques', '林懿苑', 42, 25, 17, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'I103', '4', '1,2', '紓壓理療治療模組。修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技進修部、護理及長照與幼保學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '整合傳統經絡推拿法及相關變化徒手型式，組合臨床上經常處理到的問題及常⽤⽳道來進⾏指導與練習。了解⼗⼆經絡與奇經⼋脈之常⽤⽳位與其相對解剖位置，了解現代常⽤基本調理徒⼿經絡⼿法之流派及其差異，了解常⽤基本調理徒⼿經絡⼿法的適應症與禁忌症，了解常⽤基本調理徒⼿經絡療法的主要⽣理效應與相關臨床研究，發展常⽤基本調理徒⼿經絡⼿法之基本能⼒與臨床實⽤經驗，指導學⽣了解各項徒⼿經絡療法技術之使⽤時機與機理。矯正學⽣實⾏徒⼿經絡調理⼿法進⾏常⽤基本調理時技術之常犯錯誤。', 'This course is linked up with traditional Chinese medicine manual therapy to practice the ways of treatment for several human body injuries that we often meet up. In the process, we would use these traditional Chinese medicine manual therapies to practice for trunk, upper limb, and lower limb sections.', '808', '4502Q931', '450BA2', '運四二A2', '808'),
(467, '458', '1131', '黃俊清', '321400536012A2', '32140', '536', '1', 2, 0, '運動按摩學', 'Sports Massage', '黃俊清', 40, 23, 17, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'I103', '2', '8,9', '紓壓理療治療模組。修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技進修部、護理及長照與幼保學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校', '利用引導及循序漸進的教學方式，教導學生運動按摩的基本動作，透過對基本動作的熟練，進而提昇學生對運動按摩的興趣。講授運動按摩的計畫及管理策略。強調學生必須在安全範圍內施行競賽前中後的運動按摩，期望學生能自行規劃運動按摩計畫。', 'The class divides in small group in order to offer students have more opportunity to learn better in very short time. Teach them to learn sports massage, not only to make them learn more, but also build the bridge to improve the human relationship. Cultivating their self-confident and enthusiasm of sports massage, and wishing sports massage can be the lifelong habit for student.', '408', '4502Q921', '450BA2', '運四二A2', '408'),
