(470, '461', '1131', '洪雅琦', '32140100000000 ', '32140', '541', '1', 3, 31, '有氧運動指導 II', 'Aerobic ExerciseⅡ－ Theory and Practicum', '洪雅琦', 30, 12, 18, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '3', '1,2', '授課地點：韻律教室，修課限制：本系四技一般生大三以上，須修過「有氧運動指導 I」', '本課內容主要在教導學生認識基本團體肌力與心肺循環的的益處與應用領域，並有能力進行基本的器材架設與課程設計、音樂選擇、不同目標之課程設計與安排，再依據不同會員需求帶領團隊團體有氧雕塑課程。', 'Group aerobic and resistance circuit is a form of high-intensity exercise that involves using a free weight equipment and step in a classroom setting. During the class the instructor simulates a move. Together, follow by music, all participants doing same movement at the same time. The benefits of this class can both challenge physical and mental ability, can be enjoyed by almost anyone, regardless of age or fitness level. This course is to lead student to know the group free weight class and all the teaching method, In order to lead the one hour basic aerobic and resistance circuit workout in group setting.', '424', '4503Z811', '450C31', '運日四31', '424'),
