(511, '502', '1131', '廖翊宏', '324600631012A0', '32460', '631', '1', 2, 0, '學術論文寫作', 'Academic Writing for Publication', '廖翊宏', 14, 4, 10, 2.00, '第1,3,5,7,9,11,13,15,17週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S105', '5', '11,12,13,14', '1.單數週上課。\n2.修課限制：本所專班碩士班二年級以上學生、外所（是否列入畢業學分請參照入學年課程科目表）、跨校。', '本課程在提升學生邏輯的思維與寫作的技巧，以期達到撰寫學術性文章的能力。課程綜合了資料分析、寫作技巧及電腦文書處理。內容大綱包括：資料庫分析、資料查詢的方法與技巧、學術性文獻分析與統整、文章構思與寫作技巧、寫作常見的問題、文章批判、APA5書寫方式、及寫作的倫理。', 'The purpose of this course is to promote logistic thinking and writing skill of students. The main content of this course includes data analysis, writing skill, data searching, literature review, paper critic and word processing, etc. This course, through', '469', '6012Q331', '601221', '運保專二', '469'),
(512, '503', '1131', '陳郁雯', '251400918011A0', '25140', '918', '1', 1, 0, '言語科學', 'Speech Sciences', '陳郁雯', 47, 8, 39, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F401', '3', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程目地為建立學生的言語科學基礎。主要的範圍為言語產生的解剖學與生理學。討論的範圍有呼吸(聲門下)系統、喉部系統、構音(共鳴) 系統。學生也同時學習言語產生之理論。', 'This course aims to help graduate students to establish a solid foundation in the field of speech sciences, especially the anatomy, physiology, and theory of speech sciences.  Four major areas including speech breathing, laryngeal physiology, articulatory and resonance mechanisms are discussed thoroughly.  In addition, the physiological equipments to monitor the respiratory, laryngeal and supralaryngeal systems during speech production are introduced.', '1160', '4641Q471', '464411', '聽四一A ', '1160'),
(513, '504', '1131', '何澍', '251400000011A0', '25140', '0', '1', 1, 0, '國文一', 'Chinese Literature I', '何澍', 54, 11, 43, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F408', '1', '8,9', '大一新生限54名，其餘名額預留予重修生。\n1.第二階段加退選僅由人康、健科學院四技生一年級生互相跨班選課及人康、健科學院重修生選課。\n2.第三階段加退選開放系外及重修生選課。\n3.主題:文學與成長', '本課程銜接中學國文教育，著重培養學生閱讀、欣賞、寫作、口語表達等語言文字能力，並提升學生閱讀興趣、拓展人文視野，增進學生人文精神與文化涵養，進而落實至生活中，以培養獨立思考、理性自主的健全人格。', 'In this course students will study representative works of classical and modern literature, with an emphasis on improving verbal skills such as reading, writing, speaking and appreciation for Chinese literature. In doing so, the course aims to inspire students\' interest in reading in order to expand on their knowledge, thus able to integrate vitality and cultural conservation into everyday life, whilst promoting independent, logical thinking and a healthy character.', '105', '4641F141', '464411', '聽四一A ', '105'),
(514, '505', '1131', '翁仕明', '251401359011A0', '25140', '1359', '1', 1, 0, '普通心理學', 'General Psychology', '翁仕明', 45, 9, 36, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F401', '1', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生、本所、跨域課程、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '該課程帶領學生了解心理學各種研究領域的相關理論及成果，並透過心理測驗和科學研究方法的相關概念，促進助人領域所需的同理心發展，並體驗個別心理諮商。', 'This course aims to lead students to the area of psychological assessment and research method. Students may facilitate emergency of sympathy which is critical in consulting-related fields and be encouraged to experience psychological consulting individually.', '8384', '4641Q491', '464411', '聽四一A ', '8384'),
(515, '506', '1131', '張宸瑋', '251400916011A0', '25140', '916', '1', 1, 0, '溝通障礙學導論', 'Introduction to Communication Disorders', '張宸瑋,陳雅資,邱怡婷', 50, 10, 40, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F401', '2', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程將協助學生對發展與各類溝通障礙有先備的知識與常識; 透過實例與影片提供學生與各類溝通障礙的首次接觸,開啟學生對發展語溝通障礙行為的敏感度.奠定未來各科障礙課程與臨床的基礎。', 'This course is designed to provide undergraduate students with an introduction to different types of communication disorders through actual examples and case studies used.', '266', '4641Q461', '464411', '聽四一A ', '26,690,601,130'),
(516, '507', '1131', '陳郁夫', '251401362011A0', '25140', '1362', '1', 1, 0, '聽語基礎臨床實驗(一)', 'Basic Practice in Speech-Language Pathology and Audiolgoy I', '陳郁夫', 46, 8, 38, 2.00, '全18週', 4.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F401', '2', '5,6,7,8', '修課限制：本系四技一般生、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程目的在於引導學生對語言治療師的專業及臨床業務有初步的認識及瞭解。課程中所討論的主題包含語言治療師的專業及生涯簡介，以協助學生做未來學習及生涯規劃。授課教師在課程中亦將與學生討論學習策略以助學生提升自我學習力。', 'This course is designed to provide first-year undergraduate students with an introduction to the clinical practice in the field of speech-language pathology and audiology. Topics in this course include the career as a speech-language therapist, audiologist, ethical and professional practices, learning strategies and self-exploration for the students, as well as various resources provided by the University.', '1629', '4641Q501', '464411', '聽四一A ', '1629'),
(517, '508', '1131', '陳雅資', '251401358011A0', '25140', '1358', '1', 1, 0, '聽語解剖與生理學', 'Speech and Hearing Anatomy and physiology', '陳雅資', 48, 8, 40, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F401', '3', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本系四技一般生、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程的教學目的在於使本系學生瞭解人體生理各系統，進而瞭解聽語密切相關的器官構造與功能，為學生在往後修習聽語專業科目打下深厚的基礎，在從事臨床工作時能得心應手。為達成上述教學目標，除了教授正常結構、系統生理內容外，會佐以相當份量的臨床症狀，說明本課程與日後應用的密切關係。', 'This course aims to help students have an overall understanding about human physiology and anatomy related to speech and hearing therapy, which benefits for the leaning and working in this field. To attain the goal above, there will be an amount of clinical discussions and lectures to connect the advanced profession in the future.', '9060', '4641Q481', '464411', '聽四一A ', '9060'),
(518, '509', '1131', '藍偉雄', '251401746011A0', '25140', '1746', '1', 1, 0, '體育-基本運動素養', 'P E-Fundamental Movement Capacities', '藍偉雄', 45, 8, 37, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '4', '6,7', '1. 四技一年級新生，由教務處安排於入學系別之一年級原班授課。\n2. 第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。\n3.上課地點請洽體育室。\n4.跨校。', '新生的體育教學課程設計著重在體適能的強化、健康運動概念介紹及休閒運\r\n動入門引導。主要內容包括健康體適能之心肺適能的強化，以及帶動身體協\r\n調性與強調團隊合作的籃球運動為主，期望學生不僅習得運動健康概念，也\r\n因球類運動而習得助人及團隊合作的態度。', 'The purpose of this course for freshman is emphasis on the both physical \r\nfitness and basic sport skill. Lecturers instruct the concept of sports and healthy to \r\nthe student through cardiovascular fitness and sport skill (basketball) as well as to \r\npromote the coordination of the body and the emphasis on teamwork of basketball. \r\nFreshmen not only acquire the concept of sports health, but also learn to help \r\npeople and teamwork attitude.', '410', '4641F151', '464411', '聽四一A ', '410'),
(519, '510', '1131', '翁仕彥', '251401360012A0', '25140', '1360', '1', 2, 0, '生物統計概論', 'Introduction to Biostatistics', '翁仕彥', 44, 11, 33, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S103', '1', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程主要使學生熟悉溝通障礙學上常使用的統計方法理論。本課程以介紹統計理論之觀念為主，數學公式之之推導為輔。期望藉由介紹文獻與研究上最常使用的統計方法使學生可以充分將統計理論應用於實際研究會遇到的問題。', 'This course provides a practical introduction to the theorem, methods, techniques, and computation of statistics in communication disorder. It prepares students for their future courses and careers by introducing the statistical methods most often used in relative literatures. We will minimize the amount of mathematical formulation (algebra-based) while still giving complete explanations of all the important concepts.', '252', '4642Q511', '464421', '聽四二A ', '252'),
(520, '511', '1131', '童寶娟', '251401365012A0', '25140', '1365', '1', 2, 0, '兒童語言發展學', 'Child Language Development', '童寶娟', 48, 12, 36, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F402', '4', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨域課程', '本課程主要建立學生的兒童語言發展學基礎。課程範圍包括嬰幼兒、學齡前兒童及學齡兒童的語言發展。討論的範圍有溝通、語言及認知之間的關係、 語言習得理論、語言前期及語言期的音韻、詞彙、語法語意及語用發展。', 'This course aims to provide speech pathology students a thorough understanding of the development of language. The language development of infant, toddler, preschooler, and school-age are included. Major topics include: the relation among communication, language and cognition, the theories of language development, nonverbal communication at the pre-linguistic stages and the linguistic development.', '1622', '4642Q531', '464421', '聽四二A ', '1622'),
(521, '512', '1131', '巴甫仁', '251400058012A0', '25140', '58', '1', 2, 0, '研究概論', 'Research Method', '巴甫仁', 44, 11, 33, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F402', '1', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本堂課提供學生學習應用於不同領域的研究方法，包含研究假說設立、質性與量性研究法、抽樣設計、文獻搜尋、研究上倫理考量、調查研究法,資料收集的基本概念及其策略、溝通障礙學研究、統計分析及其資料解釋，與撰寫專題研究計劃案。本課程在幫助學生認識各種溝通障礙研究法，建立溝通障礙研究的基本概念，並培養參與及進行溝通障礙研究之基本能力', 'This course provides training and experience in survey questionnaire design and related survey research methods, including concepts and strategies for developing and assessing survey questionnaires, formatting, wording, coding, and ordering questions, design issues for various modes of survey data collection, designing questions to measure various key groups of variables, analyzing and interpreting survey data, and writing a research report', '1144', '4642Q491', '464421', '聽四二A ', '1144'),
(522, '513', '1131', '葉侃彧', '251401364012A0', '25140', '1364', '1', 2, 0, '語音學及語音聲學', 'Phonetics and Acoustic Phonetics', '葉侃彧', 43, 12, 31, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F402', '3', '7,8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程是為未來聽語臨床工作者所設計之基礎語音學及語音聲學課程。在這門課中，透過不同語言中的語音實例，探討人類的發音器官、語音本質、產生語音的方法及說話時的語音聽知覺與聲學變化。學生在這門課中亦將學習國際音標符號，並使用這些音標及符號標示及描述或記錄語音。本課程亦將帶領學生學習語音聲學分析，學生將熟悉語音聲學分析的學理基礎、以及語音分析軟體的實務操作。', 'This is an introduction to areas of phonetics of languages in the world geared towards speech-language pathologists and audiologists. Students will explore their articulators and learn how individuals produce and perceive speech sounds. They will also explore various topics regarding speech sounds and learn to describe and transcribe sounds in spoken languages.\r\nThis course is also designed to introduce the acoustic aspects of speech production and speech perception.  Students will learn software implementation of acoustic analysis.  This course covers the acoustic theory of speech production, and the practical applications for the acoustic analysis of speech.  The acoustic characteristics of Mandarin speech sounds will also be included.', '0', '4642Q521', '464421', '聽四二A ', '1262'),
(523, '514', '1131', '陳郁夫', '251400912012A0', '25140', '912', '1', 2, 0, '臨床聽力學', 'Clinical Audiology', '陳郁夫', 46, 13, 33, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F402', '3', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程之目的是臨床聽力學之基本知識。課程之內容包括純音與語音聽力評估, 中耳測試, 電生理聽力評估之原則與嬰幼兒聽力評估之原則, 以及與臨床有關之聽力評估課題。課程之實施包括課堂講授, 討論, 與分組實驗。', 'Course Description: The purpose of this course is to prepare students with basic knowledge in clinical audiology.  The course contents include: case history, otoscopic exam, pure tone audiometry, middle ear measures, otoacoutic emissions and auditory evoked potentials.  The course also includes diagnostic audiometric procedures and pediatric audiological evaluations.', '1629', '4642Q501', '464421', '聽四二A ', '1629'),
(524, '515', '1131', '張宸瑋', '251401366012A0', '25140', '1366', '1', 2, 0, '聽語基礎臨床實驗(三)', 'Basic Practice in Speech-Language Pathology and Audiology III', '張宸瑋,陳岱靈', 44, 11, 33, 2.00, '全18週', 4.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F402', '4', '6,7,8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生二年級以上、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程目的在於引導學生對語言治療師的專業及臨床業務有初步的認識及瞭解。課程中欲討論的主題包語言治療師從事評估診斷、治療及臨床諮商方法與原則、臨床紀錄及報告之書寫等。', 'This course is designed to provide the second-year undergraduate students with an introduction to the clinical practice in the field of speech-language pathology. Topics in this course include clinical practice skills, therapy strategies and self-exploration for the students, as well as various resources provided by the University.', '266', '4642Q541', '464421', '聽四二A ', '2,668,379'),
(525, '516', '1131', '田政文', '251401733012A0', '25140', '1733', '1', 2, 0, '體育-體適能1', 'PE-Physical Fitness1', '田政文', 45, 8, 37, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '2', '8,9', '1.第一階段志願選，僅由健四二A、健四二B、聽四二A互相跨班選課。 \n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。 \n3.上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。 \n4.跨校。 ', '本課程旨在介紹體適能的知識，瞭解如何評估及提升\r\n體適能，同時能體驗運動效益，享受運動樂趣，養成規律運動習慣，以達到控制\r\n體重、塑身及促進健康的目標。', 'The aim of the course is to introduce the knowledge of physical fitness.\r\nUnderstanding how to evaluate and promote physical fitness, at the same\r\ntime, enjoy the exercise, develop regular exercise habits to reach the goal of\r\nweight control, body sculpting and health promotion.', '473', '4642F111', '464421', '聽四二A ', '473'),
(526, '517', '1131', '張敬賢', '25140100000000 ', '25140', '1412', '1', 3, 30, '行為改變技術與應用', 'Behavior Modification and Application', '張敬賢', 26, 4, 22, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F605', '2', '8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上語言組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程著重在認識行為改變技術的特性與理論背景與了解行為改變的原理及使用之策略，透過個案討論應用行為與功能分析技巧，使學生未來在臨床工作上能善用行為改變技術增進聽語治療的效率。', 'This course helps students recognize the characteristic and background of behavior change techniques, and understand the principles and the use of its strategy. Via the case study, students can apply the skill of behavior modification and function analysis to improve the efficiency in the future clinical therapy.', '9925', '4643Z221', '464C30', '語日四30', '9925'),
(527, '518', '1131', '張宸瑋', '25140100000000 ', '25140', '1417', '1', 3, 31, '聽力保健', 'Hearing Conservation', '張宸瑋', 22, 6, 16, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F406', '3', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '教導學生習得噪音量測原理與技術，學習噪音量測實務及噪音控制原則，並且藉由噪音量測結果給予噪音環境下聽覺防護設備，比較各個聽覺防護設備效益及評量。', 'This course introduces students the theory and skills of measuring noise, and provides students with knowledge required for the practice and principles to control and measure noise. Students needs to compare the benefit of hearing protector devices according to the noise tests under noisy environment.', '266', '4643Z231', '464C31', '語日四31', '266'),
(528, '519', '1131', '吳璦如', '251401371013A0', '25140', '1371', '1', 3, 0, '成人語言障礙實驗', 'Practicum of the Communicative Disorders in Adults', '吳璦如', 36, 7, 29, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F406', '4', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上語言組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '透過影片以及安排學生見習，親自參與個案、紀錄成人語言障礙的治療狀況，進行個案討論和分享。', 'With the videos and the clinical observation, students participate in the case of the communicative disorders in adults, and record the clinical treatments. Students need to do the discussion in the class.', '237', '4643Q951', '464431', '聽四三A ', '237'),
(529, '520', '1131', '張智婷', '251401370013A0', '25140', '1370', '1', 3, 0, '成人語言障礙學', 'Communicative Disorders in Adults', '張智婷', 36, 7, 29, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F406', '4', '1,2', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上語言組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '主要探討成人語言障礙，包括失語症、右腦傷、創傷性腦傷和失智症。', 'This course is focus on the diagnosis, assessment, and intervention of the communicative disorders in adults, including aphasia, right hemisphere damage, TBI, and dementia.', '691', '4643Q941', '464431', '聽四三A ', '691'),
(530, '521', '1131', '王麗美', '251401377013A0', '25140', '1377', '1', 3, 0, '吞嚥障礙實驗', 'Swallowing  Disorders Practicum', '王麗美', 35, 7, 28, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F406', '4', '8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上語言組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '讓學生從實作中，學習吞嚥篩檢工具、床邊吞嚥檢查評估工具等的使用及判讀方法。依據吞嚥異常評估結果，擬定治療策略。再經由探討頭頸部腫瘤個案及神經性異常個案之吞嚥問題，學習該類個案吞嚥代償性治療、直接治療、間接治療等方法，以培養臨床處置吞嚥障礙個案之基礎實務技能。', 'The goal of this course is to teach students learn swallowing screening tools, bedside swallow assessment etc. and their interpretations from hands on practice. Based on diagnostic impression, the students should learn to make treatment plan for swallowing disorders. From knowledge of swallowing problems of head and neck cancer and neurologic impairments, the students should learn compensatory strategies, direct therapy and indirect therapy from hands on practice to build up their clinical skills for swallowing disorders.', '260', '4643Q0B1', '464431', '聽四三A ', '260'),
(531, '522', '1131', '童寶娟', '251401376013A0', '25140', '1376', '1', 3, 0, '吞嚥障礙學', 'Swallowing  Disorders', '童寶娟', 35, 7, 28, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F406', '4', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上語言組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '吞嚥異常是讓學生從正常吞嚥構造與吞嚥機轉，探討異常的吞嚥構造及吞嚥機轉，    以了解吞嚥異常原因以及其評估與治療方法。授課內容包括正常吞嚥構造與吞嚥機轉，各類型吞嚥異常，吞嚥異常評估方法，吞嚥異常治療方法，以及吞嚥異常臨床決策。', 'The goal of this course is to teach students to learn assessment and treatment methodologies of swallowing disorders from knowledge of normal and abnormal swallowing anatomy and physiology. The course content includes normal swallowing anatomy and physiology, abnormal swallowing anatomy and physiology, the causes of swallowing disorders, evaluation and treatment of swallowing disorders, clinical decision making, and multidisciplinary management.', '1622', '4643Q0A1', '464431', '聽四三A ', '1622'),
(532, '523', '1131', '陳郁雯', '251401373013A0', '25140', '1373', '1', 3, 0, '嗓音異常實驗', 'Voice Disorders Practicum', '陳郁雯', 35, 7, 28, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F303', '1', '8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上語言組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '讓學生從實作中，學習嗓音評估工具，包括病史、聽知覺評估、自評、聲學及氣\r\n動學測量等的使用及判讀方法。依據嗓音評估結果，擬定嗓音治療計劃。再經由實際練習各種嗓音治療方法，包括衛教嗓音治療、症狀嗓音治療、心理嗓音治療、及生理嗓音治療，以培養臨床處置嗓音障礙個案之實務技能。', 'The goal of this course is to teach students learn voice evaluation tools including history taking, auditory perceptual judgment, self-report, acoustic and aerodynamic measurements etc. and their interpretations from hands on practice. Based on diagnostic impression, the students should learn to make treatment plan for voice disorders. From hands on practice a variety of treatment methods including vocal hygiene, symptomatic voice therapy, psychogenic voice therapy and physiological voice therapy, the students will build up their clinical skills for voice disorders.', '1160', '4643Q971', '464431', '聽四三A ', '1160'),
(533, '524', '1131', '陳郁雯', '251401372013A0', '25140', '1372', '1', 3, 0, '嗓音異常學', 'Voice Disorders', '陳郁雯', 35, 7, 28, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F303', '1', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上語言組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '讓學生從正常發聲系統構造與機轉，探討異常的發聲構造及發聲機轉，以了解嗓音異常原因以及其評估與治療方法。授課內容包括介紹正常發聲構造與機轉、嗓音異常原因、嗓音異常機轉，嗓音異常類型，嗓音異常症狀與徵候，嗓音評估方法，以及嗓音治療原則與方法。', 'Introduce to students abnormal phonation physiology, classification of voice disorders and signs as well as symptoms of voice disorders. From these bases, the assessment of voice disorders from multidimentional aspects including perceptual judgment, acoustic analysis, aerodynamic analysis, videostroboscoby etc are then instructed. The principle and methodology of treatment for voice disordered patients are also included.', '1160', '4643Q961', '464431', '聽四三A ', '1160'),
(534, '525', '1131', '邱怡婷', '251401375013A0', '25140', '1375', '1', 3, 0, '學齡兒童語言異常實驗', 'Practice in Language Disorders in School-Age Children', '邱怡婷', 35, 7, 28, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F303', '1', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上語言組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程旨在以兒童語言發展學及學前兒童語言異常學、學前兒童語言異常實作為基礎，使學生透過臨床觀摩見習、示範、講解等方式，與學齡兒童語言異常學之學理結合，了解各種學齡兒童評估和診斷與治療之工具、方式與技巧。', 'The purpose of this course is to provide students with opportunities to observe school-age children and adolescents with language and/or related disorders. Specifically, students will observe clinical assessment and intervention processes of language disorders in school age children and adolescents in various institutions.', '1130', '4643Q991', '464431', '聽四三A ', '1130');
INSERT INTO `課程` (`編號`, `課程編號`, `學期`, `主開課教師姓名`, `科目代碼_新碼`, `系所代碼`, `核心四碼`, `科目組別`, `年級`, `上課班組`, `科目中文名稱`, `科目英文名稱`, `授課教師姓名`, `上課人數`, `男學生上課人數`, `女學生上課人數`, `學分數`, `上課週次`, `上課時數_週`, `課別代碼`, `課別名稱`, `上課地點`, `上課星期`, `上課節次`, `課表備註`, `課程中文摘要`, `課程英文摘要`, `主開課教師代碼_舊碼`, `科目代碼_舊碼`, `課表代碼_舊碼`, `課表名稱_舊碼`, `授課教師代碼_舊碼`) VALUES
(535, '526', '1131', '邱怡婷', '251401374013A0', '25140', '1374', '1', 3, 0, '學齡兒童語言異常學', 'Language Disorders in School-Age Children', '邱怡婷', 35, 7, 28, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F605', '2', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上語言組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程旨在以兒童語言發展學為基礎，探討學齡期兒童至青少年時期之語言異常及相關障礙。內容包括語言的認知處理歷程、語言異常／障礙之理論、各類障礙學齡兒童的語言問題、以及語言異常／障礙之評估與介入。本課程亦將討論學齡兒童語言異常之相關議題與研究。', 'The purpose of this course is to provide student with information on language disorders in the population of school-age children and adolescents, with an emphasis on language development in school-age to adolescence. Specifically, students will review various issues pertaining to the identification, assessment and intervention of language disorders in school age children and adolescents.', '1130', '4643Q981', '464431', '聽四三A ', '1130'),
(536, '527', '1131', '吳旻穎', '251400027013A0', '25140', '27', '1', 3, 0, '藝術文化史', 'History of Artistic Culture', '吳旻穎', 37, 10, 27, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F407', '5', '6,7', '1.第二階段開放修習「藝術文化史/世界文明史」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。\n2.全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '透過藝術文化的類型與不同的表現形式及中西方藝術的演進與賞析，瞭解藝術的理念、內涵與歷史演變，深入探討藝術與生命、美感與生活、藝術與文化等重要議題之意義。培養學生對藝術文化有基本的認識與高度的敏感度，提升審美素養，持續自主學習的興趣。', 'Through the exploration of various types and form of art and culture, as well as the evolution and appreciation of Eastern and Western art, this course provides an understanding of the concepts, meaning and historical transformations of arts. It further delves deeply into significant topics such as art and life, aesthetics and everyday life, and art and culture. Students will acquire a foundational comprehension and heightened sensitivity of art and culture, enhance their aesthetic literacy, and foster a sustained commitment to self-directed education.', '787', '4643F171', '464431', '聽四三A ', '787'),
(537, '528', '1131', '彭賢德', '251401714013A0', '25140', '1714', '1', 3, 0, '體育-羽球3', 'PE-Badminton3', '彭賢德', 50, 10, 40, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '5', '3,4', '1.第一階段志願選，僅由語四三A、生四三A互相跨班選課。\n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。\n3.上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。\n4.跨校。', '本課程透過對羽球雙打常用技術及比賽概念的介紹，引\r\n導學生體驗羽球雙打比賽的奧妙。授課內容包括發球、網邊球、挑球、切球、平擊球、\r\n高遠球、殺球、球路組合、雙打站位、比賽規則與戰術介紹及實際比賽體驗。', 'This program leads students to experience the secret of badminton doubles \r\nthrough the introduction of the common skills and game concept of badminton \r\ndoubles. Course content includes service, drop shot, lobs, cut, drive, clear, \r\nsmashes, technique combination, doubles standing position, game rules, \r\ntactic introduction and actual experience of games.', '1006', '4643F181', '464431', '聽四三A ', '1006'),
(538, '529', '1131', '陳郁夫', '251400936013A1', '25140', '936', '1', 3, 0, '電生理聽力學', 'Auditory Electrophysiology', '陳郁夫', 10, 5, 5, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F406', '3', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上聽力組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程介紹聽覺電生理學性之生理基礎，測試方法及臨床應用。內容包括各類聽性誘發反應，及耳聲傳射。', 'This course is designed to study the physiological bases, methods and clinical application of auditory brainstem response and other electrophysiological measures as well as otoacoustic emissions. The focus of the course is in the areas of auditory brainstem response and evoked otoacoustic emissions including TEOAE and DPOAE.', '1629', '4643Q931', '464CA1', '聽四三A1', '1629'),
(539, '530', '1131', '陳岱靈', '251401386013A1', '25140', '1386', '1', 3, 0, '電生理聽力學實驗', 'Auditory electrophysiology Practicum', '陳岱靈', 10, 5, 5, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F406', '3', '8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上聽力組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程教導將理論運用於實際操作聽覺電生理學性之儀器，如腦幹聽性反應、聽覺誘發電位與耳聲傳射等，實際操作並學習撰寫評估報告。', 'This course is designed to provide students with laboratory practice and case report writing for auditory brainstem response and other electrophysiological measures as well as otoacoustic emissions. The focus of the practice is in the areas of auditory brainstem response, other auditory evoked potentials, and evoked otoacoustic emissions.', '8379', '4643Q0E1', '464CA1', '聽四三A1', '8379'),
(540, '531', '1131', '龔碧菁', '251401383013A1', '25140', '1383', '1', 3, 0, '聽覺輔具原理運用', 'Rationales and Use of Hearing Devices', '龔碧菁', 11, 5, 6, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F931', '3', '11,12', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上聽力組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程涵蓋聽覺輔具選配及驗證所需之相關學理知識與實務操作技能。教學內容依各類聽覺輔具的選擇、評估及維護分為三大主軸，依序選讀相關文獻，並將在課程中搭配聽覺輔具原理運用實作課程，帶領學生進行實務演練，以培養學生未來進入臨床實習階段所需之專業知能。', 'This course prepares students to knowledge required for fitting hearing devices. Class readings, lectures, discussions and hands-on experience focus on the evidence-based procedures developed for the audiologic management of hearing loss through various kinds of hearing devices. The goals of this course are to provide: knowledge for fitting and evaluation of hearing devices; and knowledge forthe process of hearing device validation/verification.', '386', '4643Q0C1', '464CA1', '聽四三A1', '386'),
(541, '532', '1131', '陳雪霞', '251401384013A1', '25140', '1384', '1', 3, 0, '聽覺輔具原理運用實驗', 'Rationales and Use of Hearing DevicesPracticum', '陳雪霞', 10, 5, 5, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F931', '4', '11,12', '修課限制：本系四技一般生三年級以上聽力組、本所、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）', '本課程涵蓋聽覺輔具選配及驗證所需之實務操作技能。教學內容搭配聽覺輔具原理運用實作課程，帶領學生進行實務演練，以培養學生未來進入臨床實習階段所需之專業知能。', 'This course prepares students to clinical skills required for fitting hearing devices.  Hands-on experience focus on the evidence-based procedures developed for the audiologic management of hearing loss through various kinds of hearing devices. The goals of this course are to provide: 1) clinical skills for fitting and evaluation of hearing devices; and 2) clinical skills for the process of hearing device validation/verification.', '1625', '4643Q0D1', '464CA1', '聽四三A1', '1625'),
