(562, '537', '1131', '葉侃彧', '25161100000000 ', '25161', '924', '1', 1, 10, '心理語言學', 'Psycholinguistics', '葉侃彧', 3, 0, 3, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F931', '3', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本所語言組', '本課程旨在幫助學生建立心理語言學領域的基礎知識，並熟悉本領域之相關議題。學生將學到語言使用者如何理解語言、產出語言、及習得語言，及其相關的認知歷程。學生亦有機會學習並運用本課程內容至臨床評估治療或語言學相關之領域。', 'Psycholinguistics stands at the crossroads of linguistics, psychology, computer science and neuroscience. This course aims to introduce basic issues in this interdisciplinary study that explores how human beings use languages. Topics to be covered in the semester include: (1) language comprehension, (2) language production and (3) language acquisition. Students will acquire basic understanding of important issues in psycholinguistics through literature review, class discussion, and writing of a research paper.', '0', '6641Z0I1', '664A10', '語日碩10', '1262'),
(563, '538', '1131', '邱怡婷', '25161100000000 ', '25161', '919', '1', 1, 10, '兒童語言發展研究', 'Child Language Development Research', '邱怡婷', 5, 0, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F803', '1', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所聽力組與語言組合開', '本課程主要建立學生的兒童語言發展的學理及研究探討能力。課程範圍包括嬰幼兒、學齡前兒童及學齡兒童的語言發展。討論的範圍有溝通、語言及認知之間的關係、 語言習得理論、語言前期及語言期的音韻、詞彙、語法語意及語用發展。', 'This course aims to provide speech pathology students a thorough understanding of the research in the development of language. The language development of infant, toddler, preschooler, and school-age are included. Major topics include: the relation among communication, language and cognition, the theories of language development, nonverbal communication at the pre-linguistic stages and the linguistic development.', '1130', '6641Z0D1', '664A10', '語日碩10', '1130'),
(564, '539', '1131', '陳郁雯', '25161100000000 ', '25161', '922', '1', 1, 10, '發聲機轉', 'Phonation Mechanism', '陳郁雯', 6, 0, 6, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F803', '3', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所語言組', '介紹呼吸系統、喉部、以及與發聲有關的神經系統構造，聲帶振動原理，發聲壓力閾、頻率、及音量控制，與發聲機轉有關的聲學與氣動學，以及實驗室分析發聲特性。', 'To teach students phonation anatomy and physiology. In phonation anatomy, the course contents are respiratory system, laryngeal system, and phonation-related nervous system. In phonation physiology, the course contents are vocal fold oscillation, phonatio', '1160', '6641Z0G1', '664A10', '語日碩10', '1160'),
(565, '540', '1131', '巴甫仁', '25161100000000 ', '25161', '920', '1', 1, 10, '進階言語聲學', 'Advanced Speech Acoustics', '巴甫仁', 8, 0, 8, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F803', '2', '6,7,8', '修課限制：混合式遠距教學、本所聽力組與語言組合開、遠距教學課程', '本課程目的為建立學生對聲學的進階知識與應用。課程將介紹和言語相關的進階聲學概念，包括聲源濾波理論、聲帶振動模型、聲道面積函數、言語分析、言語合成。學生將獲得相關的實物操作能力，包括熟悉使用跨平臺、多功能的語音分析電腦軟體 PRAAT。學生將會熟悉使用聲學方法進行和言語異常、聽力異常相關的研究。', 'This course will provide an overview of advanced principles and applications of acoustics for speech pathology and audiology. Students will develop an understanding of advanced concepts in speech acoustics, including the acoustic theory of speech production, models of vocal fold vibration, vocal tract area functions, various approaches of speech analysis, and speech synthesis. Students will acquire a working knowledge of a versatile cross-platform computer speech analysis and synthesis software, PRAAT. Students will be able to apply acoustical methods for research studies of speech and hearing disorders.', '1144', '6641Z0E1', '664A10', '語日碩10', '1144'),
(566, '541', '1131', '翁仕明', '25161100000000 ', '25161', '921', '1', 1, 10, '語言及聽覺神經機轉', 'Neurological Mechanism Underlying Hearing &amp; Language Behavior', '翁仕明', 11, 1, 10, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F803', '5', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本所聽力組與語言組合開', '本課程將透過講演及文獻選讀的方式，介紹認識與聽力及語言相關之神經解剖構造、基礎神經生理、神經傳導、知覺處理、動作控制、認知功能、相關疾病機轉、以及神經科學研究方法等等。', 'This course will, through lectures and literature review, introduce to the students functional neuroanatomy, basic neurophysiology, neuronal signaling, sensory processing, motor control, cognitive processing, pathophysiology of common diseases, and curren', '8384', '6641Z0F1', '664A10', '語日碩10', '8384'),
(567, '542', '1131', '徐建業', '25162100000000 ', '25162', '915', '1', 1, 10, '數位訊號處理', 'Digital Signal Processing for Speech and Hearing Science', '徐建業', 2, 0, 2, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F803', '5', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所聽力組與語言組合開', '本課程為一學期之研究所選修課程，重點為介紹聽力語言相關之數位訊號處理技術及其應用，課程設計希望能在數位訊號處理基礎之外，加強理論及實際應用的討論。教學內容包括：數位訊號處理之相關數學基礎、數位訊號系統、語音認知(Speech Perception)及心理聲學(Psychoacoustics)基礎、聽覺系統的感應知覺原理、例如聽覺系統的時間解析(Temporal Resolution)及聽覺模型(Auditory Pattern and Model)，語音分析及合成原理，語音辨識及語者辨識。並利用電腦軟體，', 'This course is a one-semester course. In the Fall semester of 2013, we will focus on the fundamentals of digital signal processing applied for speech and hearing science. The course is designed not to elaborate on the digital signal processing itself but to introduce the basic concepts of signal processing and its applications for speech and hearing science. This course can be used to support other courses for the technology point of view. We will discuss some basic signal processing theory and their applications. Some reading will be assigned to the students. Computer software is also used in this course. The students will review those tools and do some analysis and processing on the signals.', '1609', '6641Z0H1', '664A10', '語日碩10', '1609'),
(568, '543', '1131', '陳郁夫', '25162200000000 ', '25162', '1826', '1', 1, 10, '聽力科學研究', 'Research in Hearing Sciences', '陳郁夫', 9, 1, 8, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F803', '2', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本所聽力組與語言組合開', '本課程之主要目的是提供聽語系學生有關聲學、聽覺系統解剖與生理及心理聲學等專業知識。本課程也會讓學生有機會進行心理聲學等與教學內容相關之實作。完成本課程後，學生將具備足夠之基本能力修習更進階的聽力學相關課程。', 'The main purpose of this course is to provide audiology students with professional knowledge about acoustics, the anatomy and physiology of the auditory system, and psychoacoustics. This course will also give students the opportunity to practice psychoacoustics and other related teaching content. After completing this course, students will have sufficient basic abilities to take more advanced audiology-related courses.', '1629', '6641Z0K1', '664A10', '語日碩10', '1629'),
(569, '544', '1131', '童寶娟', '25161200000000 ', '25161', '1825', '1', 1, 10, '聽語臨床方法', 'Clinical Methods for Speech Language Pathology and Audiology', '童寶娟', 1, 1, 0, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F803', '1', '2,3', '修課限制：本所聽力組與語言組合開', '\"本課程為培訓學生對聽語實習研究(clinical research)的基礎課程。課程內容包\r\n含：\r\n（一）臨床專業的聽力與語言治療師的評估與治療的臨床示範、教學與\r\n研究；藉由引導與討論，增進學生臨床實務與研究結合的能力，\r\n培養出學生的思考與執行能力，同時瞭解臨床研究的專業倫理與規範。\r\n（二）聽力與語言治療實作與實證：讓學生在教學場域直接進行聽力與語\r\n言治療之實作，藉由完整的為聽語言障礙進行個別化的語言評估及實證的治\r\n療法，同時精進實作技巧。\"', '\"\"\"This course is a basic course for training students in clinical research. Course content includes\r\nContains:\r\n(1) Clinical demonstration, teaching and treatment of clinical professional hearing and speech therapists\r\nResearch; through guidance and discussion, improve students’ ability to combine clinical practice with research,\r\nCultivate students\' thinking and execution abilities while understanding the professional ethics and norms of clinical research.\r\n(2) Listening and language therapy practice and evidence: Let students directly conduct listening and language therapy in the teaching field\r\nThe implementation of speech therapy through complete individualized language assessment and empirical treatment for hearing and speech disorders\r\ntherapy while improving practice skills. \"\"\"', '1622', '6641Z0J1', '664A10', '語日碩10', '1622'),
(570, '545', '1131', '張智婷', '251611231011A0', '25161', '1231', '1', 1, 0, '語言病理學論文寫作', 'Academic Writing in Speech-Language Pathology', '張智婷', 9, 0, 9, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F803', '4', '3,4', '修課限制：本所語言組', '本課程將透過教師講授、課室討論、作業活動、圖書館資料庫研習、學生課堂報告等方式，使學生習得聽語研究文獻搜尋技巧，以及科學論文寫作之架構與格式。', 'Students will learn to use discipline-specific databases to access research and to explore various issues in the field of speech-language pathology. In addition, students will also learn to apply basic rules of APA Style in scientific writing.', '691', '6641Q241', '664211', '聽語研一', '691'),
(571, '546', '1131', '張宸瑋', '251620929011A0', '25162', '929', '1', 1, 0, '聽力學專題討論(一)', 'Seminar in Audiology Ⅰ', '張宸瑋', 2, 0, 2, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F931', '3', '6,7', '修課限制：本所聽力組', '在此課程中，學生將學習論文寫作格式及研究方法。並將藉由校外學者專家進行專題演講，帶領學生熟悉聽語領域的相關研究，以為未來的碩士論文作準備。', 'This course is designed for students to familiarize with contemporary topics in the field of audiology. Invited talks and student presentations are included. Students will be required to participate and write a summary of the content of the presentations during class.', '266', '6641Q251', '664211', '聽語研一', '266'),
(572, '547', '1131', '陳雅資', '25161100000000 ', '25161', '895', '1', 2, 20, '失語症', 'Aphasia', '陳雅資', 7, 2, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F803', '3', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本所語言組二年級以上', '本課程主要討論成人失語症的溝通障礙。範圍包括神經解剖學、神經生理、失語症的介入與治療。同時也討論國語和台語失語症病人的聲調研究。', 'This course focuses on communication disorders associated with aphasia. Neuroanatomical and neurophysiological mechanisms underlying aphasia as well as knowledge of assessment, diagnosis, prognosis, and treatment are addressed.', '9060', '6642Z3J1', '664B20', '語日碩20', '9060'),
(573, '548', '1131', '張宸瑋', '25162100000000 ', '25162', '935', '1', 2, 20, '平衡系統評估', 'Evaluation of balance function', '張宸瑋', 5, 2, 3, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F1049', '2', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所聽力組', '前庭解剖與生理、一般平衡功能原理、電氣眼振圖原理、重心動搖儀原理、旋轉椅原理及平衡障礙疾患。', 'By lectures and oral presentation, understand the balance system, how it works as a team to coordinate, to compensate and to reach its goal-balance in space.', '266', '6642Z3N1', '664B20', '語日碩20', '266'),
(574, '549', '1131', '張智婷', '25161200000000 ', '25161', '1834', '1', 2, 20, '成人語言障礙研究', 'Research in Adult Communicative Disorders', '張智婷', 3, 1, 2, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F931', '5', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本所語言組二年級以上', '本課程基礎為培養學生具有評估成人語言障礙個案之能力，並提供適切介入方案與報告撰寫。課程內容包含介紹語言功能之神經解剖構造，並進一步解釋各類障礙如失語症、失智症、漸進性失語症、右腦傷、廣泛性腦創傷之病理原因與語言特徵。並透過課堂講授與實際示範標準化測驗流程，讓學生得以鑑別診斷各類語言障礙患者，以提供適切之治療方案。課程後半為進階研究，引導研究生研析成人語言障礙前瞻性文獻，並實際應用單一個案研究於實證本位介入。', 'The basis of this course is to cultivate students\' ability to evaluate adult speech disorder cases, provide appropriate intervention plans and report writing. The course content includes an introduction to the neuroanatomical structure of language function, and further explains the pathological causes and language characteristics of various disorders such as aphasia, dementia, progressive aphasia, right brain injury, and generalized brain trauma. Through classroom lectures and practical demonstrations of standardized testing procedures, students can identify and diagnose patients with various speech disorders and provide appropriate treatment plans. The second half of the course is advanced research, which guides graduate students to analyze prospective literature on adult language disorders and actually apply single case studies in evidence-based intervention.', '691', '6642Z3F1', '664B20', '語日碩20', '691'),
(575, '550', '1131', '巴甫仁', '25161100000000 ', '25161', '886', '1', 2, 20, '吞嚥異常', 'Swallowing Disorders', '巴甫仁', 11, 3, 8, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F931', '2', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本所語言組二年級以上', '吞嚥異常是讓學生從正常吞嚥構造與吞嚥機轉，探討異常的吞嚥構造及吞嚥機轉，以了解吞嚥異常原因以及其評估與治療方法。授課內容包括正常吞嚥構造與吞嚥機轉，各類型吞嚥異常，吞嚥異常評估方法，吞嚥異常治療方法，吞嚥異常團隊處置以及吞嚥異常臨床決策。', 'The goal of this course is to teach students to learn assessment and treatment methodologies of swallowing disorders from knowledge of normal and abnormal swallowing anatomy and physiology. The course content includes normal swallowing anatomy and physiology, swallowing disorders, assessments/treatments/teamwork/clinical diagnosis of swallowing disorders.', '1144', '6642Z3H1', '664B20', '語日碩20', '1144'),
(576, '551', '1131', '', '25161000000000 ', '25161', '161', '1', 2, 20, '專題研究', 'Independent Study', '巴甫仁,張智婷,邱怡婷,翁仕明,陳郁雯', 7, 3, 4, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '7', '2', '修課限制：本所語言組、書面選課、實際上課時間及地點請洽授課教師。', '撰寫論文前與指導老師之討論課程', 'Independent Study', '0', '6642Z3G1', '664B20', '語日碩20', '11,440,691,113,083,800,000'),
(577, '552', '1131', '', '25162000000000 ', '25162', '161', '1', 2, 20, '專題研究', 'Independent Study', '張宸瑋,李國熙,陳郁夫', 2, 0, 2, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '7', '2', '修課限制：本所聽力組、書面選課、實際上課時間及地點請洽授課教師。', '撰寫論文前與指導老師之討論課程', 'Independent Study', '0', '6642Z3M1', '664B20', '語日碩20', '26,616,631,629'),
(578, '553', '1131', '趙文崇', '25161100000000 ', '25161', '1069', '1', 2, 20, '診斷語言病理學', 'Differential Diagnosis in Speech-Language Pathology', '趙文崇', 12, 3, 9, 3.00, '第2,4,6,8,10,12,14,16,18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F803', '6', '2,3,4,6,7,8', '修課限制：雙數周上課', '瞭解語言病理學之機制及臨床表現、語言病理學所可能遇到之評估及鑑別診斷，使具備實證基礎的語言、言語、吞嚥障礙評估及處置所需之專業技術，清楚語言病理學之介入方針。\r\n能尊重溝通障礙之個案，建立全人關懷、尊重、同理心的專業倫理與服務態度，並瞭解聽語國際發展趨勢並養成社會參與及終身學習的精神', 'Speech and Language behavior is the most sophisticate communicating skill within human society. The ability arises from individual physical capability and acquired achievement of linguistic learning. There are various pathologic factors can compromise and distort the acquisition of this ability. The direct effect and the interaction of the these pathologic status will express different phenomenon of speech and language disorders. To learn and aware of these interaction is important for every speech and language therapist.', '1612', '6642Z3L1', '664B20', '語日碩20', '1612'),
(579, '554', '1131', '陳雅資', '25161100000000 ', '25161', '888', '1', 2, 20, '語暢異常', 'Fluency Disorders', '陳雅資', 9, 3, 6, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F931', '2', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所語言組二年級以上', '語暢異常是指說話時的言語流暢度出現障礙。依症狀及成因可分為三個類型包括口吃、迅吃以及神經性口吃。其中以口吃最廣為人知，主要是說話的流暢度及韻律出現障礙，目前成因仍未知；迅吃的特點是語速過快，導致說話急促且含糊不清並伴隨過多不流暢，可能和異常的語言及思考過程有關；神經性口吃指後天形成的不流暢，常導因於神經性疾病。', 'This course is designed to provide a comprehensive introduction of fluency disorders regarding etiology, diagnosis, and treatments. Additional skills including consulting, strategies applying, \r\nevidence-based practicing in treatment efficacy are applied.', '9060', '6642Z3I1', '664B20', '語日碩20', '9060'),
(580, '555', '1131', '陳郁夫', '25162100000000 ', '25162', '939', '1', 2, 20, '擴音系統聲學特性、選擇、評估及維護', 'Characteristics, Selection, Evaluation and Maintenance of  Amplification System', '陳郁夫', 2, 1, 1, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F931', '4', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所聽力組二年級以上', '本課程涵蓋選配及驗證擴音系統所需之相關學理知識與實務操作技能。教學內容依系統的聲電特性、選擇、評估及維護分為四大主軸，依序選讀相關文獻，並將在課中帶領學生進行實務演練，以培養學生未來進入臨床實習階段所需之專業知能。', 'This course prepares students to knowledge required for hearing aid fitting. Class readings, lectures,  discussions and hands-on experience focus on the evidence-based procedures for the audiologic management of hearing loss through amplification. The goals of this course are to provide: 1) knowledge for fitting and evaluation of hearing aid; 2) an understanding of the electroacoustic characteristics of hearing aids, the measurement of their performance; and 3) knowledge for the process of hearing aid validation/verification.', '1629', '6642Z3O1', '664B20', '語日碩20', '1629'),
(581, '556', '1131', '童寶娟', '25161100000000 ', '25161', '923', '1', 2, 20, '讀寫萌發研究', 'Studies in Emergent Literacy', '童寶娟', 7, 1, 6, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F931', '1', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所語言組二年級以上', '本課程目地為建立碩士學生之兒童讀寫萌發概念及如何促進兒童閱讀能力之實物操作能力。範圍包括兒童的讀寫發展、早期讀寫經驗(early literacy experiences ) 及讀寫知識 (literacy knowledge)。研究範圍包括1. 如何有效的與兒童共讀繪本、2.父母在家裡如何提供閱讀經驗及、3.社會文化對閱讀的價值觀。同時也探討兒童如何從這些經驗逐漸萌發對讀寫的興趣，漸漸累積建立整體的讀寫知識，這些早期讀寫知識包括：1.文字符號系統的知識、2.對母語語言聲音音韻的覺察認識、3. 理解語言文', 'This course is designed to provide students with an overview of the research in the early literacy. Three major areas are discussed, including the development of early literacy, the literacy experiences and the literacy knowledge.', '1622', '6642Z3K1', '664B20', '語日碩20', '1622'),
(582, '557', '1131', '陳郁夫', '251621233012A0', '25162', '1233', '1', 2, 0, '助聽輔具專題討論', 'Seminars in Listening Devices', '陳郁夫,徐建業', 2, 1, 1, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F1049', '4', '9,10', '修課限制：本所聽力組二年級以上', '本課程將延續「聽力學專題討論」課程之內容，更深入帶領學生進一步閱讀助聽輔具之相關研究及最新發展等。', 'This course provides students with advanced knowledge on hearing devices for hearing-impaired population.  Students will read selected journal articles on various topics in the field of hearing devices.  Latest development in hearing devices will be introduced as well.', '1629', '6642Q561', '664221', '聽語研二', '16,291,609'),
