(638, '613', '1131', '邱瓊慧', '31140000000000 ', '31140', '287', '1', 2, 20, '兒童文學', 'Children Literature', '邱瓊慧', 37, 1, 36, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'I206', '1', '3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生大二以上、教室容量40人', '本課程旨在了解兒童文學的發展源流、意義與價值。並藉由不同形式的兒童文學創作文本之賞析與評鑑，激發閱讀與研究兒童文學之興趣。並探析兒童文創產業的實務與趨勢，進而期許學生除能設計融入兒童文學的幼稚園相關課程活動外，能以更寬闖、更多元的角度與觀點來賞析兒童文學創作文本。', 'This course is designed for students who major in child care in order to equip students with the knowledge of children’s literature-poetry, story, drama…etc. It will also be expected that the student’s ability of designing the activity integrated children’s literature in this course.', '213', '4302Z471', '430B20', '嬰日四20', '213'),
(639, '614', '1131', '陳亮吟', '31140000000000 ', '31140', '454', '1', 2, 21, '0-2歲托育服務概論', 'Introduction of Infant &amp; Toddler care service', '陳亮吟', 50, 1, 49, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F414', '1', '6,7', '修課限制：本系二技一般生大二、本系四技一般生大二以上、跨校。', '本課程旨在引導學生了解-2歲托育服務的意義、各國托育模式、我國-2歲托育服務現況和政策及相關法令、督導Department、托嬰機構評鑑等，從政策面到實際面瞭解-2托育服務概觀。', 'This course is to introduce child care services for infants and toddlers in Taiwan and in other countries. Curriculum content includes the definition, functions, and types of infant and toddler care services, major theoretical approaches, and administration and delivery systems in care service. In addition, also introduce the concept of quality care services, as well as understand the characteristics and differences in child care services in different countries.', '8358', '4302Z481', '430B21', '嬰日四21', '8358'),
(640, '615', '1131', '湯佳美', '31140100000000 ', '31140', '1061', '1', 2, 21, '職場英文', 'English for the Work Place', '湯佳美', 37, 8, 29, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'B216', '3', '6,7', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放人康學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。4.全英語授課。', '本課程為一學期兩小時兩學分的課程。由英語中級程度提昇至中高級之訓練課程。教學重點為職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧及其應用。於該課程中學生能熟悉並練習職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧。', 'This is a two-hour weekly and one-semester course which is worth two credits. This is an intermediate to high-intermediate level English course. The main contents of the course consist of: common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, communication skills in workplace, and the application of communication skills. In this course, students are expected: (a) to become familiar with common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, and communication skills; and (b) to apply common English vocabulary in workplace and business English dialogue expressions to their everyday English conversations.', '866', '4302F471', '430BBA', '人英二21', '866'),
(641, '616', '1131', '潘敏', '31140000000000 ', '31140', '485', '1', 2, 22, '幼兒體能', 'Child Physical Ability', '潘敏', 41, 0, 41, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'I206', '5', '6,7', '1.修課限制：本系二技一般生大二、本系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技一般生大二、外系四技一般生大二以上、跨域課程。\n2.教室容量限40人。', '本課程透過幼兒的生理、社會化、情緒、認知、音樂性和創造力等發展面向，引領學生探討肢體動作所扮演的角色；課程輔以音樂增進動作經驗，逐步使學生體認到設計幼兒體能課程所需考慮之各種要素，同時啟發學生將幼兒體能與其他課程領域結合，建構出更紮實、更有效益的課程論述與實踐。', 'The course of Child Physical Ability is organized into four parts covering theory, research, assessment, and intervention. It focuses on the phases of child motor development, physical ability in particular, and provides a solid introduction to the biolog.', '1248', '4302Z491', '430B22', '嬰日四22', '1248'),
(642, '617', '1131', '湯佳美', '31140100000000 ', '31140', '1061', '1', 2, 22, '職場英文', 'English for the Work Place', '湯佳美', 39, 8, 31, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'B216', '3', '8,9', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放人康學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。4.全英語授課。', '本課程為一學期兩小時兩學分的課程。由英語中級程度提昇至中高級之訓練課程。教學重點為職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧及其應用。於該課程中學生能熟悉並練習職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧。', 'This is a two-hour weekly and one-semester course which is worth two credits. This is an intermediate to high-intermediate level English course. The main contents of the course consist of: common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, communication skills in workplace, and the application of communication skills. In this course, students are expected: (a) to become familiar with common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, and communication skills; and (b) to apply common English vocabulary in workplace and business English dialogue expressions to their everyday English conversations.', '866', '4302F471', '430BBB', '人英二22', '866'),
(643, '618', '1131', '陳紀萍', '311400495012A0', '31140', '495', '1', 2, 0, '兒童行為觀察與紀錄', 'Observations and Recording of Children Behavior', '陳紀萍', 67, 1, 66, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F302', '4', '1,2', '幼四二AB合開，修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、本所與國際蒙特梭利專班（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、維持十八週課程。', '本課程在培養學生具備兒童行為觀察與紀錄的知識與技能，並透過實際的觀察與紀錄練習，使學生更能了解嬰幼兒的各階段發展情形，以便將來在托兒所職場上能夠提供有助嬰幼兒發展與成長的最適當環境與教保方式，及增進幼兒教保的實務能力。', 'This course is designed for training students’ knowledge and skills in child behavior observation and recording, through actual observations and record keeping. The purpose of this course is to improve students’ understanding of different child developmen.', '901', '4302Q481', '430421', '幼四二Ａ', '901'),
(644, '619', '1131', '林炫沛', '311400442012A0', '31140', '442', '1', 2, 0, '嬰幼兒身體評估', 'Physical Assessment of Infant and Child', '林炫沛,詹偉添', 67, 1, 66, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F302', '5', '8,9', '幼四二AB合開，修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上。', '由小兒臨床醫師，以每週4小時的時間，介紹兒科嬰幼兒的生長、發育、疾病、保健及健康照護等相關之問題。', 'Lectures described on the normal growth and development of infant and toddlers and theirs relative diseases.', '906', '4302Q451', '430421', '幼四二Ａ', '9,060,453'),
(645, '620', '1131', '楊金寶', '311400443012A0', '31140', '443', '1', 2, 0, '嬰幼兒保育', 'Generality of Infant and Child Care', '楊金寶', 66, 1, 65, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F302', '2', '2,3,4', '幼四二AB合開，修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、本所與國際蒙特梭利專班（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、維持十八週課程。', '本課程設計旨在協助學生獲得和運用有關兒童養育照護、教育、機構經營管理等知識，以問題解決及發展理論的觀點，評估學齡前兒童生理發展的關鍵、成長變化之挑戰及常見之社會問題。運用演說、討論、演練等過程，協助學生獲得幼兒照護知能以及自我成長。', 'The purpose of this course is to help the pupils to have the knowledge of child care technique. With the viewpoints of problem solving and developing theory, the pupils learn how to evaluate the key points of physical development of the preschool children.', '920', '4302Q461', '430421', '幼四二Ａ', '920'),
(646, '621', '1131', '何文君', '311400447012A0', '31140', '447', '1', 2, 0, '嬰幼兒遊戲', 'Infant and Child Play', '何文君', 66, 1, 65, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F302', '2', '6,7,8', '幼四二AB合開，修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上。', '遊戲係嬰幼兒生活中的主要活動。嬰幼兒不但從遊戲中得到樂趣，更透過遊戲來瞭解周遭生活世界，消化日常生活經驗。在遊戲中嬰幼兒之體能、創造力、認知能力、社會情緒能力等各方面均得以發展；即遊戲促進嬰幼兒身心健康且與學習緊密結合。本課程主要內容包含遊戲之基本概念、遊戲理論、遊戲與身心發展之關係、遊戲行為之發展、遊戲之觀察、遊戲素材與安全、物理環境設計、以及成人在嬰幼兒遊戲中應當扮演之角色；學生應根據課堂所學，依嬰幼兒之發展差異進行遊戲活動設計。', 'Play enhances both physical and mental health of children and is the Way it learns. The major contents for this class include：theories of play； the relationship between play and the physical-mental development；development of play behavior；play observation；play materials；physic environmental design. Students will also be able to design play for children in its different development stages by using what they learned in this course.', '1093', '4302Q471', '430421', '幼四二Ａ', '1093'),
(647, '622', '1131', '朝日美智代', '311400027012A0', '31140', '27', '1', 2, 0, '藝術文化史', 'History of Artistic Culture', '朝日美智代', 69, 3, 66, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'G202', '1', '1,2', '1.第二階段開放修習「藝術文化史/世界文明史」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。\n2.全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '透過藝術文化的類型與不同的表現形式及中西方藝術的演進與賞析，瞭解藝術的理念、內涵與歷史演變，深入探討藝術與生命、美感與生活、藝術與文化等重要議題之意義。培養學生對藝術文化有基本的認識與高度的敏感度，提升審美素養，持續自主學習的興趣。', 'Through the exploration of various types and form of art and culture, as well as the evolution and appreciation of Eastern and Western art, this course provides an understanding of the concepts, meaning and historical transformations of arts. It further delves deeply into significant topics such as art and life, aesthetics and everyday life, and art and culture. Students will acquire a foundational comprehension and heightened sensitivity of art and culture, enhance their aesthetic literacy, and foster a sustained commitment to self-directed education.', '9808', '4302F451', '430421', '幼四二Ａ', '9808'),
(648, '623', '1131', '廖莉安', '311401712012A0', '31140', '1712', '1', 2, 0, '體育-羽球1', 'PE-Badminton1', '廖莉安', 49, 5, 44, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '4', '8,9', '1.第一階段志願選，僅由幼四二A、幼四二B、護四二A、休四三A互相跨班選課。 \n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。 \n3.上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。\n4. 跨校。', '利用循序漸進的教學方式，教導學生羽球的基本動作，\r\n透過對羽球基本動作的熟練，進而提昇學生對羽球比賽的興趣、享受羽球運動的樂趣。\r\n講授羽球運動的規則及比賽策略。強調運動員必須在規則範圍內做合法的競賽，透過羽\r\n球運動來幫助學生守法、守分與合作的精神，並協助運動習慣的養成，期望學生能以羽\r\n球運動作為終身運動。', 'The content of course is to instruct students’ badminton skill by using step-bystep teaching method. Over the basic movement of the skilled is to enhance \r\nthe students\' interest in badminton game and enjoyment the fun of \r\nbadminton. The rules and strategies of teaching badminton to emphasize that \r\nathletes must be legitimate competition in the scope of the rules through the \r\nsport of badminton to help students to obey the law, be law-abiding and \r\ncooperation spirit, Therefor, students are expected to develop the habit of \r\nexercise and to choice badminton as a lifetime of activity.', '8401', '4302F481', '430421', '幼四二Ａ', '8401'),
(649, '624', '1131', '孫沛婕', '31140000000000 ', '31140', '214', '1', 3, 30, '幼兒英語教學', 'English Teaching for Young Children', '孫沛婕,郭蕙琪', 44, 0, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'I206', '4', '8,9', '1.修課限制：本系二技一般生大二、本系四技一般生大二以上。\n2.教室容量限40人。EMI全英語授課', '透過概念介紹、討論各類相關美語教學概念，進而強化學子設計幼兒美語課程能力及教學執行。', 'Through the introduction of sorts of concepts involving with reading, writing, listening and speaking teaching and learning to students, also gradually building up the students’ abilities to collect, analyze and assemble the teaching materials through the design of lesson plans to present the young kids wonderful and cultural English programs.', '1159', '4303Z471', '430C30', '嬰日四30', '11,591,110'),
(650, '625', '1131', '陳俊全', '31140000000000 ', '31140', '489', '1', 3, 31, '兒童保護', 'Child Protect', '陳俊全', 44, 1, 43, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F301', '4', '6,7', '修課限制：本系二技一般生大二、本系四技一般生大二以上。\n', '本課程旨在協助學生瞭解兒童保護之相關概念與理論，包含基礎與實務工作現況等，透過課堂講授與討論、影片觀摩等方式，廣泛討論包含兒童虐待之種類與成因、相關之立法與保護措施、福利機構與保護服務流程等，期使學生在從事教保或托育服務時能更有效地面對並因應兒童虐待與保護之相關議題。', 'This course aims at guiding students to understand relevant theoretical foundations and practice of child protection, through multiple type of studying plan, include lecture, film editing and study, moot court and discuss, etc. These teaching activities could help students extensively knowing types and causes of children maltreat, including relevant legislations and protective procedures, child welfare organizations and child welfare service procedures, etc.', '942', '4303Z451', '430C31', '嬰日四31', '942'),
(651, '626', '1131', '朱俐蓉', '31140100000000 ', '31140', '502', '1', 3, 32, '嬰兒活動設計與環境規劃', 'Infants and Toddlers Environment and Instruction', '朱俐蓉', 54, 0, 54, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'I206,I501', '3', '6,7', '1.修課限制：本系二技一般生大二、本系四技一般生大二以上。\n2.教室容量限40人。', '本課程旨在瞭解如何規劃、設計、與呈現適合嬰兒發展與學習的活動與學習環境。課程內容奠基於瞭解嬰幼兒由出生至2歲間各階段的發展特點與學習需要，並學習如何根據嬰幼兒的不同需求，設計與規劃適性發展的嬰幼兒學習活動及探索空間。本課程對有志進入嬰兒相關領域職場者，可以增進相關課程與教學的概念及技能。', 'This course is aimed to explore how to design and present instruction and environments appropriate \r\nfor infants and toddlers. It focuses on planning, arranging learning areas within indoor and outdoor \r\nspaces in preschool. Contents of this course include understanding the unique developmental and \r\nlearning needs of infants and toddlers, principles of designing instruction, and guidelines for the design and arrangement of learning environments. This course will be helpful for students interested in working in family daycare or center care facilities.', '8380', '4303Z461', '430C32', '嬰日四32', '8380'),
(652, '627', '1131', '歐姿秀', '311400472013A0', '31140', '472', '1', 3, 0, '幼兒園教材教法I', 'Teaching Materials and Methods for Young Children I', '歐姿秀,陳香娟', 32, 0, 32, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F301', '4', '1,2', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大三以上、本所與國際蒙特梭利專班（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、維持十八週課程。', '課程設計與教學能力係屬幼兒教保工作人員之專業能力，為提升教保品質之基本條件，不可或缺。衡量當今幼兒教育思潮、幼兒發展需求與社會發展狀況，本課程從統整理念出發，依據「幼兒園教保活動與課程大綱」（新課綱）之精神及內涵，幫助學生建立以幼兒為中心之幼兒教材教法觀念、培養學生實際進行幼兒教保活動之能力。主要內容包含瞭解幼兒園教學之理念與實務，認識新課綱身體動作與健康領域、語文領域、社會領域之課程目標與學習指標，以及各領域之教學內容與教學方法，包含學習區教學。學生應能根據課堂所學，設計教學活動並實施，之後進行檢討。', 'Course Description：\r\n\r\nThe purposes of this course are to explore the characteristics, contents, and trends of teaching methods and materials for preschoolers. Due to the limitation of course schedule, this course will focus on six major child development aspects. The contents focus both theories and practices in this topics. Students will also be able to design different lesson plans for children in its different development stages by using what they learned in this course.', '1504', '4303Q461', '430431', '幼四三A ', '15,041,078');
INSERT INTO `課程` (`編號`, `課程編號`, `學期`, `主開課教師姓名`, `科目代碼_新碼`, `系所代碼`, `核心四碼`, `科目組別`, `年級`, `上課班組`, `科目中文名稱`, `科目英文名稱`, `授課教師姓名`, `上課人數`, `男學生上課人數`, `女學生上課人數`, `學分數`, `上課週次`, `上課時數_週`, `課別代碼`, `課別名稱`, `上課地點`, `上課星期`, `上課節次`, `課表備註`, `課程中文摘要`, `課程英文摘要`, `主開課教師代碼_舊碼`, `科目代碼_舊碼`, `課表代碼_舊碼`, `課表名稱_舊碼`, `授課教師代碼_舊碼`) VALUES
(653, '628', '1131', '李佳馨', '311400031013A0', '31140', '31', '1', 3, 0, '哲學與人生', 'Philosophy and Life', '李佳馨', 64, 8, 56, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'G101', '3', '8,9', '1.第二階段開放修習「哲學與人生/邏輯概論」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。\n2.全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '「哲學與人生」是對「人的生命」所作的「哲學反省」。人，作為自然的、社會的、歷史的存在，在他所生活的世界中，面臨著繁複多樣、瞬息萬變的問題：處境、命運、愛情、知識、道德、藝術、宗教、臨終與死亡……其中有些問題事實上已經深深困擾著我們，另外一些則伺機突襲，在我們還來不及準備的時候，就被迫面對。生命的意義究竟是什麼？本課程嘗試以深入淺出的討論，藉由過去、當代人物的所感、所思，促進學習者進一步反省自我生命之種種。', 'Philosophy and Life is as a philosophical reflective thinking for the life.\r\nHuman beings, as natural, social and historical beings, face a great many complex varied and fast changing problems in the life-world, for example, love, destiny, knowledge, morality, art, religion, dying, and moreover the death so on.... Actually some of them have deeply perplexed us, while others watch for their chances to attack there would leave no time for covering our ears and we are merely compelled to confront with them. After all, what does Life mean?\r\nWhereas this course tries to take up by the way a kind of discussion in explaining the profound in simple terms, and in making use of whatever in history, or the present age somebody\'s feeling and thinking, in order to promote the students to question themselves more about, and reflect further on all sorts of life-self.', '157', '4303F251', '430431', '幼四三A ', '157'),
(654, '629', '1131', '謝亞恆', '311400498013A0', '31140', '498', '1', 3, 0, '嬰幼兒特殊教育概論', 'Special Education for Preschools with Special Needs', '謝亞恆', 67, 0, 67, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F301', '2', '2,3,4', '幼四三AB合開，修課限制：本系四技一般生大三以上、本所與國際蒙特梭利專班（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、維持十八週課程、跨校。', '從嬰幼兒特殊需要意義討論到各種不同需求的特質，進而瞭解未來願景，係本課程的重點。 特殊需要嬰幼兒早期介入的基本精神在於早期發現、早期治療。在課程中透過各種障礙類別定義與特質的介紹，並說明有關鑑定評估與安置處遇基本概念，希望能提供學生對特殊需要嬰幼兒有正確的認識。並對介入特殊需要嬰幼兒的方式與流程有所瞭解，以培養學生從事特殊需要嬰幼兒保育的興趣與熱誠。 課程裡也將國內現有早期療育工作的規畫與進行情況作一完整的介紹，希望學生畢業投入嬰幼兒保育工作後，碰上有特殊需要嬰幼兒保育問題時，能知道諮詢與轉介的單位。', 'This class will introduce the theory for early intervention, the categories and characteristics of exceptional young children, the needs of the families with exceptional young children, the laws and the future about early intervention。', '1229', '4303Q471', '430431', '幼四三A ', '1229'),
(655, '630', '1131', '朱郁文', '311400440013A0', '31140', '440', '1', 3, 0, '嬰幼兒教保專業倫理', 'Professional Ethics of Infant and Child Care', '朱郁文', 66, 0, 66, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F301', '5', '6,7', '幼四三AB合開，修課限制：本系四技一般生大三以上、本所與國際蒙特梭利專班（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、維持十八週課程。', '本課程第一階段將探討嬰幼兒保育重要議題與現況、了解嬰幼兒保育工作之內容、教保人員角色、以及職業道德的意義。第二階段將探討嬰幼兒保育工作可能面臨之各種倫理問題，並利用討論與分享的方式培養解決問題及反思成長的能力。', 'Professional Ethics are the moral commitments of a profession that involve moral reflection that extends and Teacher’s academic 0code:09460946 09466enhances the personal morality practitioners bring to their work, that concern actions of right and wrong in the workplace, and that help individuals resolve moral dilemmas they encounter in their work. Childhood is a \r\nunique and valuable stage in the human life cycle. Our paramount responsibility is to provide care and \r\neducation in settings that are safe, healthy, nurturing, and responsive for each child. We are committed to supporting children’s development and learning; respecting individual differences; and helping children learn to \r\nlive, play, and work cooperatively. We are also committed to promoting children’s self-awareness, competence, self-worth, resiliency, and physical well-being.The purpose of the course is to establish student work ethics in the field of early childhood education and care. The instructions of the courses include instructor’s lectures, discussions between the student and instructor, group discussions and oral report.', '219', '4303Q441', '430431', '幼四三A ', '219'),
(656, '631', '1131', '楊曉苓', '311400446013A0', '31140', '446', '1', 3, 0, '嬰幼兒學習環境設計', 'Planning of Learning Environments for Infants and Young Children', '楊曉苓', 33, 0, 33, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'I303,I304', '2', '6,6,7,7,8,8', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大三以上。\n教室：I304、I303(後六週)，請洽授課教師。', '本課程旨在探討如何規畫與設計嬰幼兒的學習環境。課程內容著重於嬰幼兒托育機構之學習環境設計，除探討學習環境對嬰幼兒之潛在影響、學習環境設計之基本原理原則外，並著眼於嬰幼兒學習環境設計之實務，與各類型學習區之規畫與管理。學生於課堂中透過一系列的練習活動與實務演練，除練習設計嬰兒之教保環境外，並學習依照課程主題創造統整情境、規劃且佈置數個完整的學習區。', 'This course is aimed to explore how to create and design learning environments appropriate for infants and young children. It focuses on planning, arranging learning areas within indoor and outdoor spaces in preschool. Contents of this course include principles for the design of classrooms and other learning spaces, guidelines for the design and arrangement of learning centers, and observation and evaluation skills of learning centers. Students will explore, plan, arrange, and evaluate the design of various learning areas.', '903', '4303Q451', '430431', '幼四三A ', '903'),
(657, '632', '1131', '許均宇', '311401717013A0', '31140', '1717', '1', 3, 0, '體育-桌球3', 'PE-Table Tennis3', '許均宇', 50, 9, 41, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '3', '3,4', '1.第一階段志願選，僅由健四三A、健四三B、幼四三A、幼四三B互相跨班選課。 \n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。 \n3.上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。 \n4.跨校。 ', '此課程是先學習與養成良好的基本技術與接發球技術後\r\n再加強雙打戰術理論與應用。學習「雙打戰術理論模式」就是以理論為基礎，以提升雙\r\n打戰術觀念。而雙打注重的是技術與兩位球員搭配之默契並運用各種戰術以全面、快速、\r\n變化之打法獲得有效之成果或在比賽中贏取勝利。', 'In this course, a player should learn and cultivate good basic skills and the \r\nskills in receiving and serving the ball first, and then reinforce the theory and \r\napplications of doubles tactics. To learn “the model of doubles tactics theory” \r\nis to enhance the concept of doubles tactics based on theories. In doubles, the \r\nskills and the unspoken consensus of cooperation between the two players \r\nare emphasized; also, various kinds of tactics are applied, so as to use \r\ncomprehensive, rapid and variable playing skills to obtain effective results or \r\ntriumph.', '9133', '4303F241', '430431', '幼四三A ', '9133'),
