(673, '640', '1131', '邱瓊慧', '31160100000000 ', '31160', '763', '1', 1, 10, '各國托育問題探討', 'Child Care Issue Around The World', '邱瓊慧', 16, 0, 16, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'I305', '1', '8,9,10', '修課限制：本所。', '本課程旨在探究世界主要國家在學前幼兒的教育和保育的相關議題。其中又以美、英日德芬蘭、瑞典、紐澳等國家為主，探究各國之學前幼兒教育和保育相關制度與政策，以及遭遇到的問題與困境。透過比較教育的研究方法，分析比較各主要國家的學前教保議題。', 'The course is aimed to explore child care service around the world, including the basic\r\nknowledge and theories of child care service, issues of the changes of family function and child\r\ncare services for children aged from 0?12. To be specific, the content includes issues of the changes\r\nof family function and child care needs, models of sharing child care responsibilities, the\r\ndevelopment of childcare services, the characteristics of child care services, family policy and child\r\ncare policy, international comparison of family and child care services. In addition, this course\r\nincludes development and trends of child care policy and laws, and international comparison of\r\nchild care policies.Students are expected to have a comprehensive understanding of child care servicesaround the world and acquire abilities to discuss child care issues.', '213', '6301Z181', '630A10', '嬰日碩10', '213'),
(674, '641', '1131', '謝亞恆', '311600740011A0', '31160', '740', '1', 1, 0, '進階社會科學統計', 'Advanced Statistics in Social Science', '謝亞恆', 9, 0, 9, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'I305', '3', '8,9,10', '修課限制：本所。', '本課程旨在增進學生詮釋與應用健康科學相關之統計方法。課程設計運用實際資料分析的經驗，使學生能了解統計應用之意義，並激發學生研究之興趣。課程內容包括社會統計學之概念與方法，各類統計模式、統計分析之技術、統計圖之使用及製作、統計軟體SPSS之操作學習與資料分析之應用等。強調學生能從實際資料分析之經驗中，使其能應用適當之統計方法，解決專業上的各種研究問題。', 'The course is designed to provide an education that students will understand and interest the specialty of social statistics, and foster ability for independent thinking and solving problems. This course contents include statistical graphs, summary Statistics, probability distribution, significant tests, ANOVA (one way and two way), regression analysis (simple and multiple regression), model selections, design of questionnaire, factor analysis, reliability, and nonparametric approaches.', '1229', '6301Q591', '630211', '幼保研一', '1229'),
(675, '642', '1131', '段慧瑩', '311600741011A0', '31160', '741', '1', 1, 0, '嬰幼兒教保服務專題', 'Special Issues in Early Childhood Education and Care Services', '段慧瑩', 9, 0, 9, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'I305', '6', '2,3,4', '1.修課限制：本所。\n2.ESP課程。', '課程之宗旨為培養學生以文件分析法探討有關幼兒教育及照顧、兒童福利、兒童托育服務等之政策、法規、社會事件等相關議題。本課程閱讀的文件以經濟合作暨發展組織（簡稱:經合組織：Organization for Economic Co-operation and Development，OECD）A Quality Toolbox for Early Childhood Education and Care-III，如何提升一個國家的教保生態達到優質的境界為主軸，並探討2011年我國幼托整合後在嬰幼兒教保政策、課程、教保人員的資格與薪資福利、家園社區的合作、研究與輔導及評鑑等政策的實施至今與OECD的標準比較。以及從達到教保優質的水準，我國幼托政策的可能的作為為何？', 'It is important to recognize the trend of development of early childhood education and care from the concepts of OECD. The aim of the course is to analyze Taiwan’s early childhood education from the views of OECD. Thus the purposes of the course are: to explore the evolution of educare services;recognize the significances and functions of educare services;investigate the types of as well as delivery and management systems of domestic child care services;analyze child care service policies; and to understand trends in international child care services\r\nCourse contents include the research papers, articles and all kinds of documents related to educare services.\r\nSince most of the materials are written in English, it is required all the students need to familiar with the materials before they attend the class.', '1503', '6301Q601', '630211', '幼保研一', '1503'),
(676, '643', '1131', '陳俊全', '311600744011A0', '31160', '744', '1', 1, 0, '嬰幼兒福利服務專論', 'Special Topics on the Welfare Service for Infants and Young Children', '陳俊全', 20, 0, 20, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'I304', '4', '8,9,10', '修課限制：本所', '透過嬰幼兒相關福利服務措施的介紹與議題的討論，協助學生了解兒童福利的意涵、認識兒童的各種福利服務工作之原則與方法，配合兒童福利相關政策、法規、實務的檢討，使同學認識目前兒童福利服務所遭遇的重要課題。', 'Through the discussion with topic of relevant welfare services for infant and pre-school children, this seminar course could help students understanding meaning of child welfare service, various welfare principle and method of services, and some relevant', '942', '6301Q611', '630211', '幼保研一', '942'),
(677, '644', '1131', '', '31160000000000 ', '31160', '161', '1', 2, 20, '專題研究', 'Independent Study', '歐姿秀,陳紀萍,楊曉苓,段慧瑩,謝亞恆,孫沛婕,何文君', 16, 0, 16, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '7', '1', '1.書面選課、實際上課時間及地點請洽授課教師。\n2.修課限制：本所二年級以上學生。', '本課程旨在增進學生對研究的了解並提昇其研究能力。課程內容包括：依學生個人興趣擬定方向，進行文獻的查閱與整理、發現問題、進行探究，以期能發展出具專業性及學術性之研究計畫。藉由整信課程內容的設計，培養學生邏輯思考能力。學生將可在所選的教授指導下，進行個人有興趣之專題研究。', 'This course offers students opportunities to improve their research capabilities. The topics covered in this course include selecting research topics, doing literature reviews, identifying research questions, exploring problems, and developing professional research proposals. By conducting individual study of a selected topic with faculty guidance, students will improve their ability to think in a logical way and learn how to evaluate a research design.', '0', '6302Z141', '630B20', '嬰日碩20', '1,504,090,109,031,500,000,000,000,000'),
(678, '645', '1131', '', '311600300012A0', '31160', '300', '1', 2, 0, '碩士論文', 'Thesis', '歐姿秀,邱瓊慧,段慧瑩,何文君', 4, 1, 3, 6.00, '全18週', 6.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '2', '1.書面選課、實際上課時間及地點請洽授課教師。\n2.修課限制：本所二年級以上學生，須通過本所論文計畫口試者3個月後方可提學位考試。', '本課程主要目標在引導學生在嬰幼兒保育相關領域內，能對特定主題進行原創性實證研究，並作為完成碩士學位的重要工作。學生在指導教授的指導下，能建立特定的研究議題、進行嚴謹的文獻探討、選擇合宜的研究方法、符合學術專業倫理下執行研究，將研究結果撰寫論文並舉行口試。', 'The primary objective of this course is to guide students in conducting original empirical research on specific topics in the field of infant and child care, fulfilling the requirements for the completion of a master\'s degree. Under the guidance of their advisors, students will establish specific research topics, conduct rigorous literature reviews, select appropriate research methods, adhere to academic and professional ethics, write research papers, and participate in oral examinations.', '0', '6302Q231', '630221', '幼保研二', '1,504,021,315,031,090'),
(679, '646', '1131', '馮麗琦', '311800488012A0', '31180', '488', '1', 2, 0, '幼兒園班級經營', 'Preschool Classroom Management', '馮麗琦', 30, 0, 30, 2.00, '第2,4,6,8,10,12,14,16,18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G403', '6', '6,7,8,9', '修課限制：本系學士後、維持十八週課程、雙數周上課。', '探討幼兒園課室經營相關之理論與研究、幼兒園課室經營之實施原則及相關策略，透過幼兒園的現場實例介紹、實地觀察、教學環境設計與活動實做，熟練學習環境與幼兒學習的相關性。包括課程與教學、學習環境規劃、學前融合教育、輔導策略、親師溝通、家園合作等實務探討。', 'This paper explores the theories and research related to preschool classroom management, the implementation principles and related strategies of preschool classroom management, and the relevance of proficient learning environment and children\'s learning through on-site examples, field observations, teaching environment design and activity implementation. It includes practical discussions on curriculum and teaching, learning environment planning, preschool integrated education, tutoring strategies, parent-teacher communication, and home cooperation.', '1243', '2302Q661', '230225', '幼保學二', '1243'),
