(735, '698', '1131', '周雪棻', '1C1201510012A0', '1C120', '1510', '1', 2, 0, '婦女健康照護(二)', 'Women Health Care (Ⅱ)', '周雪棻', 25, 1, 24, 2.00, '第1~9週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G308', '4', '1,2,3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生二年級，本所(本國生)、密集前九週。', '本課程乃以婦女為中心的健康出發，藉由生命週期所經歷的生命事件，探討不同年齡層婦女面臨之健康問題，並從身、心、靈、社會及文化各層面關注婦女的健康，期望培育學生能以正向、積極的態度正是婦女健康，並將其應用於生活及臨床工作中，達到促進及維護婦女健康之目的。', 'This course will enable students to develop a body of knowledge related to health care of women. Women’s health will be understood and explored from physical, psychological, social, spiritual, and culture aspects and life events. The course will assist students to learn how to promote and maintain health, within the context of women’s lives.', '8408', '2622Q461', '262221', '助二二A ', '8408'),
(736, '699', '1131', '陳莉莉', '1C1200305012A0', '1C120', '305', '1', 2, 0, '專業與倫理', 'Profession and ethics', '陳莉莉', 25, 1, 24, 2.00, '第1~9週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G308', '1', '1,2,3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生二年級，本所(本國生)、密集前九週。', '旨在使學生獲得專業與倫理之基本知識、概念及各種婦女健康照護及助產倫理困境之分析與決策能力，進而激發學生發展批判性的倫理思考與判斷之潛能。課程內容以專業倫理之基本概念及倫理理論與原則之婦女健康照護及助產實務應用為主，包含價值觀與衝突、倫理與道德觀、病人權利與責任、助產師的權利與責任、倫理理論、基本倫理原則、倫理困境與倫理決策等之分析與討論。', 'The purposes of this course are to help students to gain the basic knowledge, concepts and standardized behavior of women health care and midwifery ethics, to distinguish clinical ethical issues, as well as the ability to analyze and make decisions of ethical dilemma in order to urge them to develop critical thinking and proper judgment. The concepts of this course focus on the ethical basic concepts and the application of ethical principles: including the analysis and discussion of ethics and moral concepts; the formation and conflicts of values, the rights and responsibilities of patients and midwives; the cooperational relationships of medical team; application the main theories and principles of ethics; nursing and midwifery code, ethical dilemma, and the ethical decision framework.', '169', '2622Q431', '262221', '助二二A ', '169'),
(737, '700', '1131', '高美玲', '1C1201423012A0', '1C120', '1423', '1', 2, 0, '實證健康照護', 'Evidence-based practice in healthcare', '高美玲', 25, 1, 24, 2.00, '第1~9週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F604,F603', '2', '1,2', '1.修課限制：本系二技一般生二年級，本所(本國生)、密集前九週。\n2.上課時間：週二/1-2上課教室F604、週五/6-7上課教室F603。', '本課程目標在協助學生獲得實證健康照護相關的知識與技能。課程以執行實證五步驟為架構，內容包含:介紹實證健康照護概念、提出實證可以回答的臨床問題(PICO)、文獻資料庫與搜尋最佳證據、評析文獻與實證護理應用。實作方面包含:運用學習小組練習以PICO詢問臨床問題、搜尋回答問題之最佳證據、練習評讀隨機控制研究、判斷證據等級、提出臨床決策建議及閱讀系統性文獻回顧文章。', 'This course aims to introduce evidence-based practice in Healthcare and strengthen knowledge and skills of evidence-based nursing for nursing students. Course contents include foundational concepts of evidence-based practice, concepts of systematic review and clinical guideline, PICO, searching for the current best evidence, methodology appraisal, and analyzing data. Students will have the opportunity to practice skills of using PICO to ask answerable clinical questions, searching the evidence and assessing quality of a randomized controlled trial, levels of evidence, and reading articles of systematic review.', '853', '2622Q451', '262221', '助二二A ', '853'),
(738, '700', '1131', '高美玲', '1C1201423012A0', '1C120', '1423', '1', 2, 0, '實證健康照護', 'Evidence-based practice in healthcare', '高美玲', 25, 1, 24, 2.00, '第1~9週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F604,F603', '5', '6,7', '1.修課限制：本系二技一般生二年級，本所(本國生)、密集前九週。\n2.上課時間：週二/1-2上課教室F604、週五/6-7上課教室F603。', '本課程目標在協助學生獲得實證健康照護相關的知識與技能。課程以執行實證五步驟為架構，內容包含:介紹實證健康照護概念、提出實證可以回答的臨床問題(PICO)、文獻資料庫與搜尋最佳證據、評析文獻與實證護理應用。實作方面包含:運用學習小組練習以PICO詢問臨床問題、搜尋回答問題之最佳證據、練習評讀隨機控制研究、判斷證據等級、提出臨床決策建議及閱讀系統性文獻回顧文章。', 'This course aims to introduce evidence-based practice in Healthcare and strengthen knowledge and skills of evidence-based nursing for nursing students. Course contents include foundational concepts of evidence-based practice, concepts of systematic review and clinical guideline, PICO, searching for the current best evidence, methodology appraisal, and analyzing data. Students will have the opportunity to practice skills of using PICO to ask answerable clinical questions, searching the evidence and assessing quality of a randomized controlled trial, levels of evidence, and reading articles of systematic review.', '853', '2622Q451', '262221', '助二二A ', '853'),
(739, '701', '1131', '邱慧洳', '1C1200026012A0', '1C120', '26', '1', 2, 0, '應用法規導論', 'Introduction of Professional Law', '邱慧洳', 30, 1, 29, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F303', '5', '1,2', '1.第二階段開放修習護理/高照/醫教/助產/健管/長照/聽語「應用法規導論」課程之學生互相跨班選課。\n2.重修生請自第二階段開放選課。全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '本課程醫護法學之介紹，使學生對法律結構、法學理念及我國現行法有一整體性的認知，以奠定法學啟發基礎。從醫護正義概念出發，就醫護法規、醫護法制、護理法律責任與訴訟、醫護人員切身法律問題等，深入淺出有系統的介紹，以培養現代醫護人員正確的法律觀。並從醫護業務與法律實務的角度，點出護理人員與其他醫事人員的責任分際、臨床醫護人員與公共衛生醫護人員面臨法律問題的不同、醫病糾紛的預防與處理等，以強化醫護人員處理法律問題的能力。', 'This subject is taught by way of the introduction of the basic law to let the students to understand the whole outline of the construction of law，the virtue of the jurisprudence and the  present law in Taiwan.  It begins as the teaching of the concept of the professional justice and is succeeded by introducing the medical and nursing law，the institution of the professional law，the responsibility and litigation as well as the professional liability of the member of professional society to ensure the students to know the exact concept of the law and to develop problem-solving abilities .', '1022', '2622F081', '262221', '助二二A ', '1022'),
(740, '702', '1131', '陳姿伶', '1C1200306012A0', '1C120', '306', '1', 2, 0, '醫療組織與管理', 'Health Organization and Management', '陳姿伶', 25, 1, 24, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G308', '5', '3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生二年級，本所(本國生)。', '本課程目的在於讓學生了解醫療組織的特性與醫療機構組織基本架構，並教導學生探討目前台灣醫療機構所面臨的環境因素以及實際醫院應對措施。並實際舉例說明和參訪中央健保局以及財團法人醫院評鑑暨醫療品質策進會(醫策會)。', 'This is an introduction course to organization and management in health organization and health industry. Both theory and application in major topics of management process and organizational theories will be covered. It is designed by lecture and case discussion for each topic.', '9975', '2622Q441', '262221', '助二二A ', '9975'),
(741, '703', '1131', '高美玲', '1C160161901110', '1C160', '1619', '1', 1, 10, '護理助產學實習(一)', 'Nurse-Midwifery Practicum Ι', '高美玲', 1, 0, 1, 3.00, '全18週', 9.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '6', '7', '1.實習課程。\n2.實際上課時間及地點請洽授課教師。維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）\n3.本所國內碩士班', '此課程旨在協助學生發展專業助產的能力，統整並能運用相關學理，增進助產臨床照護低危險妊娠經驗，實習內容於婦產科門診實施產前檢查、身體評估、健康指導、子宮頸抹片檢查、產後檢查等。', 'This course is designed to prepare nurses for specialization in midwifery practice. The application of knowledge gained from the lecture into the midwifery care of the low risk and high-risk woman and family is the focus of the practicum. Management ability, communication, and negotiation are also the focus of the course. The situation of the practicum includes OPD in OB-GYN, Postpartum ward, and nursery.', '853', '6621Z161', '662A10', '助日碩10', '853'),
(742, '704', '1131', '蔡秀純', '1C1601178011A0', '1C160', '1178', '1', 1, 0, '生殖生理與病理學', 'Reproductive Physiology and Pathology', '蔡秀純,蕭勝文', 4, 0, 4, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G305', '6', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本所國內碩士班。', '本課程旨在探討人類生殖生理學的原理與機轉，及婦女孕育過程中的醫療處置及其機轉和最新趨勢，課程內容包括生殖系統解剖構造與功能、生殖內分泌調節、月經週期、受精與著床、胎盤發育與功能、胎兒發育與生長、懷孕期的免疫與生理調適、基因與遺傳疾病以及分娩與泌乳，及妊娠與內外科合併症、不正常分娩、羊水栓塞、分娩與麻醉。藉由課室教學與討論使學生熟悉生殖生理的原理與機轉，並且能應用於臨床實務以及研究當中。', 'The aims of this course are to present the principles and mechanisms of reproductive physiology and pathology. The contents include the structures and functions of reproductive system, regulation of reproductive endocrine, menstrual cycles, fertilization and implantation, the development and function of the placenta, the development and growth of embryo, immunological aspects and physiological adaptation of pregnancy, genetic disorders, parturition and lactation, preconceptional counseling and prenatal care, prenatal diagnosis and antepartum assessment, intrapartum assessment &amp; management of abnormal labor, newborn assessment and resuscitation, assisting initiation of breastfeeding, the puerperium and possible complication, pregnancy hypertension, gestational diabetes mellitus, fetal growth disorder, multifetal gestation, obstetric hemorrhage (antepartum and postpartum), postterm pregnancy and induction of labor, and medical and surgical disease complicating pregnancy.\r\n  Through selected topics and discussion, students will understand advanced reproductive physiology and pathology, then will be able to apply the knowledge in clinical practice and the research.', '712', '6621Q701', '662211', '助產研一', '7,120,360'),
(743, '705', '1131', '王甄', '1C1600687011A0', '1C160', '687', '1', 1, 0, '高等生物統計學', 'Advanced Biostatistics', '王甄', 4, 0, 4, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F604,B522', '5', '4,5', '1.上課時間：11:10-13:00。\n2.修課限制：本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班（是否列入畢業學分請參照入學年課程科目表）。', '本課程以教授研究所學生具有進階應用生物統計學的分析能力。強調生物統計學之應用與醫學及護理臨床研究結合，以奠定學生具有資料收集、資料分析及統計報表解讀之能力，同時有能力評值學術期刊所發表的文章。課程內容包括：基本機率論、機率分佈理論、統計估計及檢定(獨立樣本及成對樣本t-test)、變異數分析(ANOVA)、相關係數、簡單迴歸分析到複迴歸分析等議題。本課程將會使用SPSS等專業統計軟體之操作。', 'The objective of this course is to provide graduate students with the advanced knowledge and understanding of the methods of statistical analysis applicable to medical and nursing research.  Also, this course is directed to equip graduate students with advanced capability of applying statistical analysis.  The course is \'math-lite but operation-heavy\' emphasizing concepts and application of statistical thinking and application. Probability theory, parametric statistics, correlation, regression, ANOVA, correlation analysis and regression analysis along with computer package practice (SPSS) will be introduced.', '136', '6621Q671', '662211', '助產研一', '136'),
(744, '706', '1131', '李嘉雯', '1C1600825011A0', '1C160', '825', '1', 1, 0, '健康評估及實作', 'Health Assessment and Practice', '李嘉雯,盧玉嬴', 3, 0, 3, 3.00, '全18週', 4.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G305', '5', '6,7,8,9', '修課限制：本所國內碩士班。', '本課程旨在增強學生臨床實務相關評估之學理與技巧。課程內容著重於應用焦點病史訪談、心理與生理評估技巧、詮釋評估結果於各年齡層之個案。學生應用臨床邏輯思維和鑑別診斷之模式，針對個案之健康問題主訴，應用相關學理與技巧，進行焦點評估、分析與正確的鑑別診斷個案之健康問題，以達成課程的目標。', 'The purpose of the course is to advance students\' physical assessment theory and skills that related to professional clinical nursing practice. The content of the course is emphasized on application skills of client interview, physiological and psychological assessment, interpreting results in women throughout the life span. Applying theories and techniques, assessing, analyzing and diagnosing health problems of a selected client will accomplish the course objectives.', '277', '6621Q691', '662211', '助產研一', '2,770,881'),
(745, '707', '1131', '高美玲', '1C1600822011A0', '1C160', '822', '1', 1, 0, '進階護理助產學 I', 'Nurse Midwifery I', '高美玲,高千惠,周雪棻', 6, 0, 6, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B522', '5', '1,2,3', '修課限制：本所國內碩士班。', '此課程旨在協助學生發展專業助產能力，強調角色轉換及護理助產是一個基層保健，課程內容包括以家庭為中心的取向，促進和維持低危妊娠婦女和其家庭成員的健康，及實施生產階段婦女、新生兒和家庭的健康管理。', 'This course is designed to prepare nurses for specialization in midwifery practice. Role change and nurse midwifery as a primary health care are the course. The content includes: (1) family-centered approach to care; (2) promotion and maintenance of health for women and the family during low risk child bearing and the child rearing period; (3) conducting health management for the women in labor and the family; and (4) promotion of health for childbearing stage women.', '853', '6621Q681', '662211', '助產研一', '85,308,168,408'),
(746, '708', '1131', '陳姿伶', '1C1600616011A0', '1C160', '616', '1', 1, 0, '護理理論', 'Nursing Theories', '陳姿伶,黃秀玫', 14, 0, 14, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G305', '5', '10,11,12', '1.與護研所合開（護研所碩士班婦女組及兒童組）\n2.上課時間：17:40~19:30\n3.修課限制：本所國內碩士班、外所碩士國內班（是否列入畢業學分請參照入學年課程科目表）。', '本課程旨在培養學生應用護理理論於實務、研究、教育和行政中之能力。主要學習經驗包括探討護理理論發展史、理論家背景、理論的重要概念及其闡述的現象、理論的應用。在引導下，學生深入研討至少一個護理理論，透過相關文獻的分析、歸納和演譯，練習將整合後的心得和經驗提出報告與同學分享、討論以達成本課程的目標。', 'The course aims to enhance students\' application ability of nursing theory in practice, research and education. The main contents include explore the history of nursing theory development , theorist background, key concepts and theories explained the phenomenon. I n the course guide the students in-depth discussions at least a nursing theory. Through analysis of relevant literature, induction and interpretation, reflection and sharing personal nursing beliefs and concepts achieve objectives of the course.', '9975', '6621Q661', '662211', '助產研一', '99,750,124'),
(747, '709', '1131', '', '1C160016101220', '1C160', '161', '1', 2, 20, '專題研究', 'Independent study', '高千惠,周雪棻,高美玲', 5, 1, 4, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '7', '1', '1.書面選課、實際上課時間及地點請洽授課教師。 \n2.修課限制：本所國內碩士班二年級以上學生。', '專題研究', 'The purpose of this course is to assist the student’s independent research ability in completing of master thesis. With the advisor’s help, the students should experience the research process on an academic basis. The contents include research motivation and purpose, literature review, research design, data collection and analysis.', '0', '6622Z271', '662B20', '助日碩20', '81,684,080,853'),
(748, '710', '1131', '高千惠', '1C160089801221', '1C160', '898', '1', 2, 21, '生產教育', 'Childbirth Education', '高千惠', 4, 0, 4, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'B522', '5', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所國內碩士班二年級以上學生，需先修或同時修畢「進階護理助產學 I」方得修習。', '本課程旨在協助學生成為專精之生產教育指導者，課程重點包括（1）具備懷孕、生產、產後婦女及其家庭變化及需求的正確理念及生產教育者的角色功能，（2）統整及應用課程設計、團體動力、諮商、賦權、創意/批判性思考等理論於生產教育實務，（3）討論/批判相關研究文獻並應用研究成果。教學方法將以互助及經驗分享式之學習為主，學生將以教學方案展現專精之生產教育能力', 'This course is designed to prepare students for training as a childbirth educator. The content includes (1) professional role of the childbirth educator; (2) promoting a safe and healthy pregnancy and birth; (3) assisting women and their families to make informed decisions for childbearing; (4) providing information and support that encourages attachment between babies and their families; (5) assisting women and their families to discover and to use strategies to facilitate normal, natural, and healthy pregnancy, birth, breastfeeding, and early parenting. (6) design, teach, and evaluate a course in childbirth preparation that increases a woman’s confidence and ability to give birth.', '816', '6622Z281', '662B21', '助日碩21', '816'),
(749, '711', '1131', '高千惠', '1C1601535012A0', '1C160', '1535', '1', 2, 0, '進階護理助產學實習 I', 'Advanced Nurse Midwifery Practicum I', '高千惠,高美玲,周雪棻', 5, 0, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 9.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '6', '5', '1.實習課程。\n2.實際上課時間及地點請洽授課教師。 \n3.修課限制：本所國內碩士班二年級以上學生，先修課程：進階護理助產學 I 。維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '此課程要旨在於增進學生照顧孕產期婦女及其家人的臨床專業能力，包括生育及其他健康問題，學生在此課程中將選擇與孕產期婦女健康相關主題，有組織的統整、應用並驗證相關的理論及研究於臨床實務，同時學生必須針對所選擇的孕產期婦女議題及護理應用，發展基本護理概念架構。契約學習是臨床教學的主要策略。', 'This course is designed to assist students acquiring clinical expertise in midwifery care of women during the childbirth process. In this course, students are required to select a problem or an issue discussed in the seminar and completes the nursing process through integration and application of the theories for selected women during childbirth process in appropriate clinical settings. Students are expected to develop a preliminary conceptual model to explain a clinical phenomenon involving women and its implications in nursing. Problem solving and critical thinking skills of students will be enhanced by employing the learning contract teaching strategy in the course.', '816', '6622Q431', '662221', '助產研二', '81,608,538,408'),
(750, '712', '1131', '陳姿伶', '1C1601536012A0', '1C160', '1536', '1', 2, 0, '進階護理助產學實習 II', 'Advanced Nurse Midwifery Practicum II', '陳姿伶,高美玲,周雪棻', 2, 0, 2, 3.00, '全18週', 9.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '6', '6', '1.實習課程。\n2.實際上課時間及地點請洽授課教師。\n3.修課限制：本所國內碩士班二年級以上學生，先修課程：進階護理助產學實習 I、進階護理助產學 II。維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '此課程要旨在於增進學生照顧孕產期婦女及其家人的臨床專業能力，包括生育及其他健康問題，學生在此課程中將選擇與孕產期婦女健康相關主題，有組織的統整、應用並驗證相關的理論及研究於臨床實務，同時學生必須針對所選擇的孕產期婦女議題及護理應用，發展基本護理概念架構。契約學習是臨床教學的主要策略。', 'This course is designed to assist students continuing to build on their clinical expertise in selected childbirth women care area. Students apply the selected theories to clinical situations on an operational basis is emphasized. By selecting an area of interest, students are required to demonstrate the role functions of an advanced midwifery in appropriate clinical settings. Students develop advanced midwifery roles, specifically, in client care and support, staff development, management and research. Students continuing to increase their professional competence in women health evidence-based practice', '9975', '6622Q441', '662221', '助產研二', '997,508,538,408'),
(751, '713', '1131', '', '1C1600300012A0', '1C160', '300', '1', 2, 0, '碩士論文', 'Master thesis', '高美玲,李嘉雯', 1, 0, 1, 6.00, '全18週', 6.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '2', '1.書面選課、實際上課時間及地點請洽授課教師。 \n2.修課限制：本所二年級以上學生。', '碩士論文', 'The purpose of this course is to assist the student’s independent research ability in completing of master thesis. With the advisor’s help, the students should experience the research process on an academic basis. The contents include research motivation and purpose, literature review, research design, data collection and analysis, and thesis writing.', '0', '6622Q421', '662221', '助產研二', '8,530,277'),
(752, '714', '1131', '周雪棻', '1C8600822011A0', '1C860', '822', '1', 1, 0, '護理助產學 I', 'Nurse-Midwifery I', '周雪棻,高美玲,高千惠', 6, 1, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G305', '1', '2,3,4', '修課限制：全英語授課', 'This course is designed to prepare nurses for specialization in midwifery practice. Role change and nurse midwifery as a primary health care are the course. The content includes: (1) family-centered approach to care; (2) promotion and maintenance of health for women and the family during low risk child bearing and the child rearing period; (3) conducting health management for the women in labor and the family; and (4) promotion of health for childbearing stage women.', 'This course is designed to prepare nurses for specialization in midwifery practice. Role change and nurse midwifery as a primary health care are the course. The content includes: (1) family-centered approach to care; (2) promotion and maintenance of health for women and the family during low risk child bearing and the child rearing period; (3) conducting health management for the women in labor and the family; and (4) promotion of health for childbearing stage women.', '8408', '6621Q711', '662212', '國際助一', '840,808,530,816'),
(753, '715', '1131', '', '1C8600300012A0', '1C860', '300', '1', 2, 0, '碩士論文', 'Master thesis', '高美玲', 1, 0, 1, 6.00, '全18週', 6.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '6', '1', '修課限制：書面選課、全英語授課', 'The purpose of this course is to assist the student’s independent research ability in completing of master thesis. With the advisor’s help, the students should experience the research process on an academic basis. The contents include research motivation and purpose, literature review, research design, data collection and analysis, and thesis writing.', 'The purpose of this course is to assist the student’s independent research ability in completing of master thesis. With the advisor’s help, the students should experience the research process on an academic basis. The contents include research motivation and purpose, literature review, research design, data collection and analysis, and thesis writing.', '0', '6622Q451', '662222', '國際助二', '853');
INSERT INTO `課程` (`編號`, `課程編號`, `學期`, `主開課教師姓名`, `科目代碼_新碼`, `系所代碼`, `核心四碼`, `科目組別`, `年級`, `上課班組`, `科目中文名稱`, `科目英文名稱`, `授課教師姓名`, `上課人數`, `男學生上課人數`, `女學生上課人數`, `學分數`, `上課週次`, `上課時數_週`, `課別代碼`, `課別名稱`, `上課地點`, `上課星期`, `上課節次`, `課表備註`, `課程中文摘要`, `課程英文摘要`, `主開課教師代碼_舊碼`, `科目代碼_舊碼`, `課表代碼_舊碼`, `課表名稱_舊碼`, `授課教師代碼_舊碼`) VALUES
(754, '716', '1131', '周雪棻', '1C8600826012A0', '1C860', '826', '1', 2, 0, '護理助產實務', 'Nurse Midwifery Field Experience', '周雪棻,高千惠,高美玲', 3, 0, 3, 3.00, '全18週', 6.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G305', '4', '2,3,4,6,7,8', '修課限制：全英語授課', 'The aim of this course is to integrate and apply scientific and theoretical knowledge of midwifery in target population. The student will be explored in various settings such as hospitals and community. Emphasis is on experiencing provision of midwifery care.', 'The aim of this course is to integrate and apply scientific and theoretical knowledge of midwifery in target population. The student will be explored in various settings such as hospitals and community. Emphasis is on experiencing provision of midwifery care.', '8408', '6622Q411', '662222', '國際助二', '840,808,160,853'),
(755, '717', '1131', '范立筠', '1C3301505011A0', '1C330', '1505', '1', 1, 0, '生理與病理學', 'Physiology and Pathology', '范立筠,林弘斌', 2, 0, 2, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G307', '3', '11,12,13', '修課限制：本系二技進修部、本所(本國生)、混合式遠距教學、遠距教學課程。', '本課程以學生在專科學校學得之基礎醫學知識為基礎，協助其更進一步瞭解人體生理學與病理學原理及機轉，包括：神經與肌肉生理學、神經系統、心臟血管系統、呼吸系統、腎臟與泌尿系統、消化系統、內分泌系統以及生殖系統。除了生理學與病理學的介紹之外，亦針對女性健康相關的議題進一步探討，例如：環境荷爾蒙對女性的影響、菸品對女性健康之危害、卵巢功能評估的方法、更年期、懷孕期生理的適應、不當荷爾蒙使用導致女性相關疾病的風險、女性重要慢性疾病、懷孕與疾病相關性等。', 'The purpose of this course is to introduce the principles and the mechanisms of physiology and pathology. The contents include cell physiology, nervous system, cardiovascular system, respiratory system, kidneys and urinary system, gastrointestinal system, endocrine system and reproductive system. Besides emphasizing the introduction of physiology and pathology, also discuss women’s health-related issues, e.g. impact of environmental hormones on women, harm of cigarette on women’s health, evaluation of ovarian function, menopause, physiological adaptation to pregnancy, risk of inappropriate hormones use, and women’s chronic diseases.', '827', '3621Q151', '362211', '助二一甲', '8,270,798'),
(756, '718', '1131', '李嘉雯', '1C3300303011A0', '1C330', '303', '1', 1, 0, '身體評估', 'Physical Examination', '李嘉雯,陳姿伶,陳莉莉', 2, 0, 2, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G307', '2', '11,12,13', '修課限制：本系二技進修部、本所(本國生)。', '本課程旨在提供已具有解剖、生理、病理及心理學知識的學習者，學習身體評估之知識與技巧。課程目標在增進學生身體評估技術的正確性與完整性，進而培育學生關懷、溝通與合作的專業素養; 各項評估能力則利用角色扮演並藉由示教及分組練習，使學生能有系統的進行個案整體性的身體評估。課程內涵強調以人為本及整體觀，使學生能於設計的模擬情境中展現臨床決策、溝通能力、關懷與專業倫理，並應用於護理情境中。', 'This course is offered to the learners who have had basic courses in human anatomy, physiology, pathology, and medical-surgical nursing. Health assessment is designed to promote the learners the habit of observation, the skills of data gathering, and the aptitudes required for clinical judgment. It provides a strong foundation for interviewing techniques, health history taking, assessment and diagnosis, physical examination skills, integrating the nursing process, and diagnostic study interpretation.', '277', '3621Q131', '362211', '助二一甲', '27,799,750,169'),
(757, '719', '1131', '林文絹', '1C3300519011A0', '1C330', '519', '1', 1, 0, '教學原理與健康照護實務', 'Principles of Teaching and Learning', '林文絹', 2, 0, 2, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G307', '2', '8,9', '修課限制：本系二技進修部、本所(本國生)。', '本課程旨在培養學生基本的教學能力，使學生能運用教學的原理進行個人、家庭及社區等照顧對象健康指導之教學過程。同時讓學生體認教學在健康照護實務中的功能，並培養學生對教學的興趣與應有的態度。學生修習本課程中必需實際完成教學計畫的擬定、執行、與評值過程。 課程內容包括教學在護理助產專業中之角色功能、教與學原則、教學設計、學習評估、擬定教學計畫、各種教學方法、教學媒體與資源、教學評值及臨床護理教學等。', 'The objective of this course is to develop basic teaching skills in students so that they become competent in teaching be a midwife. Lessons in this course include: the role and function of teaching in health care; principles of teaching and learning; teaching design; assessment of learning needs; teaching plan; teaching strategies; educational media; evaluation of teaching, etc. Students will learn how to apply teaching principles to midwifery instruction in individual, family and community health care situations. Students will also appreciate their function and proper attitude in the practice of health care. In this course, students are required to complete the design of a teaching plan, as well as execute and assess the process, thereby developing critical thinking, caring, communication, teamwork and self-directed learning abilities', '845', '3621Q141', '362211', '助二一甲', '845'),
(758, '720', '1131', '蘇琬婷', '1C3300224011A0', '1C330', '224', '1', 1, 0, '進階英文', 'Advanced English', '蘇琬婷', 2, 0, 2, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '1', '11,12', '1.開放助產系在職班一年級選課。 2.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。3.修課限制：同步遠距教學、遠距教學課程', '本課程為一學期每週兩小時的閱讀。教學重點為文法重點復習、閱讀技巧及練習普通英文閱讀。於該課程中學生能熟練高初級至初中級（high beginning ~low-intermediate level）基本文法重點，學習並運用各種英文閱讀技巧，閱讀並理解高初級至初中級（high beginning~low-intermediate level）普通英文文章。', 'This course includes a two-hour reading instruction each week.  Students are placed at different levels according to their individual English performance displayed in a placement test administered beforehand.  The main contents of the course are grammar review, reading skills and practice, basic level general English.', '382', '3621F091', '362211', '助二一甲', '382'),
(759, '721', '1131', '李美惠', '1C3300002011A0', '1C330', '2', '1', 1, 0, '進階國文', 'Advanced Chinese Literature', '李美惠', 2, 0, 2, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '1', '13,14', '1.遠距教學課程、混合式遠距教學\n3.修課限制：本系二技進修部、外系二技進修部二年級以上。\n2.主題:文學與社會', '本課程藉由古典文學（散文、詩詞歌賦、傳奇、戲劇）、中國哲學、現代文學（新詩、散文、小說）及兒童文學之專題選讀，指導學生研讀文學典籍及賞析的方法，使學生能掌握先賢之生命智慧與藝術心靈，了解中國學術源流及古今文學的精義，從而體認傳統文化的歷史傳承之責任。', 'The main purpose of this course is to increase students’ capabilities of appreciating literary works and expressing verbally.  Through studies of representative works of classic and modern Chinese literature, students are given the opportunity to appreciate the abundant and luxuriant styles of Chinese literature.  The instructor will guide students, by teaching methods as lecturing, discussion, and self-learning, to explore the profundity and the vitality of Chinese literature and furthermore, to understand the truth, virtue, and beauty of Chinese culture.', '115', '3621F101', '362211', '助二一甲', '115'),
(760, '722', '1131', '周雪棻', '1C3301512012A0', '1C330', '1512', '1', 2, 0, '助產學及實作(二)', 'Midwifery and practice Ⅱ', '高千惠,周雪棻,陳姿伶', 4, 0, 4, 3.00, '全18週', 4.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B522', '2', '6,7,8,9', '修課限制：本系二技進修部二年級、三年級、本所(本國生)、維持十八週課程。', '此課程為培育學生發展助產專業能力的第二階段課程，整體助產學課程架構旨在強 調助產師的角色功能，課程內容包括以家庭為中心的取向，促進和維持低危險妊娠婦女 和其家庭成員的健康，及實施生產階段婦女、新生兒和家庭的健康管理。助產學及實作 II 的課程著重在助產師於待產、生產及產後過程的角色及其功能、親善生產的核心概念、 維持正常分娩的照護措施，觀察及評估產後婦女在生理及心理方面的變化及調適，並能 提供產後婦女及其家庭文化適切的健康照護。', 'These series midwifery courses are designed to prepare students for specialization in midwifery practice. The core concepts include: (1) women and family-centered approach to care; (2) promotion and maintenance of health for women and the family during low risk child bearing and the child rearing periods; (3) conducting health management for the women in labor and the family; and (4) promotion of health for childbearing stage women. Midwifery and practice II emphasizes on the role and function of midwives during intrapartum and postpartum periods, core concepts of mother-friendly childbirth, intrapartum biopsychological assessment and care practices, facilitating normal childbirth practices. Assessing of postpartum family needs and provide individualized, culturally-appropriated as well as family-centered care.', '8408', '3622Q231', '362221', '助二二甲', '81,684,089,975'),
(761, '723', '1131', '李嘉雯', '1C3301514012A0', '1C330', '1514', '1', 2, 0, '助產學實習(一)', 'Midwifery Practice (I)', '李嘉雯,楊志貞', 5, 0, 5, 4.00, '第1週', 10.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '6', '1', '修課限制：本系二技進修部二年級、三年級、實習課程、提前開課，113.06.24~113.09.01(W1~W2)，維持十八週課程。', '此課程旨在協助學生發展助產專業照護的能力，統整並能運用相關學理，增進照護低危險的孕產婦及其家人的助產照護實務能力，實習內容於婦產科門診實施產前檢查、身體評估、健康指導、子宮頸抹片檢查、產後檢查等；並於嬰兒室實施新生兒評估及照護等技能；產後病房則為熟悉常規，執行產後評估及提供以家庭為中心之照護活動。', 'The purposes of this clinical course are designed to provide the students with a variety of clinical experiences at OBGY OPD, BR units, and postpartum ward in order to enhance their midwifery knowledge base. It also provides the opportunities for students to provide midwifery care to the childbearing family during the antepartum and postpartum periods.', '277', '3622Q241', '362221', '助二二甲', '2,771,824'),
(762, '724', '1131', '陳姿伶', '1C3301506012A0', '1C330', '1506', '1', 2, 0, '性別平權與健康照護', 'Gender Equality and Health Care', '陳姿伶,陳莉莉', 4, 0, 4, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G105', '3', '13,14', '修課限制：本系二技進修部二年級、三年級、本所(本國生)、混合式遠距教、遠距教學課程。', '本課程以性別主流化的概念為基礎，透過個體啟蒙、意識覺醒與行為實踐的過程，將引導學生了解性別論述於不同醫學專科領域，且能辨識性別概念與家庭、工作職場、社會福利和醫療政策的關係。以期使學生能發展具有性別分析的視野與能力，並能採取具備性別觀點的行動方案，應用於健康照顧的情境中。', 'This course is based on the concept of gender mainstreaming. We hope that through the process of enlightenment, awareness and practice that could help student to understand the gender perspective in different area of medical specialties, and to identify the relation for gender concept among', '9975', '3622Q211', '362221', '助二二甲', '99,750,169'),
(763, '725', '1131', '盧玉嬴', '1C3300058012A0', '1C330', '58', '1', 2, 0, '研究概論', 'Introducing to Research', '盧玉嬴', 4, 0, 4, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G105', '2', '11,12', '修課限制：本系二技進修部二年級、三年級、本所(本國生)。', '本課程旨在提供學生基本的研究知識與技能。學生除了對實務情境產生質疑，並藉由討論、批判、觀摩等活動，提升團隊合作、問題解決和批判性思考等能力。課程內容包括研究與專業發展間的關係、研究基本概念、研究步驟、研究計畫的撰寫和研究文獻的批判。', 'This course is to introduce the research process regarding basic concepts and practical applications. Empowering students assist and participate in nursing research. Besides, using criticize articles to enforce the research abilities among students.', '881', '3622Q191', '362221', '助二二甲', '881'),
(764, '726', '1131', '陳姿伶', '1C3301510012A0', '1C330', '1510', '1', 2, 0, '婦女健康照護(二)', 'Women Health Care (Ⅱ)', '陳姿伶,陳莉莉', 4, 0, 4, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G105', '3', '11,12', '修課限制：本系二技進修部二年級、三年級、本所(本國生)、混合式遠距教、遠距教學課程。', '本課程乃以婦女為中心的健康出發，藉由探討婦女面臨之健康問題，並用問題導向的教學引導方式(Problem Based Learning; PBL)從身、心、靈、社會及文化各層面深入探討婦女的健康，期望培育學生能以正向、積極的態度正視婦女健康，並將其應用於生活及臨床工作中，達到促進及維護婦女健康之目的。', 'This course examines the diverse social, cultural, psychological, developmental and biological factors that affect women\'s health status and health promotion during their different life stages. The course specifically considers how these diverse factors interact with gender regarding women\'s health. Developmental and other transitions that affect women\'s health trajectories are also considered. Using Problem Based Learning (PBL) skills leads students who can actively and positively learn women’s health care.', '9975', '3622Q221', '362221', '助二二甲', '99,750,169'),
(765, '727', '1131', '林文絹', '1C3300305012A0', '1C330', '305', '1', 2, 0, '專業與倫理', 'Profession and ethics', '林文絹', 4, 0, 4, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G105', '2', '3,4', '修課限制：本系二技進修部二年級、三年級、本所(本國生)。', '本課程旨在使學生獲得專業與倫理之基本知識、概念及各種照護倫理困境之分析與決策能力，進而激發學生發展批判性的倫理思考與判斷之潛能。課程內容以專業倫理之基本概念及倫理理論與原則之照護實務應用為主，透過講解與討論、對話與小組討論報告等教學方法，檢視價值觀與衝突、倫理與道德觀、倫理理論、基本倫理原則、倫理困境與倫理決策等議題。', 'The purposes of this course are to help students to gain the basic knowledge, concepts and standardized behavior of nursing ethics, to distinguish clinical ethical issues, as well as the ability to analyze and make decisions of ethical dilemma in order to urge them to develop critical thinking and proper judgment. The concepts of this course focus on the ethical basic concepts and the application of ethical principles: including the analysis and discussion of ethics and moral concepts; the formation and conflicts of values, the rights and responsibilities of patients and nurses; the cooperational relationships of medical team; application the main theories and principles of ethics; nursing code, ethical dilemma, and the ethical decision framework.', '845', '3622Q201', '362221', '助二二甲', '845'),
(766, '728', '1131', '周雪棻', '1C3301515013A0', '1C330', '1515', '1', 3, 0, '助產學實習(二)', 'Midwifery Practice (Ⅱ)', '周雪棻,周竹宜,楊志貞', 10, 0, 10, 4.00, '第1週', 10.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '6', '1', '修課限制：本系二技進修部三年級、實習課程、提前開課113.06.26~113.09.10(W3~W4)，維持十八週課程。', '此課程旨在協助學生發展助產專業照護的能力，統整並能運用相關學理，增進照護低危險的孕產婦及其家人的助產照護實務能力，實習內容於產房實施待產婦護理、胎兒分娩、產後病房執行產婦身體評估及護理及執行產後期照護。', 'The purposes of this clinical course are designed to provide the students with a variety of clinical experiences at delivery room in order to enhance their midwifery knowledge base. It also provides the opportunities for students to provide midwifery care to the childbearing family during the labor and delivery, and postpartum periods.', '8408', '3623Q041', '362231', '助二三甲', '840,810,291,824'),
(767, '729', '1131', '李嘉雯', '1C3301516013A0', '1C330', '1516', '1', 3, 0, '助產學實習(三)', 'Midwifery Practice (Ⅲ)', '李嘉雯,周竹宜', 10, 0, 10, 4.00, '第2~18週', 16.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '6', '2', '修課限制：本系二技進修部三年級、實習課程113.09.16~114.01.14，維持十八週課程。', '此課程旨在協助學生發展助產專業照護的能力，統整並能運用相關學理、實務經驗及研究於低危險的孕婦及其家人的助產照護業務，本課程也強調溝通及協調的能力，實習的內容包括對低危險孕產婦的由產前、生產、產後的持續性照護及高危險妊娠孕產婦的持續性照護。', 'The purposes of this clinical course are designed to provide the students with a variety of clinical experiences for perinatal women and their family, and high risk pregnant women’s care in order to enhance their midwifery knowledge base. It also provides the opportunities for students to provide midwifery care to the childbearing family during the antenatal, labor and delivery, and postpartum periods.', '277', '3623Q051', '362231', '助二三甲', '2,771,029'),
(768, '730', '1131', '邱慧洳', '1C3300026013A0', '1C330', '26', '1', 3, 0, '應用法規導論', 'Introduction of Professional Law', '邱慧洳', 10, 0, 10, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '3', '11,12', '限助二三甲學生修習。非同步遠距教學、遠距教學課程。		', '本課程醫護法學之介紹，使學生對法律結構、法學理念及我國現行法有一整體性的認知，以奠定法學啟發基礎。從醫護正義概念出發，就醫護法規、醫護法制、護理法律責任與訴訟、醫護人員切身法律問題等，深入淺出有系統的介紹，以培養現代醫護人員正確的法律觀。並從醫護業務與法律實務的角度，點出護理人員與其他醫事人員的責任分際、臨床醫護人員與公共衛生醫護人員面臨法律問題的不同、醫病糾紛的預防與處理等，以強化醫護人員處理法律問題的能力。', 'This subject is taught by way of the introduction of the basic law to let the students to understand the whole outline of the construction of law，the virtue of the jurisprudence and the  present law in Taiwan.  It begins as the teaching of the concept of the professional justice and is succeeded by introducing the medical and nursing law，the institution of the professional law，the responsibility and litigation as well as the professional liability of the member of professional society to ensure the students to know the exact concept of the law and to develop problem-solving abilities .', '1022', '3623F041', '362231', '助二三甲', '1022'),
(769, '731', '1131', '劉吉豐', '11169100000000 ', '11169', '737', '1', 1, 10, '健康照護之另類輔助療法', 'Alternative Medicine', '劉吉豐', 5, 1, 4, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'B111', '5', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、老人組、婦女組、精神組、社區組、兒童組、護資組、專師組、中西醫組）、外所國內碩士班（是否列入畢業學分，請參照入學年課程科目表）、跨校', '本課程旨在提供取於自然的理念乃是自然療法的獨到精髓；跨越預防醫學、臨床醫學、復健醫學的應用科學；討論關於輔助另類醫學及健康照護的方法與相關議題。', 'The Purpose of this course is to utilize the alternative medicine to the health care system including its background, concept and methodology. At the end of the course, the students can express their concern regarding health, illness, intervention and hea', '710', '6111Z231', '611A10', '護日碩10', '710'),
(770, '732', '1131', '劉茹涵', '11169100000000 ', '11169', '1026', '1', 1, 11, '經絡俞穴學', 'Meridians and Acupoints', '劉茹涵', 12, 1, 11, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G105', '5', '12,13,14', '修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、老人組、婦女組、精神組、社區組、兒童組、護資組、專師組、中西醫組）、外所國內碩士班（是否列入畢業學分，請參照入學年課程科目表）、跨校', '本課程旨在協助學生瞭解經絡俞穴之實證研究與實證實務，期使學生\r\n能在實證之理論與研究上有所認識，而應用於臨床有關健康照護，以增進\r\n學生健康照護之護理實證實務能力。課程內容包含介紹經絡俞穴實證研究\r\n現況，並教導臨床實務常用之經絡穴位護理介入方法，使學生能增強中西\r\n醫結合精準護理專業之實證能力。', 'This course aims to enable students to understand the empirical research and \r\npractical verification of meridians and acupoints. It is hoped that students can \r\nhave an understanding of the empirical theory and research, and apply it to \r\nclinical health care, so as to enhance the students\' health care ability in \r\npractical nursing. The course content includes introducing the current status of \r\nempirical research on meridians and acupoints and teaching the commonly used \r\nnursing interventions in clinical practice so that students can enhance the \r\nempirical ability of the precision nursing of integrated traditional Chinese and \r\nwestern medicine.', '401', '6111Z241', '611A11', '護日碩11', '401'),
(771, '733', '1131', '劉吉豐', '11169100000000 ', '11169', '1028', '1', 1, 12, '中醫診斷學', 'Diagnosis of Chinese Medicine', '劉吉豐', 17, 0, 17, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'B111', '5', '1,2', '修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、老人組、婦女組、精神組、社區組、兒童組、護資組、專師組、中西醫組）、外所國內碩士班（是否列入畢業學分，請參照入學年課程科目表）、跨校', '本課程旨在讓學生熟悉中醫診斷的基本概念與臨床常用診斷方法。主要學習經驗包括望、聞、問、切四診之傳統及現代化的研究方法，八剛辨證、六經辨證、衛氣營血辨證之診斷標準的熟悉。使學生能習得中醫的診斷、增進觀察能力，並且結合現代護理診斷的觀察與記錄，瞭解病患疾病的特質，以為選擇中西醫最佳治療方法。', 'This course attempts to familiarize students with the fundamental concepts and clinical diagnostic methods of Traditional Chinese Medicine. Inspection, Ausculation, Interrogation, Pulse Taking, and Palpation will assist us to collect comprehend many numerous signs and symptoms of the patients. In addition, eight principal syndromes for diagnosis, five zang-organs, six fu-organs, and theory of the Six Channels, Wei-Qi-Ying and Xue Systems included. These will promote the diagnostic abilities of the students. We combine Chinese-Western nursing diagnostic methods to obtain more information from the patient. This will be an essential basis from which to choose the best practices from both Modern and Traditional Chinese treatments.', '710', '6111Z251', '611A12', '護日碩12', '710'),
(772, '734', '1131', '王美華', '111690687011A0', '11169', '687', '1', 1, 0, '高等生物統計學', 'Advanced Biostatistics', '王美華,葉美玲', 21, 1, 20, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F602', '5', '3,4', '修課限制：本所碩士班（婦女組、護資組、中西醫組）、程式設計課程', '本課程以教授研究所學生具有進階應用生物統計學的分析能力。強調生物統計學之應用與醫學及護理臨床研究結合，以奠定學生具有資料收集、資料分析及統計報表解讀之能力，同時有能力評值學術期刊所發表的文章。課程內容包括：基本機率論、機率分佈理論、統計估計及檢定(獨立樣本及成對樣本t-test)、變異數分析(ANOVA)、相關係數、簡單迴歸分析到複迴歸分析等議題。本課程將會使用SPSS等專業統計軟體之操作。', 'The objective of this course is to provide graduate students with the advanced knowledge and understanding of the methods of statistical analysis applicable to medical and nursing research.  Also, this course is directed to equip graduate students with advanced capability of applying statistical analysis.  The course is \'math-lite but operation-heavy\' emphasizing concepts and application of statistical thinking and application. Probability theory, parametric statistics, correlation, regression, ANOVA, correlation analysis and regression analysis along with computer package practice (SPSS) will be introduced.', '589', '6111Q311', '610211', '護理研一', '5,890,854'),
(773, '735', '1131', '潘婉琳', '111690825011A0', '11169', '825', '1', 1, 0, '健康評估及實作', 'Health Assessment for Advanced Practice Nursing', '潘婉琳,鍾美玲,石雅文', 21, 0, 21, 3.00, '全18週', 4.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B414', '5', '6,7,8,9', '修課限制：本所碩士班（婦女組、兒童組、中西醫組）', '本課程旨在增強學生臨床實務相關評估之理與技巧。課程內容著重於應用焦點病史訪談、心理與生評估技巧詮釋結果於成年之個案。學應用臨床邏輯思維和鑑別診斷之模式，針對個案健康問題主訴應用相關學理與技巧進行焦點評估、分析與正確的鑑別診斷個案之健康問題，以達成課程目標。', 'The purpose of the course is to advance students\' physical assessment theory and skills that related to advanced nursing practice. The content of the course is emphasized on application skills of client interview, physiological and psychological assessment, interpreting results in individuals. This course focuses on development of clinical decision making skills in the process of health assessment. Applying theories and techniques, assessing, analyzing and diagnosing health problems on selected clients. As one outcome of this course, students demonstrate comprehensive and integrative health assessment practice and written skills.', '498', '6111Q321', '610211', '護理研一', '49,808,401,060'),
(774, '736', '1131', '王美華', '111690616011A0', '11169', '616', '1', 1, 0, '護理理論', 'Nursing theories', '王美華,賴倩瑜', 12, 1, 11, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G205', '5', '10,11', '修課限制：本所碩士班（精神組、中西醫組）', '本課程旨在增進學生應用護理理論於實務、研究和教育中之能力。主要學習內容包括探討護理理論發展史、理論家背景、理論的重要概念及其闡述的現象。在引導下，學生深入研討至少一個護理理論，透過相關文獻的分析、歸納和演譯，反思並分享個人護理信念和概念以達成本課程的目標。', 'The course aims to enhance students\' application ability of nursing theory in practice, research and education. The main contents include explore the history of nursing theory development , theorist background, key concepts and theories explained the phenomenon. I n the course guide the students in-depth discussions at least a nursing theory. Through analysis of relevant literature, induction and interpretation, reflection and sharing personal nursing beliefs and concepts achieve objectives of the course.', '589', '6111Q301', '610211', '護理研一', '5,891,439'),
(775, '737', '1131', '葉美玲', '11169200000000 ', '11169', '1520', '1', 2, 20, '實證健康照護與應用', 'Evidence-based Health-care and Application', '葉美玲,梁淑媛,王美華,鍾美玲', 15, 0, 15, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F601', '5', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、老人組、婦女組、精神組、社區組、兒童組、護資組、專師組、中西醫組）', '本課程主要協助學生瞭解護理之實證研究與實證實務，期使學生能在實證之理論與研究上有所認識，而應用於臨床有關健康照護，以增進學生健康照護之護理實證實務能力。課程內容包含實證相關之理論與研究以及實務層面，例如臨床決策之評量、質量性研究之評量、實證研究問題之發展、發展搜尋策略、研究品質之評量、發展實證護理研究計畫等。', 'This course provides students to have the concepts of evidence-based nursing for research and\r\npractice in healthcare. The major focus of the course encompasses the understanding of the issues\r\nabout evidence-based research and practical application through the participation, presentation, and\r\ndiscussion in the class.', '854', '6112Z721', '611B20', '護日碩20', '854,089,505,890,840'),
(776, '738', '1131', '鍾美玲', '11169200000000 ', '11169', '1791', '1', 2, 21, '針灸與傷科護理學', 'Mei-Ling Yeh; Mei-Ling Chung; Ming-Yu Luo', '鍾美玲,葉美玲,羅明宇', 17, 0, 17, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'B414', '5', '1,2', '修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、老人組、婦女組、精神組、社區組、兒童組、護資組、專師組、中西醫組）', '本課程主要學習目標，在於讓學生瞭解中醫之針灸與傷科基礎理論與其實務應用。課程內容包括中醫針灸與傷科概論、經絡學、腧穴學、針灸治療原理與原則、針灸常見疾病之辨證施護、傷科基礎理論、傷科診斷與治療、傷科基本手法、頸肩與腰背痠痛護理腰等。課程目標將培育學生能奠定針灸與傷科護理之基礎理論與實務操作能力，並能應用於健康暨疾病照護。', 'The main learning objective of this course is to enable students to understand the basic theory and practice of acupuncture and traumatology of traditional Chinese medicine. The course content includes the introduction of acupuncture and traumatology, the principles of meridian, acupuncture points as well as moxibustion, the syndrome differentiation and nursing care to common acupuncture-related diseases, the principle of traumatology, the diagnosis and therapy of traumatology, and musculoskecullar adjustment manipulations for neck, shoulder, and back pain. This course aims to cultivate students\' capabilities of the foundational theoretical and practical skills of acupuncture and traumatology, which can be applied to health and disease care.', '840', '6112Z731', '611B21', '護日碩21', '84,008,541,083'),
(777, '739', '1131', '王美華', '111691016012A0', '11169', '1016', '1', 2, 0, '中西醫結合護理 II', 'Nursing Theories with combined Traditional Chinese Medicine with Western Nursing', '王美華,葉美玲,鍾美玲,劉茹涵', 13, 0, 13, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B128', '5', '3,4,5', '06/21、08/02、08/05、08/13暑期提前授課，暑期教室G203（06/21於G201、08/02於F501）。授課時間：10:10-13:00，修課限制：本所碩士班（中西醫組）研二以上', '本課程承續中西醫護理I，旨（1）增進學生中西醫整合護理專業能力；以及（2）培育學生能執行進階護理師的角色與功能。學生需統合所學並應用中西醫整合護理知識來提升護理臨床專業角色與功能。學生藉著課程中相關專案的完成，以達到本課程的目標。', 'This course combine several nursing theories and tendency with Traditional Chinese Medicine with\r\nWestern nursing and their applications to the current self health care. Students can know the nursing\r\nof scientific research and its relationships to theories in Traditional Chinese Medicine with Western\r\nnursing\r\nThrough seminar and lecture, students will learn the background of Traditional Chinese Medicine\r\nwith Western nursing and learn skills in modern health care issues, particularly those with relevance\r\nto theories in Traditional Chinese Medicine with Western nursing.', '589', '6112Q981', '610221', '護理研二', '589,085,408,400,401'),
(778, '740', '1131', '鍾美玲', '111691017012A0', '11169', '1017', '1', 2, 0, '中西醫結合護理實習 II', 'Chinese-Western Medical Nursing Practicum II', '鍾美玲,葉美玲,王美華,劉茹涵', 14, 0, 14, 3.00, '全18週', 9.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '5', '修課限制：實習課程、本所碩士班（中西醫組）研二以上', '本實習課程承續中西醫護理實習I，旨在增進學生照護顧客的中西醫整合護理專業能力(旨在增進學生的中西醫整合護理專業照護能力)；以及培育學生能執行進階護理師的角色與功能。在此實習中，學生需應用所學並展現進階護理師的角色與功能於中西醫整合護理臨床實務。', 'The internship program continuity in the Western Nursing Practice I, aimed at improving the care of students of Chinese and Western integration of customer care and professional competence; and nurture students can perform advanced nursing roles and functions of the division. In this internship, students need to apply what they have learned and demonstrate advanced nurse roles and functions of integrated Chinese and Western medicine in clinical nursing practice', '840', '6112Q991', '610221', '護理研二', '840,085,405,890,401'),
(779, '741', '1131', '', '111690161012A0', '11169', '161', '1', 2, 0, '專題研究', 'Independent Study', '劉茹涵,王美華,葉美玲,鍾美玲', 15, 0, 15, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '7', '1', '授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所碩士班（中西醫組）、書面選課', '本課程以個別指導之形式，依據碩士生之護理專長背景及未來專業發展方向，引導學生探索相關核心概念、理論，結合其臨床專業技能，應用批判性思考及實證護理的概念，訂定研究方向及主題，擬定研究設計、完成研究計畫之書寫。', 'This course is delivered in an individualized format, tailored to the nursing specialization and future professional development of the master\'s student. It guides students in exploring relevant core concepts and theories, integrating their clinical expertise, applying critical thinking and evidence-based nursing concepts, determining research directions and topics, and developing research designs, culminating in the completion of a research proposal.', '0', '6112Z711', '610221', '護理研二', '401,058,908,540,840'),
(780, '742', '1131', '', '111690300012A0', '11169', '300', '1', 2, 0, '碩士論文', 'Thesis', '劉茹涵,王美華,葉美玲,鍾美玲', 5, 0, 5, 6.00, '全18週', 6.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '2', '授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所碩士班（中西醫組）、書面選課', '本課程以個別指導之形式，旨在協助碩士生以臨床實務為基礎，應用護理理論及研究能力，執行研究計畫，進行資料分析，並完成研究成果報告及碩士論文之撰寫。', 'This course is structured as individualized instruction, aiming to assist the master\'s student in utilizing clinical practice as a foundation. It focuses on the application of nursing theory and research skills, the execution of research protocol, data analysis, and the completion of research outcome reports and the master\'s thesis.', '0', '6112Q971', '610221', '護理研二', '401,058,908,540,840'),
(781, '743', '1131', '陳惠美', '11120000000000 ', '11120', '39', '1', 1, 10, '生死學', 'Life and Death Study', '陳惠美,曾煥棠', 50, 2, 48, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G106', '1', '6,7', '修課限制：\n1.跨域課程、志願選開放10個外系名額，第二階段開放全校。\n2.本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所(本國生)、外所(本國生)、學士後。\n3.跨校。', '本課程旨在讓同學了解生死學的研究與運用現況，從醫學、心理、社會、宗教與倫理的觀點探討死亡歷程，對個人的影響; 認識與死亡相關的儀式及其對社會組織的影響。本課程期使同學建立正向的生死觀，達到生命教育的目的。', 'This course proposes students can understand current research and application on life and death, explorate the death trajectories from medical, psychological, social, religious and ethic perspections, know death how to affect personal behaviours, ritual about death and its reflection on social organization. The expectation of this course is try to help students have positive recognition on life and death.', '893', '2101Z0D1', '210A10', '護日二10', '8,930,603'),
(782, '744', '1131', '廖珮宏', '11120000000000 ', '11120', '349', '1', 1, 10, '復健護理學', 'Rehabilitation Nursing', '廖珮宏,李林鍵', 49, 3, 46, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G106', '1', '8,9', '修課限制：本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、本系二技進修部、外系二技一般生、外系四技一般生、外系二技進修部、學士後、本所(本國生)、外所(本國生)、跨校。', '本課程在增進學生對一般復健護理的認知，透過課程學習培養學生具備以多元化觀點評估照護對象的實務能力課程內容包括：復健護理基本概論、復健護理之發展與理論、失能者整體評估、關節活動運動、擺位與移位、膀胱訓練、排便訓練、吞嚥障礙評估與訓練、皮膚損傷性復建、特殊照護服務對象之復健護理(如中風、脊髓損傷、截肢及性功能損傷病患等復健照護等)、輔具概論與應用等，教學活動包括：講習、討論、問答、影片欣賞、分組報告等。', 'This course is designed to improve the knowledge and skills of the students on the rehabilitation nursing, with multiple-cultural clinical competency, which was based on the diverse perspectives. The content of the course includes: the basic concept, the history and development, the theory and practice models of rehabilitation nursing, comprehensive assessment of disability patients, range of motion, positioning and transportation, training of bladder elimination and continence, bowel elimination and regulation, evaluation of dysphagia and swallowing training, skin integrity. In addition, the course includes the rehabilitation nursing for the client with CVA, SCI, Amputee, Neurogenic Sexual Dysfunction. The topic of stress and coping, the assistive technology and application will also be included. Teaching activities include lecture, discussing, questioning, watching movie, skill practice, and report.', '877', '2101Z0C1', '210A10', '護日二10', '8,771,200'),
(783, '745', '1131', '李坤黛', '11120000000000 ', '11120', '311', '1', 1, 11, '危機處理', 'Crisis Intervention', '李坤黛', 50, 4, 46, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G202', '1', '6,7', '修課限制：本系二技一般生一年級，護理學院。', '本課程旨在提供學生獲得危機處置之理論、知識與技能。內容分為危機處置基本概念、個人危機處置、危機案例分析三部份。學生經由分組討論、情境演練、角色扮演、家庭作業、案例分析，增加自我了解與危機處置的能力。', 'The aim of this course is to provide theory、knowledge and techniques of crisis intervention for students with nursing experience. The content will emphasize on developmental、social and situational crisis and related intervention techniques. Students’ crisis intervention ability can be strengthened through lecture、small group discussion and videotape discussion.', '879', '2101Z961', '210A11', '護日二11', '879'),
(784, '746', '1131', '徐淑貞', '11120000000000 ', '11120', '346', '1', 1, 11, '老人照護', 'Gerontological Nursing', '徐淑貞', 50, 6, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G408', '1', '8,9', '修課限制：本系二技一般生一年級、護理學院。', '本課程在增進學生對一般老人照護的認知，培養學生具備以多元化觀點評估照護一般老人的實務能力，課程內容包括：老人護理概論，與老人的溝通、文化及倫理議題，老人身體、心理、社會及靈性的評估與護理，老人常見健康問題與護理，老人居家照護與社區照護之網絡與資源等，教學活動包括：講習、討論、問答、影片欣賞、分組報告等。', 'This course is designed to improve the knowledge and skills of the students on the elderly health care, to multiple-culture the clinical competency of the students, which was based on the diverse perspectives. The course contents include the theory of aging; the assessment and nursing care of physiological, psychosocial, and spirit aspects of elders; the response of loss, dying; the conceptual framework of Gerontological nursing; community network and resources for nursing care of elders; and the presence and future of Gerontological nursing. Teaching activities include lecture, discussing, questioning, watching movie, visiting, and report.', '851', '2101Z0A1', '210A11', '護日二11', '851'),
(785, '747', '1131', '吳敍百', '11120000000000 ', '11120', '224', '1', 1, 11, '進階英文', 'Advanced English', '吳敍百', 44, 1, 43, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F609', '4', '6,7', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。 2.第二階段加退選開放本院二技一般生重修生選課。 3.第三階段加退選開放外系二技一般生重修生選課。', '本課程為一學期每週兩小時的閱讀。教學重點為文法重點復習、閱讀技巧及練習普通英文閱讀。於該課程中學生能熟練高初級至初中級（high beginning ~low-intermediate level）基本文法重點，學習並運用各種英文閱讀技巧，閱讀並理解高初級至初中級（high beginning~low-intermediate level）普通英文文章。', 'This course includes a two-hour reading instruction each week.  Students are placed at different levels according to their individual English performance displayed in a placement test administered beforehand.  The main contents of the course are grammar review, reading skills and practice, basic level general English.', '533', '2101F481', '210AAA', '護英一11', '533'),
(786, '748', '1131', '梁淑媛', '11120000000000 ', '11120', '325', '1', 1, 12, '疼痛處理', 'Pain Management Nursing', '梁淑媛', 50, 4, 46, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G302', '1', '6,7', '修課限制：本系二技一般生一年級', '課程內容由基礎疼痛之神經生理病理學介紹，且涵蓋疼痛經驗之心理社會觀，並藉由詳實之疼痛評估，以正確瞭解病人之整體性疼痛。課程中並將介紹常見疼痛症狀如：術後疼痛、肌肉骨骼疼痛、神經性疼痛、癌症疼痛等及多科際整合之疼痛處理方法如：藥物、神經外科手術、心理行為技巧、復健及物理治療等。', 'This is a course to instruct the definition, type, clinic presentations, evaluation and management of pain. In different type of pain, the strategies of assessment and management will be introduced via speech in classroom, and discussion of groups.', '895', '2101Z971', '210A12', '護日二12', '895'),
