(835, '797', '1131', '田政文', '111201739011D0', '11120', '1739', '1', 1, 0, '體育-跑步訓練', 'PE-Running', '田政文', 35, 12, 23, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '5', '1,2', '1.第一階段志願選，僅由全校二技一年級生互相跨班選課。 \n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。 \n3.上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。\n4.跨校。', '利用循序漸進的教學方式，教導學生跑步的基本動作，透過對跑步基本動作的熟練，進而提昇學生對跑步的興趣、享受跑步運動的樂趣。講授木球運動的規則及比賽策略。強調運動員必須在規則範圍內做合法的競賽，透過跑步運動來幫助學生守法、守分與合作的精神，並協助運動習慣的養成，期望學生能以跑步運動作為終身運動。', 'The content of course is to instruct students’ Running skill by using step-by-step teaching method. Over the basic movement of the skilled is to enhance the students\' interest in Running and enjoyment the fun of Running l. The rules and strategies of teaching Running to emphasize that athletes must be legitimate competition in the scope of the rules through the sport of Running to help students to obey the law, be law-abiding and cooperation spirit, Therefor, students are expected to develop the habit of exercise and to choice Running as a lifetime of activity.', '473', '2101F461', '210214', '護二一D ', '473'),
(836, '798', '1131', '陳明毅', '111200054011 ', '11120', '54', '1', 1, 0, '生物化學', 'Biochemistry', '陳明毅', 50, 2, 48, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S205', '2', '8,9', '課限制：本系二技一般生，重修/轉系生不限(本系四技一般生二年級以上)、學士後、外系二技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所(本國生)、外所(本國生)、跨校。', '本課程旨在從化學的觀點，詳細而深入地探究生物特有之分子組成與代謝，進而研究其生命現象。並以深入淺出之教學方法，將生化配合其他相關課程之需求，作一系統之教授，使符合本校之教育宗旨。', 'The course is to investigate the metabolism of proteins, lipids and sugars. And \r\ninvestigate the role of DNA, RNA in the process of biological reaction.\r\n   The student who finish this course will know the basic biochemical concept and more understanding about the living science.', '709', '2101Q0A1', '210215', '護二一E ', '709'),
(837, '799', '1131', '陳明毅', '111200301011 ', '11120', '301', '1', 1, 0, '生物化學實驗', 'Biochemistry Experiment', '陳明毅', 48, 1, 47, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S207', '2', '6,7', '課限制：本系二技一般生，重修/轉系生不限(本系四技一般生二年級以上)、學士後、外系二技一般生、外系二技進修部、本所(本國生)、外所(本國生)、跨校。', '本課程旨在從化學的觀點，詳細而深入地探究生物特有之分子組成與代謝，進而研究其生命現象。並以深入淺出之教學方法，將生化配合其他相關課程之需求，作一系統之教授，使符合本校之教育宗旨。', 'This course is to introduce the reactions of proteins, sugars and lipids in living \r\nthing; describing the meanings of data of energy exchange; techniques of \r\nmainpulation of instruments and application in nursing; using model puzzle of \r\nDNA, RNA to present the concept of gene.\r\nThe student who finish this course will know the basic biochemical concept and \r\nmore understanding about the natural science.', '709', '2101Q951', '210215', '護二一E ', '709'),
(838, '800', '1131', '廖婉彣', '111200042011 ', '11120', '42', '1', 1, 0, '生物統計學', 'Introduction of Biostatistics', '廖婉彣', 46, 1, 45, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B210', '5', '6,7', '修課限制：本系二技一般生', '授與提昇研究能力與增進閱讀學術文獻有關統計能力之知識與概念。其內容包括敘述統計學（集中趨勢量數、離中趨勢量數、分布、作圖與作表）以及推論統計學（區間估計與考驗之過程，Z score、pooled-t test、paired-t test、卡方、one-way ANOVA、皮爾遜積差相關、線性迴歸與無母數分析等）。課中利用EXCEL資料分析工具及各式小型科學電算器如Casio 36PV等協助運算，期能達成理論與實務之結合為目的。', 'The focus of this course is applied statistical techniques, with emphasis on data management, and data analysis through the Statistical Package for the Social Sciences. This course will complete weekly computer assignments that provide \"hands on\" experience with data analysis and interpretation of results. Students will actually understand statistical procedures and apply statistical techniques to concrete data.', '1081', '2101Q981', '210215', '護二一E ', '1081'),
(839, '801', '1131', '李靜恬', '111200052011 ', '11120', '52', '1', 1, 0, '生理學', 'Physiology', '李靜恬', 50, 2, 48, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G306', '4', '1,2', '修課限制：本系二技一般生', '本課程以基礎醫學的觀點，由淺入深詳細探討人體生理學原理，尤其加強各器官系統間之調節機轉，進而切入於生理失衡之分辨及科技新知之相關應用。內容包括生理機制概論、細胞生理學、神經系統功能、肌肉生理、內分泌之調控、心臟及血流動力循環生理學、呼吸、消化生理及代謝之調節、腎臟生理學、生殖與幹細胞之展望。', 'The purpose of this course is to introduce physiological principles and regulatory mechanisms in terms of cells, organs and systems, further helps students to integrate concepts of diverse normal human functions, and applied to related disease mechanism.', '945', '2101Q991', '210215', '護二一E ', '945'),
(840, '802', '1131', '陳惠美', '111200033011 ', '11120', '33', '1', 1, 0, '服務學習', 'Service Learning', '陳惠美', 47, 1, 46, 0.00, '全18週', 1.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G105', '4', '5', '修課限制：本系二技一般生', '本課程設計旨在協助學生培養服務的精神，藉由至服務機構提供服務，落實課堂所學之服務知識與理念，並進而從服務中學習、瞭解服務於社區之重要性與體驗服務之意義，培養正向的服務態度，以期自我省思、瞭解自我進而促進自我成長與肯定生命價值。', 'This course is provided to introduce the basic concepts of volunteer, and help the students with fundamental understanding in non-profit organization (NPO). The class will be guided by different instructions of lecture, group discussion, homework and test. By the end, the students will have basic understanding on concepts, principle, and management model in volunteer works and NPO. These will be helpful students for their future jobs and their quality of life.', '893', '2101Q971', '210215', '護二一E ', '893'),
(841, '803', '1131', '李慈音', '111200058011 ', '11120', '58', '1', 1, 0, '研究概論', 'Introduction to Nursing Research', '李慈音', 47, 1, 46, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G305', '3', '6,7', '修課限制：不開放跨班選課。', '本課程旨在提供學生基本的研究知識與技能。學生除了對實務情境產生質疑，並藉由討論、批判、觀摩等活動，提升團隊合作、問題解決和批判性思考等能力。課程內容包括研究與專業發展間的關係、研究基本概念、研究步驟、研究計畫的撰寫和研究文獻的批判。', 'This course is an introductory course on nursing research.  Students will have the opportunity \r\nfor a systematic investigation of a health-related topic of the student’s interest demonstrating \r\nknowledge and skills of research methodology. This course provides students step by step guidance \r\nof the research process as well as the critique of in-progress and completed research.', '815', '2101Q0C1', '210215', '護二一E ', '815'),
(842, '804', '1131', '黃馨', '111200519011 ', '11120', '519', '1', 1, 0, '教學原理與健康照護實務', 'Teaching Principles: The Application in Health Care Practice', '黃馨', 50, 1, 49, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G305', '3', '3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生', '本課程旨在培養學生基本的教學能力，使學生能運用教學的原理進行個人、家庭及社區等照顧對象健康指導之教學過程。同時讓學生體認教學在健康照護實務中的功能，並培養學生對教學的興趣與應有的態度。學生修習本課程中必需實際完成教學計畫的擬定、執行、與評值過程。課程內容包括教學在護理專業中之角色功能、教與學原則、教學設計、學習評估、擬定教學計畫、各種教學方法、教學媒體與資源、教學評值、及臨床護理教學等。', 'This course will assist students to develop basic competencies in health teaching for individuals,families,and communities. The interdisciplinary nature of health teaching, theories of teaching and learning, and their applications in client education, clinical teaching of students and staff development will be thoroughly discussed. Actual student teaching project will be developed, implemented, and evaluated.', '656', '2101Q961', '210215', '護二一E ', '656'),
(843, '805', '1131', '魏伯全', '111200002011 ', '11120', '2', '1', 1, 0, '進階國文', 'Advanced Chinese Literature', '魏伯全', 48, 1, 47, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'G109', '1', '3,4', '1.第二階段加退選僅由全校21生互相跨班選課。\n2.第三階段加退選開放系外及重修生選課。\n3.主題:戲曲選讀與欣賞', '本課程藉由古典文學（散文、詩詞歌賦、傳奇、戲劇）、中國哲學、現代文學（新詩、散文、小說）及兒童文學之專題選讀，指導學生研讀文學典籍及賞析的方法，使學生能掌握先賢之生命智慧與藝術心靈，了解中國學術源流及古今文學的精義，從而體認傳統文化的歷史傳承之責任。', 'The main purpose of this course is to increase students’ capabilities of appreciating literary works and expressing verbally.  Through studies of representative works of classic and modern Chinese literature, students are given the opportunity to appreciate the abundant and luxuriant styles of Chinese literature.  The instructor will guide students, by teaching methods as lecturing, discussion, and self-learning, to explore the profundity and the vitality of Chinese literature and furthermore, to understand the truth, virtue, and beauty of Chinese culture.', '566', '2101F471', '210215', '護二一E ', '566'),
