(895, '857', '1131', '梁惠玉', '111200306012D0', '11120', '306', '1', 2, 0, '醫療組織與管理', 'Medical Organization and Management', '梁惠玉', 52, 2, 50, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F415', '4', '8,9', '修課限制：本系二技一般生二年級', '本課程旨在透過講述、e 化、翻轉、自主和案例省思等教學與學習方法，協助學生獲得護理行政管理之知識、態度與技能。課程內容以護理管理過程為架構，主要包括：規劃、組織、人力資源管理、領導及控制等，以期啟發學生對自我管理及護理行政管理之認識與興趣，並能實際運用於臨床業務。', 'This course is designed for students to acquire the knowledge and skills of nursing administration, and it contents nursing management process, planning, organization, human resource management, leadership, control, and so on. Each student is encouraged to initiate her or his knowledge and interest in nursing administrative field and to utilize the course knowledge and skills in nursing career in the future.', '359', '2102Q2G1', '210224', '護二二D ', '359'),
(896, '858', '1131', '涂明香', '111200386012D0', '11120', '386', '1', 2, 0, '護理臨床專論', 'Introduction for Nursing Employment', '涂明香', 53, 2, 51, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F415', '4', '6,7', '修課限制：本系二技一般生二年級', '本課程旨在協助學生未來能順利的適應職涯的環境，透過討論、講授、參與職涯講座、資料搜尋、自學及分組報告等方式，認識台灣各層級醫院、優質護理職場之條件、職場相關議題和護理新鮮人可能面臨的問題，進而協助學生能有適當的選擇就業職場', 'The purpose of the course is to guide and prepare students for the practicum of obtaining nursing employment. Through lecturing and discussion, students will be familiar with the purposes and agendas of the practicum, and knowing how to prepare themselves in advance to facilitate their learning during the practicum. Through the preparation of the course, students are expected to be able to integrate and apply nursing theories, related knowledge, and skills in nursing practice. In together with the practicum for obtaining nursing employment, this course is aimed to develop students’ clinical competence in providing evidence-based, individualized, and prioritized nursing care.', '418', '2102Q2I1', '210224', '護二二D ', '418'),
(897, '859', '1131', '陳惠美', '111200305012 ', '11120', '305', '1', 2, 0, '專業與倫理', 'Profession and Ethics', '陳惠美', 50, 4, 46, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G106', '3', '3,4', '修課限制：本系二技一般生二年級', '本課程旨在使學生獲得專業與倫理之基本知識、概念及各種護理倫理困境之分析與決策能力，進而激發學生發展批判性的倫理思考與判斷之潛能。課程內容以專業倫理之基本概念及倫理理論與原則之護理實務應用為主，透過講解、分析與問題導向學習等教學方法，檢視價值觀與衝突、倫理與道德觀、病人權利與責任、護理師權利與責任、倫理理論、基本倫理原則、倫理困境與倫理決策等等議題。', 'The purposes of this course are to help students to gain the basic knowledge, concepts and standardized behavior of nursing ethics, to distinguish clinical ethical issues, as well as the ability to analyze and make decisions of ethical dilemma in order to urge them to develop critical thinking and proper judgment. The concepts of this course focus on the ethical basic concepts and the application of ethical principles: including the analysis and discussion of ethics and moral concepts; the formation and conflicts of values, the rights and responsibilities of patients and nurses; the cooperational relationships of medical team; application the main theories and principles of ethics; nursing code, ethical dilemma, and the ethical decision framework.', '893', '2102Q2F1', '210225', '護二二E ', '893'),
