(923, '875', '1131', '蘇美禎', '11140100000000 ', '11140', '1041', '1', 1, 10, '性別與健康照護', 'Gender and Healthcare', '蘇美禎', 50, 6, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G203', '5', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大一大二、技高銜接課程、混合式遠距教學、遠距教學課程、跨域課程。於第二階段加退選起開放選課。', '本課程以性別主流化的概念為基礎，透過個體啟蒙、意識覺醒與行為實踐的過程，將引導學生論述於不同醫學專科領域之性別議題，且能辨識家庭、工作職場、社會福利和醫療環境中的性別平等政策。以期使學生能發展具有性別平等的概念，並應用於健康照護的情境中。', 'This course is based on the concept of gender mainstreaming. We hope that through the process of enlightenment, awareness and practice that could help student to understand the gender perspective in different area of medical specialties, and to identify the relation for gender concept among family, workplace, social welfare, and health policy. The student would develop the vision and ability of gender analysis, and take action with gender perspective which applies in nursing care.', '8403', '4101Z031', '410A10', '護日四10', '8403'),
(924, '876', '1131', '曾貴祺', '11140100000000 ', '11140', '1055', '1', 1, 11, '英文一', 'Freshman English I', '曾貴祺', 52, 9, 43, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'G108', '1', '1,2', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放護理學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。', '本課程為一學期兩小時兩學分的閱讀課程。教學重點為文法重點複習、閱讀技巧及練習、普通英文文章閱讀。於該課程中學生能熟練高初級至初中級(high beginning ~ low-intermediate level)基本文法重點，學習並運用各種英文閱讀技巧，閱讀並理解高初級至初中級(high beginning ~ low-intermediate level)普通英文文章。', 'This is a one-semester course which is worth two credits and includes a two-hour reading instruction each week. The main contents of the course consist of: grammar review, reading skills and practice, and general English text reading. In this course, students are expected to become familiar with English grammar (from high beginning ~ low-intermediate level), learn different reading skills, and apply the skills to their comprehension of English texts (from high beginning ~ low-intermediate level).', '226', '4101F0N1', '410AAA', '護英一11', '226'),
