(971, '923', '1131', '潘愷', '111400053011D0', '11140', '53', '1', 1, 0, '化學', 'Chemistry', '潘愷', 64, 11, 53, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S205', '1', '8,9', '預排考試時間：週一第6、7節，修課限制：本系四技一般生、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程旨在從基本之化學概念，引導學生進入自然科學之領域。由最簡單之物質概述“原子”闡述，漸序進入更大分子領域，進而對有關人體之各巨觀化學現象的了解。並以深入淺出之教學方法，並配合日後生物化學等相關課程，將著重於加強有機化學，分析化學等內容作更深入的探討。', 'Students of the biological sciences require a good grounding in chemistry if they are to fully \r\nunderstand key aspects of their courses.  The course is divided into 17 sections containing 59 topics. Each topic consists of a key notes panel with concise statements of the key points covered. These are expanded on in the main part of the topic which includes simple and clear black and white figures which many readily be reproduced for essays or examinations for example.', '708', '4101Q851', '410414', '護四一Ｄ', '708'),
(972, '924', '1131', '莊青青', '111400379011D0', '11140', '379', '1', 1, 0, '化學實驗', 'Chemistry Experiment', '莊青青', 56, 10, 46, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S207', '1', '6,7', '預排考試時間：週一第6、7節，修課限制：本系四技一般生、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程旨在配合化學課程及教師提供之教材，以實際操作，加強學生對化學領域的認識與了解。藉由實驗的過程與結果，使化學理論實際化及合理化，以增進學生的學習效果。而實驗內容包括物質化性及物性之測定，定量、定性分析實驗，有機化學合成及鑑定。', 'The major purpose of this course is from the basic chemical concept in the regular living or matters to induced the nursing background students into the natural science range. From the simplest experiment , step by step , let students know how to think, design and do the experiment, combine the theory and real mater in the chemistry ..\r\n	The student who finish this course will know the basic chemical concept and more understanding about the natural science.', '713', '4101Q801', '410414', '護四一Ｄ', '713'),
(973, '925', '1131', '鍾昭瑛', '111400384011D0', '11140', '384', '1', 1, 0, '心理學', 'Psychology', '鍾昭瑛', 53, 9, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G302', '3', '8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生', '本課程主要內容是以心理學各種基礎理論、研究方法及重要實驗為主，進而擴展應用於心理衛生各種人類生活適應行為及生活層面。課程綱要包括心理學的起源與發展、基礎理論與研究方法、行為的生物學基礎、意識狀態、感覺與知覺、學習與行為、記憶、思維與智力、心理評量:人格與智力測驗、人類發展、動機與情緒、人格、壓力與衝突、異常行為、心理治療方式、社會知覺與認知、態度、社會影響與互動。', 'The main content of this curriculum is to expand and apply the fundamental theory, research method, and important experiment in psychology to mental health in various living line includes the origin and development of psychology, fundamental theory and research method, fundamentals of behavioral biology, consciousness, sensation and perception, leaning, cognition, memory, thinking and intelligence, psychological assessment, personality and intelligence test, human development, motivation and emotion, personality stress and conflict, abnormal behavior psychotherapeutics social perception, cognition, attitude, and social influence and interaction.', '576', '4101Q831', '410414', '護四一Ｄ', '576'),
(974, '926', '1131', '何澍', '111400000011D0', '11140', '0', '1', 1, 0, '國文一', 'Chinese Literature I', '何澍', 51, 9, 42, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F404', '3', '3,4', '大一新生限55名，其餘名額預留予重修生。\n1.第二階段加退選僅由護理學院四技生一年級生互相跨班選課及護理學院重修生選課。\n2.第三階段加退選開放系外及重修生選課。\n3.文學與成長', '本課程摘選古典文學及現代文學之代表作品，著重培養學生閱讀、欣賞、寫作、口語表達等語言文字能力，並提升學生閱讀興趣、拓展人文視野，增進學生人文精神與文化涵養，進而落實至生活中，以培養獨立思考、理性自主的健全人格。', 'In this course students will study representative works of classical and modern literature, with an imphasise on improving verbal skills such as reading, writing, speaking and appreciation for Chinese literature. In doing so, the course aims to inspire students\' interest in reading in order to expand on their knowledge, thus able to incooperate vitality and cultural conservation into everyday life, whilst promoting independent, logical thinking and a healthy character.', '105', '4101F0T1', '410414', '護四一Ｄ', '105'),
(975, '927', '1131', '周光儀', '111400051011D0', '11140', '51', '1', 1, 0, '解剖學', 'Human Anatomy', '周光儀,許育弘', 58, 11, 47, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B113', '2', '8,9', '預排考試時間：週一第8、9節。修課限制：本系四技一般生、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程是以學習人體解剖學課程內容為主要目標，包括: 細胞及組織的認識，骨骼、肌肉、循環、神經、呼吸、消化、泌尿、內分泌和生殖系統構造的瞭解，並靈活應用於護理專業基礎及專業核心課程之學習。', 'The purpose of this course is to introduce anatomical principles  and mechanism of body \r\nstructure, and further helps students to integrate related concepts and understand the relationship \r\nbetween structures and their functions. The contents include cellular anatomy, skeletal system, \r\nanatomy of nerve and muscle, central nervous system, cardiovascular system, respiratory system, \r\ndigestive system, urinary system, reproductive system, endocrine system and applied surface \r\nanatomy', '760', '4101Q841', '410414', '護四一Ｄ', '7,608,385'),
(976, '928', '1131', '周光儀', '111400381011D0', '11140', '381', '1', 1, 0, '解剖學實驗', 'Laboratory of Human Anatomy', '周光儀,許恒賓', 59, 9, 50, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S201', '4', '8,9', '預排考試時間：週四3、4節。修課限制：本系四技一般生、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本實驗課程主要的目標是學習人體的構造，內容包括: 細胞及組織之顯微認識，利用模具深入瞭解骨骼、肌肉、循環、神經、呼吸、消化、泌尿、內分泌和生殖系統的詳細構造，並靈活應用於護理專業基礎及專業核心課程之學習。', 'The purpose of this course is to integrate the concepts of anatomical principles and the \r\nstructure of human body. And further helps students to understand the relationship between \r\nstructures and functions. The contents of the  course include the usage of microscope and \r\nunderstanding microscopic anatomy, the structure of skeletal system, nerve and muscle, central \r\nnervous system, cardiovascular system, respiratory system, digestive system, urinary system, \r\nreproductive and endocrine system.', '760', '4101Q811', '410414', '護四一Ｄ', '7,600,857'),
(977, '929', '1131', '劉純和', '111400213011D0', '11140', '213', '1', 1, 0, '資訊素養與網路運用', 'Information Literacy and Network Application', '劉純和', 54, 12, 42, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F602', '3', '1,2', '1.第二階段加退選，開放修習「資訊素養與網路運用」課程之學生互相跨班選課。2.重修生請自第二階段開放選課。全部網路選課，無紙本加選。3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '本課程為電腦之基礎課程，主要培育學生資訊素養，以具備適當資訊應用能力。課程內容除強化電腦基本概念、作業系統與文書處理軟體應用能力外，並包含網路觀念、網路應用、網路安全、資訊倫理，與智慧財產權。', 'This course is a basic course to educate students to have enough knowledge about information literacy and network application. The course will include the basic concept of computers, operating systems, office application software, network applications, information security, and intellectual property concepts.', '9907', '4101F0V1', '410414', '護四一Ｄ', '9907'),
(978, '930', '1131', '蘇哲賢', '111400027011D0', '11140', '27', '1', 1, 0, '藝術文化史', 'History of Artistic Culture', '蘇哲賢', 53, 9, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F408', '4', '6,7', '1.第二階段開放修習「藝術文化史/世界文明史」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。\n2.全部網路選課，無紙本加選。\n3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '透過藝術文化的類型與不同的表現形式及中西方藝術的演進與賞析，瞭解藝術的理念、內涵與歷史演變，深入探討藝術與生命、美感與生活、藝術與文化等重要議題之意義。培養學生對藝術文化有基本的認識與高度的敏感度，提升審美素養，持續自主學習的興趣。', 'Through the exploration of various types and form of art and culture, as well as the evolution and appreciation of Eastern and Western art, this course provides an understanding of the concepts, meaning and historical transformations of arts. It further delves deeply into significant topics such as art and life, aesthetics and everyday life, and art and culture. Students will acquire a foundational comprehension and heightened sensitivity of art and culture, enhance their aesthetic literacy, and foster a sustained commitment to self-directed education.', '381', '4101F0U1', '410414', '護四一Ｄ', '381'),
(979, '931', '1131', '李坤黛', '111400302011D0', '11140', '302', '1', 1, 0, '關懷與溝通', 'Caring and Communication', '李坤黛,高千惠', 54, 10, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B114', '2', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生、跨域課程', '本課程旨在培養學生具備關懷與溝通的能力。課程內容包含了解關懷的內涵、引導學生從認識自己、關懷自我，延伸至關懷家人及關懷他人，並在人際互動中展現關懷與溝通的技巧與行為。', 'The aims of the course are to improve the self- awareness of the student, to nurture the competence of communication and caring. The course contents include the relationships among people to people, people to society, people to environment and spirit. The art of caring, caring and nursing, critical attributes of communication, communication model and related factors. The course emphasizes self-refection, student will be able to integrate the knowledge, attitude and skills of communication and caring, to aware self’s pattern of communication, analyze the influences in daily life and nursing performance, willing to change, and demonstrate communication skill and caring in daily life.', '879', '4101Q791', '410414', '護四一Ｄ', '8,790,816'),
(980, '932', '1131', '張寧', '111401746011D0', '11140', '1746', '1', 1, 0, '體育-基本運動素養', 'P E-Fundamental Movement Capacities', '張寧', 53, 9, 44, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '3', '6,7', '1.四技一年級新生，由教務處安排於入學系別之一年級原班授課。 \n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。 \n3.上課地點請洽體育室。 \n4.跨校。 ', '新生的體育教學課程設計著重在體適能的強化、健康運動概念介紹及休閒運動入門引導。主要內容包括健康體適能之心肺適能的強化，以及帶動身體協調性與強調團隊合作的籃球運動為主，期望學生不僅習得運動健康概念，也因球類運動而習得助人及團隊合作的態度。', 'The purpose of this course for freshman is emphasis on the both physical fitness and basic sport skill. Lecturers instruct the concept of sports and healthy to the student through cardiovascular fitness and sport skill (basketball) as well as to promote the coordination of the body and the emphasis on teamwork of basketball. Freshmen not only acquire the concept of sports health, but also learn to help people and teamwork attitude.', '8397', '4101F0S1', '410414', '護四一Ｄ', '8397'),
(981, '933', '1131', '蘇琬婷', '11140000000000 ', '11140', '224', '1', 2, 11, '進階英文', 'Advanced English', '蘇琬婷', 45, 7, 38, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'B216', '2', '6,7', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放護理學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。', '本課程為一學期兩小時兩學分的課程。教學重點為文法重點複習、閱讀技巧及練習、普通英文文章閱讀，於該課程中學生能熟練中級至中高級(intermediate ~high intermediate level)基本文法重點、學習並運用各種英文閱讀技巧、閱讀並理解中級至中高級(intermediate ~high intermediate level)英文文章。', 'This is a two-credit, one-semester course. Included in the instruction for students of all levels are grammar review, basic sentence structure, introduction and application of English reading skills to high-intermediate reading articles, outlining and summarizing, as well as general or professional conversational English, talks, lectures, reports, and programs.', '382', '4102F741', '410BAA', '護英二11', '382'),
(982, '934', '1131', '何思源', '11140100000000 ', '11140', '1061', '1', 2, 21, '職場英文', 'English for the Work Place', '何思源', 35, 3, 32, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F610', '2', '6,7', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放護理學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。4.全英語授課。', '本課程為一學期兩小時兩學分的課程。由英語中級程度提昇至中高級之訓練課程。教學重點為職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧及其應用。於該課程中學生能熟悉並練習職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧。', 'This is a two-hour weekly and one-semester course which is worth two credits. This is an intermediate to high-intermediate level English course. The main contents of the course consist of: common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, communication skills in workplace, and the application of communication skills. In this course, students are expected: (a) to become familiar with common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, and communication skills; and (b) to apply common English vocabulary in workplace and business English dialogue expressions to their everyday English conversations.', '273', '4102F751', '410BBA', '護英二21', '273'),
(983, '935', '1131', '何思源', '11140100000000 ', '11140', '1061', '1', 2, 22, '職場英文', 'English for the Work Place', '何思源', 40, 8, 32, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F610', '2', '8,9', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放護理學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。4.全英語授課。', '本課程為一學期兩小時兩學分的課程。由英語中級程度提昇至中高級之訓練課程。教學重點為職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧及其應用。於該課程中學生能熟悉並練習職場英語常用字彙、句法、對話技巧。', 'This is a two-hour weekly and one-semester course which is worth two credits. This is an intermediate to high-intermediate level English course. The main contents of the course consist of: common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, communication skills in workplace, and the application of communication skills. In this course, students are expected: (a) to become familiar with common English vocabulary in workplace, business English dialogue expressions, and communication skills; and (b) to apply common English vocabulary in workplace and business English dialogue expressions to their everyday English conversations.', '273', '4102F751', '410BBB', '護英二22', '273'),
