(985, '937', '1131', '林淑雯', '11140000000000 ', '11140', '212', '1', 2, 31, '新聞英語', 'Journalistic English', '林淑雯', 38, 6, 32, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'B216', '5', '3,4', '1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二、三階段加退選開放重修生選課。3.全英語授課。4.修課限制：混合式遠距教學、遠距教學課程', '本課程為每學期兩學分。教學內容包括熟練新聞句法、新聞用字及新聞英語中文章的閱讀技巧及其應用，是突破中級程度進階至中高級或高級之最佳訓練課程，學生能聽懂新聞廣播、閱讀新聞報導及收看新聞節目。', 'This course includes two hours of instruction each week and is worth two credits. This course focuses on the application of different listening and reading strategies for comprehending the latest news, including those related to nursing and health sciences published in Times as well as at BBC, CNN, and New York Times websites. Students are expected to learn the information related to the news and become familiar with the vocabulary and sentence structures contained in the news. Students are also expected to participate in the following activities: discussing issues related to the news, giving presentations, and criticizing each piece of news as well as other peers’ presentation performances in the classroom. In addition, students also need to study the materials at http://140.131.85.13/enginfo/myABC/index.htm for NTUNHS Joint Exams.', '770', '4102F731', '410BCA', '護英二31', '770'),
