(1003, '953', '1131', '翁慧玲', '111400382012B0', '11140', '382', '1', 2, 0, '營養學與實驗', 'Nutrition &amp; Nutrition Experiment', '翁慧玲', 49, 7, 42, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G201', '4', '8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、護理系學士後、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程是以營養學為基礎，搭配如理想體重、飲食指南、飲食指標、DRIs、食物代換表、營養標示等單元介紹，並以六大類營養素為主軸結合疾病療養學的應用，例如介紹熱量的概念後，以體重控制為例；介紹碳水化合物的生理功能後，搭配糖尿病的飲食保健；介紹脂肪的生理功能時，搭配心血管疾病的飲食保健；在蛋白質單元課程則與慢性腎衰竭營養治療飲食原則結合；維生素單元以抗氧化劑的介紹為搭配；礦物質的介紹則以骨質疏鬆症的營養保健搭配；另一方面介紹住院病人營養評估、營養支持與腸道營養配方等單元，讓學生可以把基礎營養學與相關的疾病營養照護的概念聯成一氣，培育保健照護產業中關懷助人及敬業樂群的護理專業實務人才。', 'The course of Clinical Nutrition is design for the 4- year program of Nursing \r\nDepartment consists two parts. The first part introduces the concept of nutrition. Such \r\nas body weight management, dietary guideline, dietary goal, DRIs, exchange list, \r\nnutrition label.The second part introduces the nutritional care and the diet therapy on \r\nvarious diseases, such as obesity, DM, atherosclerosis disease, chronic renal failure, \r\nosteoporosis, nutritional deficiency (such anemia) etc.', '190', '4102Q821', '410422', '護四二Ｂ', '190');
INSERT INTO `課程` (`編號`, `課程編號`, `學期`, `主開課教師姓名`, `科目代碼_新碼`, `系所代碼`, `核心四碼`, `科目組別`, `年級`, `上課班組`, `科目中文名稱`, `科目英文名稱`, `授課教師姓名`, `上課人數`, `男學生上課人數`, `女學生上課人數`, `學分數`, `上課週次`, `上課時數_週`, `課別代碼`, `課別名稱`, `上課地點`, `上課星期`, `上課節次`, `課表備註`, `課程中文摘要`, `課程英文摘要`, `主開課教師代碼_舊碼`, `科目代碼_舊碼`, `課表代碼_舊碼`, `課表名稱_舊碼`, `授課教師代碼_舊碼`) VALUES
(1004, '954', '1131', '林和駿', '111400021012B0', '11140', '21', '1', 2, 0, '環境教育', 'Environmental Education', '林和駿', 49, 7, 42, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'G202', '3', '6,7', '1.第二階段加退選，開放修習「環境教育」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。2. 全部網路選課，無紙本加選。3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '本課程旨在闡述環境永續發展的意義與重要性，教學內涵希望提昇學生永續發展的覺知，增加永續發展的概念知識，培養正確的永續發展態度與價值觀，並發展永續發展的行動技能與行動經驗。課程強調在環境中進行教育，學習有關環境的知識、態度、技能，並且為實踐永續環境而準備。環境教育包含六個核心的學習要素：自然資源保育概念、環境管理概念的融入；生態原理、互動與互賴概念的融入；以及融入環境倫理與永續性的概念等。\r\n    課程內容涵蓋環境概論、環境倫理、環境教育法規、環境變遷與防災、節能減碳與能源管理、與永續發展與生態保育等主題內容。教學策略運用：做中學、在真實的情境中體驗、合作學習法、運用感官學習、探索環境議題等項目。教學方法採取課堂講解、分組討論、專題討論、現地參訪等方式進行，並以多媒體教材教學。期望藉由環境議題的認識與討論，深入環境的內涵；透過對於環境問題的觀察與思考，了解環境永續的本質及善盡環境保護的義務。環境教育是一種教育的過程，在過程中個人認識他們的環境，以及組成環境的生物、物理和文化間的交互作用，得到知識、技能和價值觀，並能個別或集體地了解並解決現在和將來的環境問題。', 'Environmental education is designed to explain the meaning and importance of environment and sustainable development. It refers to organized efforts to teach how natural environments function, and particularly, how human beings can manage behavior and ecosystems to live sustainably. It is a multi-disciplinary field integrating disciplines such as biology, chemistry, physics, ecology, earth science, atmospheric science, mathematics, and geography. The term often implies education within the school system, from primary to post-secondary. However, it sometimes includes all efforts to educate the public and other audiences, including print materials, websites, media campaigns, etc. \r\n  Environmental education consists of six core elements: the concept of conservation of natural resources, environmental management into ecological principles, into the concept of interaction and interdependence; and the concept of integration of environmental ethics and sustainable environment. Environmental education is the teaching of individuals, and communities, in transitioning to a society that is knowledgeable of the environment and its associated problems, aware of the solutions to these problems, and motivated to solve them.Environmental education is an educational process, in the process of personal awareness in their environment, and form an environment of interaction between biological, physical and cultural, are knowledge, skills, and values, and individually or collectively, can understand and solve current and future environmental problems.', '617', '4102F721', '410422', '護四二Ｂ', '617'),
(1005, '955', '1131', '翁逸奎', '111400050012B0', '11140', '50', '1', 2, 0, '藥理學', 'Pharmacology', '翁逸奎', 52, 8, 44, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B114', '2', '1,2', '修課限制：本系二技一般生大二、本系四技一般生大二以上、本系二技進修部大二以上、外系四技一般生大二以上有修習過生理學者、護理系學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程之設計係以四技護理系學生為授課對象，課程內容著重於培養學生對臨床用藥的認知及應能力；故以深入淺出之方式探討物於人體理作機轉，並介紹與臨床應用有關之藥品動力、交互作副及物中毒解等課程單元內容包括：藥理學概論、自主神經系統作用劑心臟血管中樞劑、自泌素相關藥物影響內分及新陳代謝以化學治療等。', 'This pharmacology is a two credit hour course and designed especially for students of nursing. This curriculum emphasizes on the clinical applications and action mechanisms of various drugs. The curriculum training will start from more details and bring a completely concepts, including general concepts of clinical pharmacokinetics, drugs interaction and antidote of drugs. The course outlines include of autonomic nervous system, cardiovascular system, central nervous system, endocrine and metabolism system, autacoids and chemotherapy related drugs.', '785', '4102Q781', '410422', '護四二Ｂ', '785'),
(1006, '956', '1131', '翁逸奎', '111400377012B0', '11140', '377', '1', 2, 0, '藥理學實驗', 'Experimental of Pharmacology', '翁逸奎', 51, 9, 42, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S201', '2', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、護理系學士後、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程之設計係以四技護理系學生為授課對象，課程內容著重在實際操作以及示範操作實驗以印証藥理學所涵蓋之課程內容；包括：藥品動力、交互作用、 自主神經系統作用劑、影響內分泌及新陳代謝藥物、中樞神經作用劑、心臟血管疾病用藥以及化學療法藥物等。', 'This experimental of pharmacology is a one credit hours course and designed especially for students of nursing. The purpose of this course is to approve the concepts of drugs by demonstrative experiments and movie appreciation. The subjects include general concepts of drugs and pharmacokinetic, autonomic nervous system drugs, cardiovascular drugs, CNS related drugs (Analgesics and Anesthetics) and chemotherapeutics.', '785', '4102Q801', '410422', '護四二Ｂ', '785'),
(1007, '957', '1131', '黃正銘', '111401740012B0', '11140', '1740', '1', 2, 0, '體育-游泳', 'PE-Swimming', '黃正銘', 41, 12, 29, 0.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', '', '1', '8,9', '1. 第一階段志願選，僅由高四二A、運四二B、護四二B互相跨班選課。\n2. 第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技二年級(含)以上一般生選課。\n3. 上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。\n4.跨校。', '教育部針對高中職以下學校，鼓勵其應落實游泳教學及提昇學生之游泳能力。然而許多高中職學生進入大專院校後，並非全部達到基本游泳能力之要求。本課程旨在引導學生認識水的危險和水上安全等相關知識，進一步則教導學生學會並增進游泳之基本能力，包括基本潛水、韻律呼吸、自由式、蛙式、仰式、蝶式等。', 'The Ministry of Education proposed that all students under 12 should learn swimming and achieve certain criteria in individual swimming levels. However, many Taiwan students those have entered colleges appear to not develop their skills in swimming. The course is to awaken students to the safety and danger about waters. The instructor will help students to develop and improve their swimming skills, such as underwater swimming, rhyming and efficient breathes, freestyle, breaststroke, backstroke, and butterfly stroke.', '1244', '4102F801', '410422', '護四二Ｂ', '1244'),
(1008, '958', '1131', '簡翠薇', '111400303012C0', '11140', '303', '1', 2, 0, '身體評估與實作', 'Physical Examination and Practice', '簡翠薇', 43, 8, 35, 3.00, '全18週', 4.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B420', '3', '6,7,8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、護理系學士後、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程旨在提供已具有解剖、生理、病理及心理學知識的學習者，學習身體評估之知識與技巧。課程目標在增進學生身體評估技術的正確性與完整性，進而培育學生關懷、溝通與合作的專業素養; 教學策略將針對不足之學理，進行澄清和討論，各項評估能力則利用角色扮演並藉由示教及分組練習，使學生能有系統的進行個案整體性的身體評估。課程內涵強調以人為本及整體觀，使學生能於設計的模擬情境中展現臨床決策、溝通能力、關懷與專業倫理，並應用於護理情境中。', 'This course is designed to provide students who already have knowledge of anatomy and physiology to learn the knowledge and skills of physical examination. The goal of the course is to improve the correctness and completeness of students\' physical examination techniques, thereby develop students\' professional qualities of care, communication, and cooperation. The teaching strategy will be to clarify and discuss deficiencies in academic theory, and to practice physical examination through role-play, demonstration, and group practice. Thereafter, students can systematically conduct a comprehensive physical examination of different cases. The content of the course emphasizes a person-centered and holistic view, enabling students to demonstrate clinical decision-making, communication skills, caring and professional ethics in designed simulated situations, and allow students to apply them in actual nursing situations.', '810', '4102Q791', '410423', '護四二Ｃ', '810'),
(1009, '959', '1131', '柳舒祥', '111400049012C0', '11140', '49', '1', 2, 0, '病理學', 'Pathology', '柳舒祥,林弘斌,王業翰,余忠泰,許志怡,鄭威', 46, 8, 38, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F415', '2', '1,2', '本課程建議有解剖學、生理學、微生物免疫學基礎者可修。修課限制：本系二技一般生大二、本系四技一般生大二以上、本系二技進修部大二以上、外系二技一般生大二、外系四技一般生大二以上、外系二技進修部大二以上、護理系學士後、跨校', '病理學是探討疾病的原因、機轉、病理變化及過程、預後等的一門學問 課程分二大部分1.概論2.各論。 概論主要介紹外來的傷害與疾病的刺激對細胞與組織所造成的共通的變化、與反應與機轉。詳細內容包括細胞傷害與死亡、炎症與癒合、細胞生長發育的異常、體液代謝障礙、免疫與腫瘤、遺傳、代謝與營養疾病。 各論討論各器官系統其各類疾病的致病原因、機轉，病理變化及臨床表現等。詳細 的內容包括心臟血管系統疾病、呼吸系統疾病、肝臟及膽管系統疾病、消化系統及 胰臟疾病、內分泌系統疾病、血液與淋巴系統疾病、腎臟疾病、男性生殖系統疾病、', 'The scientific focus of pathology is on the etiology of disease, the mechanisms of pathogenesis, and the pathways by which morphologic changes occur.  Pathogenesis of diseases will be discussed on the molecular basis to facilitate the understanding of difficult concepts. The content of this coursed are design to fit the requirement for who will be working in the field of nursing.   \r\nThe curriculum is divided into 2 major parts: (1) General Pathology and (2) Systemic Pathology.      General Pathology introduces the effects of exogenous injurious agents on the cells and tissues, and the resultant cellular changes, reactions and diseases.  The contents include: introduction, cell injury and cell death, metabolic disturbances of the body fluids, immunologic disorders, inflammation and repair, neoplasia, genetic disorders, chemical and physical injuries and metabolic and nutritional diseases.    \r\nSystemic pathology discusses the etiology and pathogenesis of various disease entities from the aspects of each organ system.  This covers the diseases of the cardiovascular system,  the respiratory system, the digestive system, the musculoskeletal system and nervous system;   the disorders of the endocrines, the kidneys, the male reproductive organs, the breast and the female reproductive organs and the skin.', '106', '4102Q771', '410423', '護四二Ｃ', '10,607,980,577,075,900,000,000'),
(1010, '960', '1131', '柳舒祥', '111400378012C0', '11140', '378', '1', 2, 0, '病理學實驗', 'Pathology Experiment', '柳舒祥,林弘斌,王業翰,余忠泰,許志怡,鄭威', 49, 10, 39, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F415', '3', '1,2', '需要修習過病理學或至少與病理學同一學期修課者可修。修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、護理系學士後', '病理學實驗教學旨在使學生融合病理知識與疾病的臨床表徵. 課程內容包括: 實驗病理學、感染性疾病、,臨床病理學、心臟血管系統疾病、呼吸系統疾病、肝臟及膽管系統疾病、消化系統及肝胰臟疾病、 內分泌系統疾病、血液與淋巴系統疾病、腎臟疾病、男性生殖系統疾病、乳房及女性生殖系統疾病、骨骼肌肉系統、神經系統疾病、皮膚疾病的病例說明與病理討論。', 'The curriculum introduce the main works of anatomic pathology and clinical pathology first , then follows the courses which cover the diseases of cardiovascular system, respiratory system,  digestive system, lymphoid and hemopoietic system, the disorders of the kidneys, the male reproductive organs, the breast and the female reproductive organs, and the diseases of central nerve system. The main teaching activities are problem based learning, though the clinical cases reports, interactive discussions and conferences, the student recognize the pathological phenomenon of human diseases.', '106', '4102Q811', '410423', '護四二Ｃ', '10,607,980,577,075,900,000,000'),
(1011, '961', '1131', '簡翠薇', '111400394012C0', '11140', '394', '1', 2, 0, '基本護理學與實作', 'Basic Nursing and Practicum', '簡翠薇,劉桂芬,王美華,劉茹涵', 53, 10, 43, 4.00, '全18週', 6.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S401,S408', '4', '1,2,6,7,8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、護理系學士後、網路退選書面加選、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程培養學生具有護理專業之基本知識與技能。課室內容包括觀察與專業性人際關係、醫療環境、個案各種基本需要之護理等。學生透過討論、反思、技術練習、回示教、自主學習體驗活動等多元教學策略與學習方法，學習主動展現關懷、基本護理學相關知識及技能並發揮團隊合作完成課室指定之報告，以達成學生對基本護理學之知識、態度與技能的學習，並能運用於臨床實務中。', 'This course provided for developing students\' foundational knowledge and skills in nursing. The content includes professional interpersonal relationships, healthcare environments, and the fundamental needs of patients. Employing a rich array of teaching methodologies, including discussions, reflection, technical practice, guided instruction, and independent learning experiences, students are actively encouraged to demonstrate compassionate care, acquire pertinent knowledge and skills, and collaborate within teams. Ultimately, the objective is to equip students with the capability to apply their acquired knowledge, attitudes, and skills in real-world clinical practice.', '810', '4102Q831', '410423', '護四二Ｃ', '810,083,305,890,401'),
(1012, '962', '1131', '周秋燕', '111400382012C0', '11140', '382', '1', 2, 0, '營養學與實驗', 'Nutrition &amp; Nutrition Experiment', '周秋燕,林晏如', 49, 9, 40, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G201', '4', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、護理系學士後、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程是以營養學為基礎，搭配如理想體重、飲食指南、飲食指標、DRIs、食物代換表、營養標示等單元介紹，並以六大類營養素為主軸結合疾病療養學的應用，例如介紹熱量的概念後，以體重控制為例；介紹碳水化合物的生理功能後，搭配糖尿病的飲食保健；介紹脂肪的生理功能時，搭配心血管疾病的飲食保健；在蛋白質單元課程則與慢性腎衰竭營養治療飲食原則結合；維生素單元以抗氧化劑的介紹為搭配；礦物質的介紹則以骨質疏鬆症的營養保健搭配；另一方面介紹住院病人營養評估、營養支持與腸道營養配方等單元，讓學生可以把基礎營養學與相關的疾病營養照護的概念聯成一氣，培育保健照護產業中關懷助人及敬業樂群的護理專業實務人才。', 'The course of Clinical Nutrition is design for the 4- year program of Nursing \r\nDepartment consists two parts. The first part introduces the concept of nutrition. Such \r\nas body weight management, dietary guideline, dietary goal, DRIs, exchange list, \r\nnutrition label.The second part introduces the nutritional care and the diet therapy on \r\nvarious diseases, such as obesity, DM, atherosclerosis disease, chronic renal failure, \r\nosteoporosis, nutritional deficiency (such anemia) etc.', '539', '4102Q821', '410423', '護四二Ｃ', '5,391,129'),
(1013, '963', '1131', '陳建和', '111400021012C0', '11140', '21', '1', 2, 0, '環境教育', 'Environmental Education', '陳建和', 52, 10, 42, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '1', '通識必修(通識)', 'F414', '3', '3,4', '1.第二階段加退選，開放修習「環境教育」課程之學生及重修生互相跨班選課。2. 全部網路選課，無紙本加選。3.因轉學轉系或修習雙聯學位同學如欲提早修課，經中心同意後，請於第三階段開放其選課，名單會於第二階段選課結束後送交教務處。', '本課程旨在闡述環境永續發展的意義與重要性，教學內涵希望提昇學生永續發展的覺知，增加永續發展的概念知識，培養正確的永續發展態度與價值觀，並發展永續發展的行動技能與行動經驗。課程強調在環境中進行教育，學習有關環境的知識、態度、技能，並且為實踐永續環境而準備。環境教育包含六個核心的學習要素：自然資源保育概念、環境管理概念的融入；生態原理、互動與互賴概念的融入；以及融入環境倫理與永續性的概念等。\r\n    課程內容涵蓋環境概論、環境倫理、環境教育法規、環境變遷與防災、節能減碳與能源管理、與永續發展與生態保育等主題內容。教學策略運用：做中學、在真實的情境中體驗、合作學習法、運用感官學習、探索環境議題等項目。教學方法採取課堂講解、分組討論、專題討論、現地參訪等方式進行，並以多媒體教材教學。期望藉由環境議題的認識與討論，深入環境的內涵；透過對於環境問題的觀察與思考，了解環境永續的本質及善盡環境保護的義務。環境教育是一種教育的過程，在過程中個人認識他們的環境，以及組成環境的生物、物理和文化間的交互作用，得到知識、技能和價值觀，並能個別或集體地了解並解決現在和將來的環境問題。', 'Environmental education is designed to explain the meaning and importance of environment and sustainable development. It refers to organized efforts to teach how natural environments function, and particularly, how human beings can manage behavior and ecosystems to live sustainably. It is a multi-disciplinary field integrating disciplines such as biology, chemistry, physics, ecology, earth science, atmospheric science, mathematics, and geography. The term often implies education within the school system, from primary to post-secondary. However, it sometimes includes all efforts to educate the public and other audiences, including print materials, websites, media campaigns, etc. \r\n  Environmental education consists of six core elements: the concept of conservation of natural resources, environmental management into ecological principles, into the concept of interaction and interdependence; and the concept of integration of environmental ethics and sustainable environment. Environmental education is the teaching of individuals, and communities, in transitioning to a society that is knowledgeable of the environment and its associated problems, aware of the solutions to these problems, and motivated to solve them.Environmental education is an educational process, in the process of personal awareness in their environment, and form an environment of interaction between biological, physical and cultural, are knowledge, skills, and values, and individually or collectively, can understand and solve current and future environmental problems.', '1209', '4102F721', '410423', '護四二Ｃ', '1209'),
(1014, '964', '1131', '王雅惠', '111400050012C0', '11140', '50', '1', 2, 0, '藥理學', 'Pharmacology', '王雅惠,沈郁強', 60, 11, 49, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G403', '1', '8,9', '修課限制：本系二技一般生大二、本系四技一般生大二以上、本系二技進修部大二以上、外系四技一般生大二以上有修習過生理學者、護理系學士後、本所國內碩士班、外所國內碩士班、（研究生下修，不計入畢業學分）、跨校、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程之設計係以四技護理系學生為授課對象，課程內容著重於培養學生對臨床用藥的認知及應能力；故以深入淺出之方式探討物於人體理作機轉，並介紹與臨床應用有關之藥品動力、交互作副及物中毒解等課程單元內容包括：藥理學概論、自主神經系統作用劑心臟血管中樞劑、自泌素相關藥物影響內分及新陳代謝以化學治療等。', 'This pharmacology is a two credit hour course and designed especially for students of nursing. This curriculum emphasizes on the clinical applications and action mechanisms of various drugs. The curriculum training will start from more details and bring a completely concepts, including general concepts of clinical pharmacokinetics, drugs interaction and antidote of drugs. The course outlines include of autonomic nervous system, cardiovascular system, central nervous system, endocrine and metabolism system, autacoids and chemotherapy related drugs.', '9030', '4102Q781', '410423', '護四二Ｃ', '90,309,019'),
(1015, '965', '1131', '王雅惠', '111400377012C0', '11140', '377', '1', 2, 0, '藥理學實驗', 'Experimental of Pharmacology', '王雅惠,沈郁強', 49, 8, 41, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S201', '1', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、護理系學士後、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程之設計係以四技護理系學生為授課對象，課程內容著重在實際操作以及示範操作實驗以印証藥理學所涵蓋之課程內容；包括：藥品動力、交互作用、 自主神經系統作用劑、影響內分泌及新陳代謝藥物、中樞神經作用劑、心臟血管疾病用藥以及化學療法藥物等。', 'This experimental of pharmacology is a one credit hours course and designed especially for students of nursing. The purpose of this course is to approve the concepts of drugs by demonstrative experiments and movie appreciation. The subjects include general concepts of drugs and pharmacokinetic, autonomic nervous system drugs, cardiovascular drugs, CNS related drugs (Analgesics and Anesthetics) and chemotherapeutics.', '9030', '4102Q801', '410423', '護四二Ｃ', '90,309,019'),
