(1019, '969', '1131', '柳舒祥', '111400378012D0', '11140', '378', '1', 2, 0, '病理學實驗', 'Pathology Experiment', '柳舒祥,林弘斌,王業翰,余忠泰,許志怡,鄭威', 43, 7, 36, 1.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F415', '3', '3,4', '需要修習過病理學或至少與病理學同一學期修課者可修。修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、護理系學士後', '病理學實驗教學旨在使學生融合病理知識與疾病的臨床表徵. 課程內容包括: 實驗病理學、感染性疾病、,臨床病理學、心臟血管系統疾病、呼吸系統疾病、肝臟及膽管系統疾病、消化系統及肝胰臟疾病、 內分泌系統疾病、血液與淋巴系統疾病、腎臟疾病、男性生殖系統疾病、乳房及女性生殖系統疾病、骨骼肌肉系統、神經系統疾病、皮膚疾病的病例說明與病理討論。', 'The curriculum introduce the main works of anatomic pathology and clinical pathology first , then follows the courses which cover the diseases of cardiovascular system, respiratory system,  digestive system, lymphoid and hemopoietic system, the disorders of the kidneys, the male reproductive organs, the breast and the female reproductive organs, and the diseases of central nerve system. The main teaching activities are problem based learning, though the clinical cases reports, interactive discussions and conferences, the student recognize the pathological phenomenon of human diseases.', '106', '4102Q811', '410424', '護四二Ｄ', '10,607,980,577,075,900,000,000'),
(1020, '970', '1131', '柯莉珊', '111400394012D0', '11140', '394', '1', 2, 0, '基本護理學與實作', 'Basic Nursing and Practicum', '柯莉珊,黃慧芬,林英,黃馨,林婷茹', 54, 10, 44, 4.00, '全18週', 6.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S401,S408', '3', '6,7,8,9', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大二以上、護理系學士後、網路退選書面加選、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程培養學生具有護理專業之基本知識與技能。課室內容包括觀察與專業性人際關係、醫療環境、個案各種基本需要之護理等。學生透過討論、反思、技術練習、回示教、自主學習體驗活動等多元教學策略與學習方法，學習主動展現關懷、基本護理學相關知識及技能並發揮團隊合作完成課室指定之報告，以達成學生對基本護理學之知識、態度與技能的學習，並能運用於臨床實務中。', 'This course provided for developing students\' foundational knowledge and skills in nursing. The content includes professional interpersonal relationships, healthcare environments, and the fundamental needs of patients. Employing a rich array of teaching methodologies, including discussions, reflection, technical practice, guided instruction, and independent learning experiences, students are actively encouraged to demonstrate compassionate care, acquire pertinent knowledge and skills, and collaborate within teams. Ultimately, the objective is to equip students with the capability to apply their acquired knowledge, attitudes, and skills in real-world clinical practice.', '821', '4102Q831', '410424', '護四二Ｄ', '8,210,843,089,006,560,000'),
