(1086, '1016', '1131', '賴倩瑜', '111400418014A0', '11140', '418', '1', 4, 0, '精神科護理學與實作', 'Psychiatric Nursing and Practice', '賴倩瑜,林佑蓉', 41, 6, 35, 3.00, '第1週', 4.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '6', '1', '授課期間：06/24-08/08暑期授課，暑期教室G407，修課限制：本系四技一般生大三以上、護理系學士後大三、網路退選書面加選、維持十八週課程（未採16+2模式）', '本課程旨在培養四年制學生具備執行精神衛生護理的關懷、溝通與合作與批判思考等基本能力。課程內容包括我國精神衛生有關的政策、法律、業務與推展現況、基本理念、常用的精神衛生照護模式及處置，並期許學生增進精神衛生護理知識、態度與技能。', 'This course provides nursing students with the basic knowledge and skills about psychiatric patient nursing care. The major elements include the policies, laws, regulations, theories and skills of advanced psychiatric mental health nursing, and missions of psychiatric nursing organizations. Students are required to identify and establish their own philosophy of nursing as well as to recognize psychiatric mental health nurse’s roles and functions. Nursing assessment, interventions and evaluation used by psychiatric clinicians are presented and discussed in this class.', '1439', '4104Q931', '410441', '護四四Ａ', '14,390,958'),
(1087, '1017', '1131', '潘婉琳', '111400386014A0', '11140', '386', '1', 4, 0, '護理臨床專論', 'Introduction for Nursing Employment', '潘婉琳', 43, 7, 36, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G206', '2', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大三以上、護理系學士後大三', '本課程旨在協助學生未來能順利的適應職涯的環境，透過討論、講授、參與職涯講座、資料搜尋、自學及分組報告等方式，認識台灣各層級醫院、優質護理職場之條件、職場相關議題和護理新鮮人可能面臨的問題，進而協助學生能有適當的選擇就業職場。', 'The purpose of the course is to guide and prepare students for the practicum of obtaining nursing employment. Through lecturing and discussion, students will be familiar with the purposes and agendas of the practicum, and knowing how to prepare themselves in advance to facilitate their learning during the practicum. Through the preparation of the course, students are expected to be able to integrate and apply nursing theories, related knowledge, and skills in nursing practice. In together with the practicum for obtaining nursing employment course, this course is aimed to develop students’ clinical competence in providing evidence-based, individualized, and prioritized nursing care.', '498', '4104Q901', '410441', '護四四Ａ', '498'),
