(1098, '1022', '1131', '李怡賢', '111400305014B0', '11140', '305', '1', 4, 0, '專業與倫理', 'Profession and Ethics', '李怡賢', 49, 9, 40, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G402', '2', '1,2', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大四', '本課程旨在使學生獲得專業與倫理之基本知識、概念及各種護理倫理困境之分析與決策能力，進而激發學生發展批判性的倫理思考與判斷之潛能。課程內容以專業倫理之基本概念及倫理理論與原則之護理實務應用為主，透過講解、分析與問題導向學習等教學方法，檢視價值觀與衝突、倫理與道德觀、病人權利與責任、護理師權利與責任、倫理理論、基本倫理原則、倫理困境與倫理決策等等議題。', 'The purposes of this course are to help students to gain the basic knowledge, concepts and standardized behavior of nursing ethics, to distinguish clinical ethical issues, as well as the ability to analyze and make decisions of ethical dilemma in order to urge them to develop critical thinking and proper judgment. The concepts of this course focus on the ethical basic concepts and the application of ethical principles: including the analysis and discussion of ethics and moral concepts; the formation and conflicts of values, the rights and responsibilities of patients and nurses; the cooperational relationships of medical team; application the main theories and principles of ethics; nursing code, ethical dilemma, and the ethical decision framework.', '1238', '4104Q891', '410442', '護四四Ｂ', '1238'),
(1099, '1023', '1131', '張淑芳', '111401423014B0', '11140', '1423', '1', 4, 0, '實證健康照護', 'Evidence-Based Practice in Healthcare', '張淑芳', 50, 9, 41, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G402', '2', '3,4', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大四', '本課程目標在協助學生獲得實證護理相關的知識與技能。課程以執行實證五步驟為架構，內容包含:介紹實證護理概念、提出實證可以回答的臨床問題(PICO)、文獻資料庫與搜尋最佳證據、評析文獻與實證護理應用。實作方面包含:運用學習小組練習以PICO詢問臨床問題、搜尋回答問題之最佳證據、練習評讀隨機控制研究、判斷證據等級、提出臨床決策建議及閱讀系統性文獻回顧文章。', 'This course aims to introduceevidence-based nursing and strengthen knowledge and skills of evidence-based nursing for nursing students. Course contents includefundationalconcepts of evidence-based nursing, concepts of systematic review and clinical guideline, PICO, searching for the current best evidence, methodologyappraisal, and analyzing data. Students will have the opportunity to practice skills of using PICO to ask answerable clinical questions, searching the evidence and assessing quality of a randomized controlled trial, levels of evidence, and reading articles of systema tric review .', '804', '4104Q951', '410442', '護四四Ｂ', '804'),
(1100, '1024', '1131', '陳貞秀', '111400386014B0', '11140', '386', '1', 4, 0, '護理臨床專論', 'Introduction for Nursing Employment', '陳貞秀', 42, 8, 34, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G402', '2', '6,7', '修課限制：本系四技一般生大三以上、護理系學士後大三', '本課程旨在協助學生未來能順利的適應職涯的環境，透過討論、講授、參與職涯講座、資料搜尋、自學及分組報告等方式，認識台灣各層級醫院、優質護理職場之條件、職場相關議題和護理新鮮人可能面臨的問題，進而協助學生能有適當的選擇就業職場。', 'The purpose of the course is to guide and prepare students for the practicum of obtaining nursing employment. Through lecturing and discussion, students will be familiar with the purposes and agendas of the practicum, and knowing how to prepare themselves in advance to facilitate their learning during the practicum. Through the preparation of the course, students are expected to be able to integrate and apply nursing theories, related knowledge, and skills in nursing practice. In together with the practicum for obtaining nursing employment course, this course is aimed to develop students’ clinical competence in providing evidence-based, individualized, and prioritized nursing care.', '377', '4104Q901', '410442', '護四四Ｂ', '377'),
