(1214, '1111', '1131', '林惠如', '118700828011A0', '11870', '828', '1', 1, 0, '科學哲學與知識發展', 'Philosophy of Science and Knowledge Development', '林惠如,賴倩瑜,黃慧芬', 7, 5, 2, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B603', '2', '2,3,4', '\"\"\"修課限制 Course restrictions ： \n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.本所國內博士班一年級、本所國際博士班一年級 Eligible students include first-year students of the International Nursing program (doctoral level) and first-year students of domestic doctoral programs in nursing.\"\"\"\n', '本課程旨在培養學生探索、批判、分析與建構護理知識之能力。主要學習經驗包括 區辨及探討科學哲學的演進與知識建構之型式，科學的哲理、批判理論以及探討及評值 概念的建構及理論的發展。透過相互的研討，期能使護理博士學生能從科學哲學與知識 認識層面，探討其所關注的護理議題，且應用理論或概念建構發展與實務議題有關之護 理理論或概念模式。', 'This course aims to provide students with the skills to investigate, assess, and analyze nursing knowledge. The learning experience involves the exploration of the development of science philosophy and of nursing knowledge. The course is a research and discussion experience aimed at enabling doctoral graduate students to become knowledgeable about approaches to studies of scientific knowledge development. Forces affecting the development of knowledge, the origins of key terms and concepts, and the identification of nursing issues related to epistemology and the philosophy of science identification will also be explored.', '839', '7101Q581', '710712', '國際博一', '83,914,390,843'),
(1215, '1112', '1131', '王采芷', '118701182011A0', '11870', '1182', '1', 1, 0, '高等量性研究方法論', 'Advanced Quantitative Research Methods', '王采芷,李慈音,葉美玲', 7, 5, 2, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B636', '4', '6,7,8', '\"授課教室 Classroom ：B636。 \"\"修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n 1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.本所國內博士班一年級、本所國際博士班一年級 Eligible students include first-year students of the International Nursing program (doctoral level) and first-year students of domestic doctoral programs in nursing.\"\"\"\n', '本課程為進階量性研究方法論；課程在探討實證護理應用於實務及不同的研究設計方 法之特性及優缺點，並進一步介紹各個研究步驟之重點及相關議題。學生將依指引檢驗與 批判已發表於專業期刊當中之研究文獻，學習發表研究報告之重點；以期未來能以此知識 為基礎，完成完善的量性研究計畫。', 'This course addresses theoretical basis of advanced quantitative methods. Focus of the course is placed on the importance of nursing research in evidence-based practice. Various research designs, research steps and related issues will be thoroughly discussed. Based on the guidance, students are required to critique papers published in well-known journals. After completion of the class, students will learn to appreciate a research paper, report the research findings, and develop their research plans in the near future.', '860', '7101Q591', '710712', '國際博一', '86,008,150,854'),
(1216, '1113', '1131', '賴倩瑜', '118701600011A0', '11870', '1600', '1', 1, 0, '進階護理實務專論', 'Doctoral Seminar in Nursing Science', '賴倩瑜,黎靜婷,黃慧芬,盧玉嬴', 7, 5, 2, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B636', '4', '3,4', '\"授課教室 Classroom ：B636。 修課限制 Course restrictions ： \n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.本所國內博士班一年級、本所國際碩士班一年級 Eligible students include first-year students of the International Nursing program (doctoral level) and first-year students of domestic doctoral programs in nursing.\"\"\"\n', 'This course aims to provide nursing doctoral students to obtain clinical or research experiences at health related institutions. Based on familiar with clinical issues, students will analyze and interpret the current development of nursing science, involve the related practice. In this course, students engage in a 144-hour advanced practicum in theory-guided practice in a selected domain of nursing. Concurrently, students participate in two seminars to present the progress of practicum and clinical experiences, and the theoretical and evidence based nursing care model', 'This course aims to provide nursing doctoral students to obtain clinical or research experiences at health related institutions. Based on familiar with clinical issues, students will analyze and interpret the current development of nursing science, involve the related practice. In this course, students engage in a 144-hour advanced practicum in theory-guided practice in a selected domain of nursing. Concurrently, students participate in two seminars to present the progress of practicum and clinical experiences, and the theoretical and evidence based nursing care model', '1439', '7101Q601', '710712', '國際博一', '1,439,112,008,430,880'),
(1217, '1114', '1131', '梁淑媛', '11870200000000 ', '11870', '1672', '1', 2, 20, '系統性文獻回顧與統合分析', 'Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis', '李美銀,梁淑媛,葉美玲', 6, 1, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F604', '2', '7,8,9', '\"個人可以上機的電腦教室至少12台\"\"1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English.\n 2.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 3.可選學生為護理所國際博士班學生 Eligible students include students of the International Nursing program (doctoral level)\"\"\"\n', '本課程為系統性文獻回顧與統合分析及實務實作，旨在應用實證步驟於研究及實務。課程介紹系統性文獻回顧實證健康照護、組織及計畫系統性文獻回顧、文獻搜尋技巧的原則及資源、評析文獻、資料萃取及處理、統合分析。課程實務實作包含運用學習小組進行實作練習，進一步執行相關主題資料萃取及統合分析之實務操作。', 'The course Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis addresses the steps of Systematic review and meta-analysis in the nursing research and the evidence in nursing practice. Focus of the course is planced on the evidence-based nursing care，organizing and planning a systematic review，key princuples，resources and techniques for searching the literature，critical appraisal appraisal，introduce deta extraction and managment，introduce Meta-Analysis. For the practice，the course is also placed on the deta extraction，management and analysis for RCT and observational research design.After completion of the ，students will learn to develop a specific issue related systematic review and Meta-Analysis to nursing practice.', '895', '7102Z791', '710R20', '護國博20', '41,708,950,854'),
(1218, '1115', '1131', '戴君倚', '11870100000000 ', '11870', '845', '1', 2, 21, '測量工具的發展與建構', 'Measurement and Instrumentation', '戴君倚,邱秀渝,張靜芬', 6, 1, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'B128', '4', '2,3,4', '\"\"\"修課限制 Course restrictions ： \n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.可選學生為護理所國際博士班二年級以上學生、護理所國內博士班二年級學生 Eligible students include second-year and higher-level students of the International Nursing program (doctoral level) and second-year students of domestic doctoral programs in nursing. 3.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools.\"\"\"\n', 'This course aims to provide comprehensive knowledge of the theory and foundation which underlies measurement process, current measurement and measurers of frequently used in health-related inquiry, and to promote their ability in applying principles of instrument development to current measurement problem. Course contents include theories of measurement, psychometric quality of research instruments, strategies for designing measures, measurement issues in health-related inquiry, and application of principles of instruments development in research study.', 'This course aims to provide comprehensive knowledge of the theory and foundation which underlies measurement process, current measurement and measurers of frequently used in health-related inquiry, and to promote their ability in applying principles of instrument development to current measurement problem. Course contents include theories of measurement, psychometric quality of research instruments, strategies for designing measures, measurement issues in health-related inquiry, and application of principles of instruments development in research study.', '892', '7102Z741', '710R21', '護國博21', '89,208,140,825'),
(1219, '1116', '1131', '', '118700849012A0', '11870', '849', '1', 2, 0, '論文專題研究I', 'Dissertation Independent Study I', '黃慧芬,林惠如,李慈音,劉玟宜,盧玉嬴', 5, 0, 5, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '7', '1,2', '\"\"\"修課限制 Course restrictions ： \n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 3.本所國際博士班可選 Eligible students include students of the International Nursing program (doctoral level) 4.書面選課 Registration will be done by paper application using the form generated from the system.\"\"\"\n', '本課程以個別指導之形式，依據博士生未來護理專業發展方向，引導學生探索護理實務相關之研究議題，進行相關理論及照護模式之分析，結合其臨床專業技能，應用批判性思考及實證護理的概念，與產官學界等多方領域先進之討論，訂定研究方向及主題，擬定研究設計、進行或完成研究計畫之撰寫。', 'This course is conducted through individualized instruction and is designed to guide doctoral students in exploring research topics relevant to their future nursing professional development. It involves the analysis of pertinent theories and care models, integration of their clinical expertise, application of critical thinking and evidence-based nursing concepts, and engagement in discussions with experts from various sectors including academia, industry, and government. The course aims to help the student determine his/her research direction and topic, formulate research designs, and initiate or complete the writing of a research proposal.', '0', '7102Z781', '710722', '國際博二', '8,430,839,081,508,710,000'),
(1220, '1117', '1131', '許智皓', '118700834012A0', '11870', '834', '1', 2, 0, '環境與健康政策', 'Environment and Health Policy', '許智皓,謝佳容,周幸生', 6, 1, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B635', '4', '5,6,7', '\"修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n 1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.本所國內博士班二年級、本所國際博士班二年級 Eligible students include second-year students of the International Nursing program (doctoral level) and second-year students of domestic doctoral programs in nursing.\"\"\"\n', '本課程在提供學生對環境與健康政策的整體觀，從預防保健的角度分析國內及國際的環境與健康政策議題，並重新定位健康與環境政策原則。學生可針對各國健康政策的推動、健康服務品質的保障、國內外政府與非政府之健康組織與資源的整合與運用等議題進行分析與討論，針對上述健康政策議題提出需求評估、計畫評值或成果評價。', 'This course is aimed to provide a holistic view of health services. Social, economic, and political influences on environment and health policy internationally and nationally are analyzed from a political economy perspective. Students critique and debate a variety of health care reforms to enhance quality, assure access, and improve cost efficiency. The application of nursing research in outcome studies, program evaluation, and needs assessment is explored.', '971', '7102Q181', '710722', '國際博二', '97,190,150,440'),
(1221, '1118', '1131', '', '118700854013A0', '11870', '854', '1', 3, 0, '博士論文I', 'Dissertation I', '梁淑媛', 1, 0, 1, 6.00, '全18週', 6.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '2', '\"\"\"修課限制 Course restrictions ： \n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 3.本所國際博士班可選 Eligible students include students of the International Nursing program (doctoral level) 4.書面選課 Registration will be done by paper application using the form generated from the system.\"\"\"\n修課限制：全英語授課、書面選課', '本課程以個別指導之形式，旨在協助博士生以臨床實務或護理專業發展為基礎，應用相關理論、照護模式及研究能力，執行研究計畫，進行資料分析、研究成果報告發表及博士論文之撰寫。', 'This course is structured as individualized instruction with the aim of assisting the doctoral student who is building upon his/her clinical practice or nursing professional development. It emphasizes the application of relevant theories, nursing care models, and research skills, the execution of research projects, data analysis, publishing of the results of studies, and the writing of his/her dissertation.', '0', '7103Q291', '710732', '國際博三', '895'),
(1222, '1119', '1131', '', '118700850013A0', '11870', '850', '1', 3, 0, '論文專題研究II', 'Dissertation Independent Study II', '謝佳容,劉介宇,王采芷', 3, 2, 1, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '6', '1', '\"\"\"修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n 1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 3.本所國際博士班可選 Eligible students include students of the International Nursing program (doctoral level) 4.書面選課 Registration will be done by paper application using the form generated from the system.\"\"\"\n', '本課程以個別指導之形式，依據博士生未來護理專業發展方向，引導學生應用相關核心概念，發展護理相關理論及照護模式，結合其臨床專業技能，應用批判性思考及實證護理的概念，確認研究主題及設計、完成博士論文研究計畫之書寫。', 'This course is structured as individualized instruction, tailored to the doctoral student’s future development in the field of nursing. It guides the student to apply relevant core concepts, develop nursing-related theories and nursing care models, integrate his/her clinical expertise, employ critical thinking and evidence-based nursing concepts, and confirm his/her research topic and designs. It culminates in the completion of a written research proposal for his/her dissertation.', '0', '7103Z071', '710732', '國際博三', '901,505,980,860'),
(1223, '1120', '1131', '', '118700855014A0', '11870', '855', '1', 4, 0, '博士論文II', 'Dissertation II', '林惠如,王凱微', 2, 0, 2, 6.00, '全18週', 6.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '4', '\"\"\"修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n 1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 3.本所國際博士班可選 Eligible students include students of the International Nursing program (doctoral level) 4.書面選課 Registration will be done by paper application using the form generated from the system.\"\"\"\n修課限制：全英語授課、書面選課、本所', '本課程以個別指導之形式，旨在協助博士生以臨床實務或護理專業發展為基礎，應用相關理論、照護模式及研究能力，執行研究計畫，進行資料分析，完成博士論文之撰寫。', 'This course is conducted through individualized instruction with the objective of assisting the doctoral student who is building upon his/her clinical practice or nursing professional development. It focuses on the application of relevant theories, nursing care models, and research skills, the execution of research projects, data analysis, and the completion of the dissertation.', '0', '7104Q041', '710742', '國際博四', '8,390,789');
