(1224, '1121', '1131', '羅素', '118600617011A0', '11860', '617', '1', 1, 0, '高等生物應用統計學', 'Advanced Applied Biostatistics', '羅素', 13, 4, 9, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F604', '3', '2,3,4', ' \"修課限制 Course restrictions ： 1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.與助產所國際碩士班合開 Co-offered with the International Midwifery program. 3.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 4.本所國際碩士班、助產所國際碩士班、本所國內碩士班一年級可選 Eligible students include students of the International Nursing program (master\'s level), students of the International Midwifery program, and first-year students of domestic master\'s programs in nursing.\n', '本課程以教授研究所學生具有進階應用生物統計學的分析能力。強調生物統計學之應用與醫學及護理臨床研究結合，以奠定學生具有資料收集、資料分析及統計報表解讀之能力，同時有能力評值學術期刊所發表的文章。課程內容包括：基本機率論、機率分佈理論、統計估計及檢定(獨立樣本及成對樣本t-test)、變異數分析(ANOVA)、相關係數、簡單迴歸分析到複迴歸分析等議題。本課程將會使用SPSS等專業統計軟體之操作。', 'Biostatistics plays an essential role in all stages of a quantitative health care research from design through to analysis and interpretation. This course covers the essential principles and methods required for a master degree. Emphasis is on study design, appropriate analysis, software application (SPSS) and interpretation of results. The underlying concepts of statistical analysis are covered. Sessions include lectures and practical work, both computer-based and using small workshops for discussion.\r\nThe course aims to teach health care researchers the essential elements of research methodology and statistics. The focus is mainly on interpretation and understanding appropriate methodology.', '1090', '6101Q771', '610212', '國際碩一', '1090'),
(1225, '1122', '1131', '王采芷', '118600618011A0', '11860', '618', '1', 1, 0, '健康評估及實驗', 'Health Assessment for Advanced Practice Nursing', '王采芷,張靜芬,謝雨珊,鄭夙芬', 7, 3, 4, 3.00, '全18週', 4.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B517', '4', '6,7,8,9', '\"授課教室 Classroom：B517。 修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n 1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 3.本所國際碩士班、本所國內碩士班一年級可選 Eligible students include students of the International Nursing program (master\'s level) and first-year students of domestic master\'s programs in nursing.\"\"\"\n', '本課程旨在增強學生臨床實務相關評估之學理與技巧。課程內容著重於應用病史訪談、心理與生理評估技巧、詮釋評估結果於各年齡層之個案。學生須針對個案之個別性，應用相關學理與技巧，進行評估、分析與診斷個案健康問題，以達成課程的目標。', 'The purpose of the course is to advance students’ physical assessment theory and skills that related to professional clinical nursing practice. The content of the course is emphasized on application skills of client interview, physiological and psychologi', '860', '6101Q781', '610212', '國際碩一', '860,082,508,990,812'),
(1226, '1123', '1131', '', '118600161011A0', '11860', '161', '1', 1, 0, '專題研究', 'Independent Study', '劉桂芬,陳妙言', 2, 0, 2, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '6', '1', '\"修課限制 Course restrictions ： \n1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 3.本所國際碩士班可選 Eligible students include students of the International Nursing program (master\'s level). 4.書面選課 Registration will be done by paper application using the form generated from the system.\"\"\"\n修課限制：全英語授課、書面選課、本所', '', '', '0', '6101Z201', '610212', '國際碩一', '8,330,883'),
(1227, '1124', '1131', '李嘉雯', '118600616011A0', '11860', '616', '1', 1, 0, '護理理論', 'Nursing Theory', '李嘉雯,陳淑溫', 13, 4, 9, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B111', '5', '3,4', '\"修課限制 Course restrictions ： 1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.與助產所國際碩士班合開 Co-offered with the International Midwifery program. 3.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 4.本所國際碩士班、助產所國際碩士班、本所國內碩士班一年級可選 Eligible students include students of the International Nursing program (master\'s level), students of the International Midwifery program, and first-year students of domestic master\'s programs in nursing.\"\n', '本課程旨在培養學生應用護理理論於實務、研究、教育和行政中之能力。主要學習經驗包括探討護理理論發展史、理論家背景、理論的重要概念及其闡述的現象、理論的應用。在引導下，學生深入研討至少一個護理理論，透過相關文獻的分析、歸納和演譯，練習將整合後的心得和經驗提出報告與同學分享、討論以達成本課程的目標。', 'This course examines several nursing concepts and their applications to the current health care environment including practice, education, administration, and research. Students begin to recognize the nature of science and its relationships to theories in nursing. Through discussion, lecture, and specially designed projects, students will learn the philosophy and background of a theorist and her/his theory and develop skills in analyzing health care issue, particularly those with relevance to nursing.', '277', '6101Q761', '610212', '國際碩一', '2,770,331'),
(1228, '1125', '1131', '羅素', '11860100000000 ', '11860', '624', '1', 2, 21, '統計資料管理與分析策略', 'Data Management &amp; Statistical Analysis', '羅素', 9, 1, 8, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F604', '1', '6,7,8', ' \"修課限制 Course restrictions ： 1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.與助產所國際碩士班合開 Co-offered with the International Midwifery program. 3.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 4.本所國際碩士班、助產所國際碩士班、本所國內碩士班一年級可選 Eligible students include students of the International Nursing program (master\'s level), students of the International Midwifery program, and students of domestic master\'s programs in nursing.\n', '本科目於教學設計上，乃著眼於資料庫管理與統合各種量性資料分析方法之實務操作，目標在於提昇學生管理與分析統計相關資料之能力。課程中將運用SPSS統計套裝軟體來學習以下統計資料管理與分析策略：1)建立資料庫檔案並進行資料庫檔案之增刪、編輯與修改；2)著手分析健康照護相關之研究資料、繪製資料圖表;3)運用描述性與推論性統計策略;4)撰寫研究資料之分析結果。整體而言，選修本課程之學生，將透過課程講授、實際練習操作統計套裝軟體及實例研討等方法，落實學習統計資料之管理與分析。', 'The objective of this course is to provide students with practical applications of bio-statistical methods by running the SPSS statistical software. Two sample data (depression data and factor analysis data) in the health related agendas will demonstrate', '1090', '6102Z881', '610R21', '護國碩21', '1090'),
(1229, '1126', '1131', '許智皓', '11860100000000 ', '11860', '622', '1', 2, 22, '國際健康政策與實務', 'International Health Policy and Practice', '許智皓,謝佳容,魏秀靜', 9, 1, 8, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'B324', '3', '2,3,4', '本地生護理碩士班、助產所可選   \" 修課限制 Course restrictions ： 1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.與助產所國際碩士班合開 Co-offered with the International Midwifery program. 3.不開放跨校選課 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 4.本所國際碩士班二年級、助產所國際碩士班二年級、本所國內碩士班二年級可選 Eligible second-year students include students of the International Nursing program (master\'s level), second-year students of the International Midwifery program, and second-year students of domestic master\'s programs in nursing.\"\n', '本課程旨在提供有關國際健康政策相關議題的概述,協助護理學生以全球化觀點了解未來的執業環境.課程內容包括:國際與全球健康,影響健康的相關因素探討,國內外相關資源,不同地理區域的健康問題,健康疾病指標,以及國際健康未來趨勢.', 'This course is designed to provide introductory content in international health and nursing useful for all level of health care students who will be practicing in the era of globalization, regardless of whether they personally plan to live or work. The th', '971', '6102Z871', '610R22', '護國碩22', '97,190,150,868'),
(1230, '1127', '1131', '許智皓', '118601748012A0', '11860', '1748', '1', 2, 0, '進階護理II', 'Advanced Practice Nursing II', '林惠如,賴倩瑜,許智皓', 6, 1, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B635', '1', '2,3,4', '\"修課限制 Course restrictions ：\n 1.全英語授課 Taught entirely in English. 2.不開放跨校 Not open for cross-registration with students from other schools. 3.本所國際碩士班碩二以上可選 Eligible students include second-year and higher-level students of the International Nursing program (master\'s level).\"\"\"\n', '', 'This course is aimed to increase students\' understanding of the major concepts and related theories \r\nof advanced practice nursing. The focus is on the management of mental health issues as well as the \r\ncommunity health. The course will provide students with fundamental knowledge necessary to \r\ndeliver advanced nursing care for clients with mental health conditions as well as for clients in the \r\ncommunity settings. The roles and function of advance practice nurses will be integrated throughout \r\nthe course. Through lectures, discussions, and reports, students will expand their knowledge and \r\ncompetency for managing common mental health issues and community health by integrating \r\nevidenced-based nursing and their clinical experiences.', '971', '6102Q0A1', '610222', '國際碩二', '83,914,390,971'),
(1231, '1128', '1131', '李英芬', '11462100000000 ', '11462', '720', '1', 1, 10, '臨床藥理及治療學', 'Clinical Pharmacology &amp; Therapeutics', '謝雨珊,李英芬', 9, 3, 6, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G407', '6', '6,7,8', '修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、老人組、婦女組、精神組、社區組、兒童組、護資組、專師組、中西醫組）', '本課程之設計係以護理研究所碩士班學生為授課對象。課程內容著重目前有關心血管藥理、癌症治療等方面之進展為主，並探討相關藥物之藥理作用機轉與目前臨床應用有關之藥物資訊等，故使用之教材係取自較新之期刊論文，目的是讓學生對於最近之醫藥相關科學之發現與進展能獲得最新資訊。', 'This elective course is designed for nursing students at the graduate level. It emphasizes the pharmacological mechanisms and clinical application of the agents commonly prescribed in disease teratment. Topics in this course include drugs acting on cardio', '993', '6001Z111', '600M10', '護專碩10', '8,990,993'),
(1232, '1129', '1131', '李慧貞', '11462100000000 ', '11462', '835', '1', 1, 11, '健康促進與管理', 'Health promotion and management', '李慧貞,周輝政', 8, 1, 7, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G407', '4', '11,12,13,14', '修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、老人組、婦女組、精神組、社區組、兒童組、護資組、專師組、中西醫組）、本系國內博士班、外所國內碩博士班（是否列入畢業學分，請參照入學年課程科目表）', '本課程主要協助學生瞭解健康促進與管理之實務層面與其相關研究，期使學生能在健康促進與管理之理論與實務有所認識，而應用於臨床有關健康促進與管理層面之照護，以增進學生健康照護之能力。課程內容包含健康促進與管理相關之理論與研究以及實務層面之見習，例如：健康促進與管理之相關理論、體重管理之機轉，評值、體重過重與過輕對健康之影響，與疾病相關之影響、兒童肥胖與更年期肥胖、各種健康管理之策略、臨床健康管理週課程見習。', 'This course provides students to have the basic concepts of health promotion and management for health care. The major focus of the course encompasses: Introduction(Prevalence, evaluation of body composition) Etiology and health impact of obesity and underweight Obesity related disease: Metabolic syndrome, health management related problem in menopausal women, Health problems in Abnormal weight during childhood, Clinical approach of weight management, Nutritional strategies of weight management , Exercise strategies of management , Comparison of variant diet of health promotion and management: evidence based approach Visiting clinics 1(including exercise practice and diet preparation practice) ,Obesity treatment: medical, surgical and herbal preparation , Behavior approach of health promotion and management, E-health management. Students present their understanding of the health issues about health promotion and management through the participation and discussion in the class.', '830', '6001Z121', '600M11', '護專碩11', '8,300,621'),
(1233, '1130', '1131', '翁仕彥', '114620687011A0', '11462', '687', '1', 1, 0, '高等生物統計學', 'Advanced Biostatistics', '翁仕彥', 24, 4, 20, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S103', '5', '12,13', '修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、專師組）、程式設計課程', '本課程旨在介紹高等生物統計學之廣義線性模式分析方法、實用觀念、探討應用以及可行之技巧及工具，引導學生操作或使用SPSS和SAS等分析工具。透過本課程之講授和練習，可讓學生具備對廣泛醫學資料之模式分析能力，進一步能夠批判文獻、評估研究設計及相關推論之效能，並運用於工作之專業上。修讀本課程需先具備基本之流行病學概論及生物統計學基礎。', 'The focus of this course is applied statistical techniques, with emphasis on data management, and data analysis through the Statistical Package for the Social Sciences. This course will complete weekly computer assignments that provide \"hands on\" experience with data analysis and interpretation of results. Students will actually understand statistical procedures and apply statistical techniques to concrete data.', '252', '6001Q561', '600211', '護專研一', '252'),
(1234, '1131', '1131', '廖珮宏', '114620825011A0', '11462', '825', '1', 1, 0, '健康評估及實作', 'Health Assessment for Advanced Practice Nursing', '廖珮宏,謝雨珊,柯莉珊', 21, 4, 17, 3.00, '全18週', 4.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'S401', '5', '6,7,8,9', '修課限制：本所碩士班（老人組、護資組、專師組）', '本課程旨在增強學生臨床實務相關評估之學理與技巧。課程內容著重於應用病史訪談、心理與生理評估技巧、詮釋評估結果於各年齡層之個案。學生須針對個案之個別性，應用相關學理與技巧，進行評估、分析與診斷個案健康問題，以達成課程的目標。', 'The purpose of the course is to advance students\' physical assessment theory and skills that related to \r\nadvanced nursing practice. The content of the course is emphasized on application skills of client \r\ninterview, physiological and psychological assessment, interpreting results in individuals. This course \r\nfocuses on development of clinical decision making skills in the process of health assessment. Applying \r\ntheories and techniques, assessing, analyzing and diagnosing health problems on selected clients. As \r\none outcome of this course, students demonstrate comprehensive and integrative health assessment \r\npractice and written skills.', '877', '6001Q571', '600211', '護專研一', '87,708,990,821'),
(1235, '1132', '1131', '黎靜婷', '114620616011A0', '11462', '616', '1', 1, 0, '護理理論', 'Nursing Theories', '黎靜婷,簡翠薇', 21, 4, 17, 2.00, '全18週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'G203', '5', '10,11', '修課限制：本所碩士班（老人組、護資組、專師組）', '本課程旨在培養學生應用護理理論於實務、研究、教育和行政中之能力。主要學習經驗包括探討護理理論發展史、理論家背景、理論的重要概念及其闡述的現象、理論的應用。在引導下，學生深入研討至少一個護理理論，透過相關文獻的分析、歸納和演譯，練習將整合後的心得和經驗提出報告與同學分享、討論以達成本課程的目標。', 'This course examines several nursing concepts and their applications to the current health care environment including practice, education, administration, and research. Students begin to recognize the nature of science and its relationships to theories in', '1120', '6001Q581', '600211', '護專研一', '11,200,810'),
(1236, '1133', '1131', '謝雨珊', '114680712012A0', '11468', '712', '1', 2, 0, '成人專科護理 II', 'Adult Practice Nursing II', '謝雨珊,王采芷,簡靜慧', 9, 1, 8, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F501', '5', '2,3,4', '07/10暑期提前授課，修課限制：本所碩士班（專師組）研二以上', '本課程旨在培育成人專科護理師學生具備急性醫療特定疾病病人之進階知識與技能，並加強其對對專科護理師角色、功能與執業議題之瞭解。課程強調運用批判性思維與實證醫學和護理，以建立適當之健康問題診斷、處置和評價照護結果之學習。透過講述、學生課堂導讀、案例分析、小組討論、角色扮演、影片情境分析與數位平台討論等多元教學策略，訓練學生批判性思考、溝通與自學能力，並培養學生具備成人專科護理師入門所需之知識與技能，使其能以專科護理師的角色提供急性醫療特定疾病病人適切之進階護理照護。', 'This course provides the student with in-depth knowledge of advanced nursing management of complicated and acutely ill adults. Emphasis is on the utilization of critical thinking and evidence-based practice to formulate diagnoses and management and evaluation plans of care for physiologically unstable and complicated adult patients who have multiple complex health problems, and are at high risk for developing complications.  The focus is on the management of specific system problems of acute care. This course provides students with advanced knowledge necessary to deliver advanced nursing care in acute care settings.', '899', '6002Q2P1', '600221', '護專研二', '89,908,600,485'),
(1237, '1134', '1131', '謝雨珊', '114680713012A0', '11468', '713', '1', 2, 0, '成人專科護理實習 II', 'Adult Practice Nursing II - Practicum', '謝雨珊,王采芷,簡靜慧', 9, 1, 8, 3.00, '全18週', 9.20, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '5', '修課限制：實習課程、本所碩士班（專師組）研二以上', '本課程旨在培育成人專科護理師學生，具備急性醫療嚴重病人照護之進階知識與技能，並加強其對對專科護理師執業議題之瞭解。實習課程強調運用批判性思維與實證醫學和護理，以建立適當之健康問題診斷、處置和評價照護結果於所照護之個案。透過實習契約書之訂定、實習指導教師與實習教學教師的共同輔導、實習日誌、個案報告、互動記錄、臨床照護指引、教案與實習心得的完成，以確保學生的實習經驗，至實習結束每位學生將至少照護十位內外科急性醫療嚴重病人，以培養學生具備成人專科護理師所需之知識與技能，使其能以專科護理師的角色提供病情嚴重之急性醫療病人適切之進階護理照護。', 'The course is a continuum of the clinical practicum for adult health nursing I. The purposes of the course are (1) to train students’ competencies in assessing, diagnosing, examining, and managing common medical and surgical health problems, (2) to facilitate students’ consultation ability for emotional responses of acute ill patients, (3) to cultivate students’ case management ability, (4) to increase students’ communication and collaboration to achieve excellent care, and (5) to be familiar with ethical and legal issues affecting NP practice in Taiwan.. Within the practicum, student will demonstrate actual roles and responsibilities of an acute care nurse practitioner.', '899', '6002Q2W1', '600221', '護專研二', '89,908,600,485'),
(1238, '1135', '1131', '柯莉珊', '114620708012A0', '11462', '708', '1', 2, 0, '老人健康照護 II', 'Health Care of Elderly II', '柯莉珊,林惠如,謝佳容,陳妙言,簡翠薇', 5, 0, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'F405', '5', '1,2,3,4', '授課時間：08:30-11:20，修課限制：本所碩士班（老人組）研二以上', '此課程旨在透過對老人健康照護政策、管理、策略及社區發展的理論、研究與議題研討，增進學生對老人照護相關之管理、領導、教育、諮商等能力。學生需統整及應用老人健康照護、經濟、主要照顧者、社會支持、組織發展等理論研究於實務情境中，發揮其個案管理及團體照護之功能，並需獨立針對特定議題完成專案以展現其老人照顧專家的角色功能，並展現其統合資源建立社區網絡之能力。', 'This course is designed to cultivate students’ abilities on management, leadership, education, and consultant of elder care services, based on the theories of elder policy, management, strategy, and community development. Students have to integrate the theories of elder health, economy, caregiver, social support, organizational development, etc., and apply into the real situations. Students are expected to express the roles and function of case management and group care, to implement and evaluate health care project for elder groups, and to synthesis community resources.', '821', '6002Q2Y1', '600221', '護專研二', '8,210,839,901,508,830,000'),
(1239, '1136', '1131', '柯莉珊', '114620709012A0', '11462', '709', '1', 2, 0, '老人健康照護實習 II', 'Health Care of Elderly II -Practicum', '柯莉珊,林惠如,謝佳容,陳妙言,簡翠薇', 5, 0, 5, 3.00, '全18週', 9.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '5', '修課限制：實習課程、本所碩士班（老人組）研二以上', '此課程旨在透過對老人健康照護政策、管理、策略及社區發展的理論、強化臨床\r\n批判思考能力於老人相關研究與議題研討，增進學生對老人照護相關之管理、領\r\n導、教育、諮商及決策判斷等能力。學生需統整及應用老人健康照護、經濟、主\r\n要照顧者、社會支持、組織發展等理論研究於實務情境中，發揮其個案管理及團\r\n體照護之功能，並需獨立針對特定議題運用批判思考完成專案報告以展現其老人\r\n照顧專家的角色功能並能增進學生統合資源建立社區網絡之能力。', 'This course in designed to assist students acquiring ageing health policy, administration, strategy theory in the community nursing care of aging population. In this course, students are required self-direction learning, and will join an organization in community, interest to special issue and demonstrate the role functions of case manager in appropriate clinical settings.', '821', '6002Q2Z1', '600221', '護專研二', '8,210,839,901,508,830,000'),
(1240, '1137', '1131', '李慈音', '114660704012A0', '11466', '704', '1', 2, 0, '兒童健康照護 II', 'Health Care of Children (II)', '李慈音,林芳怡,黃秀玫,李美銀', 4, 0, 4, 3.00, '全18週', 3.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B6021', '5', '2,3,4', '修課限制：本所碩士班（兒童組）研二以上', '本課程在協助學生發展照顧由醫療機構至社區中具有健康問題兒童之進階護理能力。藉由相關理論及實證研究，探討不同發展階段中，具有特殊需求或高危險兒童所處的環境〈如：家庭、學校、社區〉對兒童生長發展的長期影響。內容並強調現有的醫療體系/健康政策、及社會資源與兒童及其家庭成員之間的相互影響，並從中思考所衍生的倫理議題。學生最終能具備統整知識及資源的能力並積極為個案及其家庭代言。', 'This course will explore the potential and existing issues derived from the children with health problems in the community. Based on the relevant theories and evidence based research findings, students will be able to 1) analyze the mutual influences among the children with health problems, their ecological systems and related health policies/ resources, 2) organize the client’s resources and develop effective plans in the care of children with health problems, and 3) act as advocates for the children when encountering the ethical issues.', '815', '6002Q2U1', '600221', '護專研二', '815,088,401,240,417'),
(1241, '1138', '1131', '李慈音', '114660705012A0', '11466', '705', '1', 2, 0, '兒童健康照護實習 II', 'Clinical practicum in Health Care of Children (II)', '李慈音,林芳怡,黃秀玫,李美銀', 3, 0, 3, 3.00, '全18週', 9.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', '', '7', '5', '修課限制：本所碩士班（兒童組）研二以上、實習課程', '本課程旨在協助學生發展持續性且完整性的進階護理能力，提供個案及其家庭由醫療機構延續至社區中之照顧；藉由相關理論及實證研究，探討不同發展階段中，具有特殊需求或高危險兒童所處的環境〈如：家庭、學校、社區〉對其生長發展的長期影響。內容並強調現有的醫療體系/健康政策、及社會資源與兒童及其家庭成員之間的關係，並從中思考所衍生的倫理議題。學生能統整並運用知識及資源提供完整及持續性的照護。', 'This course is designed to assist students acquiring clinical expertise in the care of children with special needs or children at risk. Students are required to select an interested area to practice. By thoroughly assessing and analyzing the client’s situation (health, environment, health policies and resources), students will integrate the evidence based knowledge and provide the continuity care to the family of a child with special needs or at risk. The practices of self-directed learning, problem solving and critical thinking skills are highly expected in this course.', '815', '6002Q2V1', '600221', '護專研二', '815,088,401,240,417'),
(1242, '1139', '1131', '', '114670161012A0', '11467', '161', '1', 2, 0, '專題研究', 'Independent Study', '', 0, 0, 0, 1.00, '全18週', 1.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', '', '7', '1', '授課時間地點請洽指導教授。修課限制：本所碩士班（護資組在職生）、書面選課', '本課程以個別指導之形式，依據碩士生之護理專長背景及未來專業發展方向，引導學生探索相關核心概念、理論，結合其臨床專業技能，應用批判性思考及實證護理的概念，訂定研究方向及主題，擬定研究設計、完成研究計畫之書寫。', 'This course is delivered in an individualized format, tailored to the nursing specialization and future professional development of the master\'s student. It guides students in exploring relevant core concepts and theories, integrating their clinical expertise, applying critical thinking and evidence-based nursing concepts, determining research directions and topics, and developing research designs, culminating in the completion of a research proposal.', '0', '6002Z841', '600221', '護專研二', ''),
