(1298, '1193', '1131', '劉吉豐', '11230000000000 ', '11230', '366', '1', 3, 30, '耳穴貼壓理論與實務', 'Auricular Acupressure', '劉吉豐', 55, 5, 50, 2.00, '第1~9週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'F301', '1', '6,7,8,9', '修課限制：\n1.本系二技進修部、本系二技一般生、本系四技一般生、護理學院。\n2.密集前9周上課，選課至加退選第二階段。', '本科目希望透過耳穴貼壓知識介紹與實作技巧之結合，讓學生有基本的健康措施與中醫照護的概念，能搜尋相關文獻瞭解非傷害性中醫措施的重要，可分析目前市場求需求及相關照護的優缺點，學習問題解決與激發中醫措施創意之動機與實作，促進健康照護創意思考與創造力。課程包含：陰陽理論、五行概念、健康照護產品實務創作或改良等。', 'This course aims to provide students with the basic concepts of health-care auricular acupressure design and through delivering health promotion knowledge and practical application. It enables them to search relevant research papers and patent materials, so as to realize the importance of intellectual property rights. Meanwhile, they are taught to analyze the current market demands and the strength and weakness of related health promotion methods, learning problem solution and creativity of health-care products, and be encouraged creativity thinking of health care. Major focuses of the course include concepts of Chinese medical sciences, universal design, and practical application and improvement of health promotion.', '710', '3103Z1F1', '310G30', '護夜二30', '710'),
(1299, '1194', '1131', '韓惠萍', '11230000000000 ', '11230', '321', '1', 3, 30, '自殺與防治概論', 'Suicide and Prevention', '韓惠萍', 50, 5, 45, 2.00, '第1~9週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G201', '1', '11,12,13,14', '修課限制：\n1.本系二技進修部、本系學士後、助產系(一、二年級)、遠距教學課程、混合式遠距教學。\n2.密集前9周上課，選課至加退選第二階段。', '本課程主要目的在探討自殺之理論及相關概念包括自殺之定義、影響因素及後續反應，台灣地區與世界各國之自殺防治策略。課程特別強調自殺高危險群、自殺徵兆之評估，自殺行為之處置，自殺遺族之照護，防治策略之探討，期能使學習者獲得自殺防治全面性之觀念與實務性之經驗。', 'This course provides nursing students with knowledge about suicide and prevention. The major elements include the theory of suicide, definition of suicide and related factor, influence, suicidal preventing strategy. Students are required to identify and e', '960', '3103Z1D1', '310G30', '護夜二30', '960'),
(1300, '1195', '1131', '徐淑貞', '11230100000000 ', '11230', '1107', '1', 3, 30, '園藝治療概論', 'Introduction of Horticultural Therapy', '徐淑貞', 50, 5, 45, 2.00, '第1~9週', 2.00, '7', '專業選修(系所)', 'G304', '2', '1,2,3,4', '修課限制：\n1.本系二技進修部、護理學院。\n2.密集前9周上課，選課至加退選第二階段。', '本課程以園藝治療的基本理論為基礎，結合健康照護實務普遍應用的園藝治療課程\r\n設計與技巧，協助學生體悟植物、人與生命之間的關係，以運用於個人之情緒及身體調\r\n適，進而紓解其情緒、學習及生活壓力。課程內容包括：園藝治療基本理論、營造健康\r\n的室內環境設計法、增加五感刺激的園藝治療、舒壓的園藝治療、園藝治療於唐氏症和\r\n自閉症兒童、精神障礙者及老人照護的設計與應用、參觀療癒花園、常用的園藝治療課\r\n程設計與應用包括：種子播種和發芽、扦插和分株、地下組織之再生、劍山插花、壓花\r\n卡片及香草的生活應用等方法、植物與生命故事及成果展示等課程內容。', 'The course is based on the basic theory of horticultural therapy, combined with health care \r\npractice is widely horticultural therapy techniques and methods. The course assists students to \r\nunderstand the relationship of life between plants and human, to relieve their life pressure and \r\nto apply their earn experiences for health care practices The course contents included: \r\nintroduction to basic theory of horticultural therapy, healthy indoor environmental design, 5 \r\nsensory therapy garden design, horticultural therapy for stress release, horticultural therapy \r\nfor Autism and Down syndromes, horticultural therapy for mental illness, horticultural \r\ntherapy for older adults, visit to therapy garden, horticultural therapy course design and 9 \r\napplication included: planting, cutting, tissue regeneration, flower arrangement on metal frog, \r\nherb application, floral embossed cards, sixth sense plant and life story and products show.', '851', '3103Z1G1', '310G30', '護夜二30', '851'),
