(1333, '1223', '1131', '吳桂花', '113301423012C0', '11330', '1423', '1', 2, 0, '實證健康照護', 'Evidence-Based Practice in Healthcare', '吳桂花', 44, 4, 40, 2.00, '第1~4週', 2.00, '3', '專業必修(系所)', 'B113', '4', '11,12,13,14', '修課限制：本系二技進修部二年級，暑假提早上課8/15-10/3、提前開課。', '本課程目標在協助學生獲得實證護理相關的知識與技能。課程以執行實證五步驟為架構，內容包含:介紹實證護理概念、提出實證可以回答的臨床問題(PICO)、文獻資料庫與搜尋最佳證據、評析文獻與實證護理應用。實作方面包含:運用學習小組練習以PICO詢問臨床問題、搜尋回答問題之最佳證據、練習評讀隨機控制研究、判斷證據等級、提出臨床決策建議及閱讀系統性文獻回顧文章。', 'This course aims to introduceevidence-based nursing and strengthen knowledge and skills of evidence-based nursing for nursing students. Course contents includefundationalconcepts of evidence-based nursing, concepts of systematic review and clinical guideline, PICO, searching for the current best evidence, methodologyappraisal, and analyzing data. Students will have the opportunity to practice skills of using PICO to ask answerable clinical questions, searching the evidence and assessing quality of a randomized controlled trial, levels of evidence, and reading articles of systema tric review .', '966', '3102Q891', '310223', '護二二丙', '966'),
